263=>['Protective Bond','While you maintain this enchantment, target ally cannot lose more than 5% max Health due to damage from a single attack or spell. When Protective Bond prevents damage, you lose 6...3 Energy or the spell ends.','Target ally cannot lose more than 5% max Health from a single attack or spell. <gray>Each time damage is reduced you lose 6...3 Energy or this spell ends.</gray>'],
