371=>['Balanced Stance','For 8...20 seconds, you cannot be knocked down and you do not suffer extra damage from a critical attack.','(8...20 seconds.) You cannot be knocked-down and do not take extra damage from critical hits.'],
372=>['Gladiator\'s Defense','For 5...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks. Whenever you block a melee attack this way, the attacker suffers 5...35 damage.','(5...11 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. Your attacker takes 5...35 damage whenever you block a melee attack this way.'],
373=>['Deflect Arrows','For 1...6 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block attacks. If you block a projectile attack, adjacent foes suffer from Bleeding for 5...15 seconds.','(1...6 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block attacks. Adjacent foes suffer Bleeding (5...15 seconds) when you block a projectile attack.'],
374=>['Warrior\'s Endurance','For 5...35 seconds, you gain 3 Energy each time you hit with a melee attack. Warrior\'s Endurance cannot raise your Energy above 10...25.','(5...35 seconds.) You gain 3 Energy each time you hit with a melee attack. <gray>No Energy gain if you have more than 10...25 Energy.</gray>'],
375=>['Dwarven Battle Stance','For 5...11 seconds, if you are wielding a hammer, you attack 33% faster, you gain +40 armor, and your attack skills interrupt foes when they hit.','(5...11 seconds.) You attack 33% faster, you gain +40 armor, and your attack skills interrupt actions. <gray>No effect unless you have a hammer equipped.</gray>'],
376=>['Disciplined Stance','For 1...4 seconds, you gain +10 armor and have a 75% chance to block attacks. Disciplined Stance ends if you use an adrenal skill.','(1...4 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block and +10 armor. <gray>Ends if you use an adrenal skill.</gray>'],
377=>['Wary Stance','For 1...6 seconds, you block any attack skills used against you. For each successful block, you gain adrenaline and 5 Energy. Wary Stance ends if you use a skill.','(1...6 seconds). You block attack skills. Gain adrenaline and 5 Energy for each block. <gray>Ends if you use a skill.</gray>'],
378=>['Shield Stance','For 1...6 seconds, while wielding a shield, you have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks, and damage is reduced by 2 for each rank of Strength (maximum 15 damage reduction).','(1...6 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. Damage is reduced by 2 for each rank of Strength (maximum 15 damage reduction). <gray>No effect unless you have a shield equipped.</gray>'],
379=>['Bull\'s Charge','For 5...11 seconds, you move 33% faster and if you strike a moving foe in melee, that foe is knocked down. Bull\'s Charge ends if you use a skill.','(5...11 seconds.) You move 33% faster. Causes knock-down if you hit a moving foe in melee. <gray>Ends if you use a skill.</gray>'],
380=>['Bonetti\'s Defense','For 5...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block melee and projectile attacks. You gain 5 Energy for each successful melee attack blocked. Bonetti\'s Defense ends if you use a skill.','(5...11 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. Gain 5 Energy for each melee attack blocked. <gray>Ends if you use a skill.</gray>'],
381=>['Hundred Blades','For 15 seconds, whenever you attack with a sword, all adjacent foes take 10...25 slashing damage.','(15 seconds.) Deals 10...25 slashing damage to all adjacent foes whenever you attack with a sword.'],
382=>['Sever Artery','If this attack hits, the opponent begins Bleeding for 5...25 seconds, losing Health over time.','Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...25 seconds).'],
383=>['Galrath Slash','This attack strikes for +1...40 damage if it hits.','Deals +1...40 damage.'],
384=>['Gash','If this attack hits a Bleeding foe, you strike for 5...20 more damage and that foe suffers a Deep Wound, lowering that foe\'s maximum Health by 20% for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage and inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if your target is Bleeding.'],
385=>['Final Thrust','Lose all adrenaline. If Final Thrust hits, you deal 1...40 more damage. This damage is doubled if your target was below 50% Health.','Deals +1...40 damage. Deals +1...40 more damage if target foe is below 50% Health. <gray>Lose all adrenaline.</gray>'],
386=>['Seeking Blade','If this attack hits you strike for +1...20 damage. If Seeking Blade is blocked, your target begins Bleeding for 25 seconds and takes 1...20 damage.','Deals +1...20 damage. Deals 1...20 damage and inflicts Bleeding condition (25 seconds) if blocked.'],
387=>['Riposte','For 8 seconds, while you have a sword equipped, you block the next melee attack against you and your attacker is struck for 20...80 damage.','(8 seconds). You block the next melee attack and your attacker takes 20...80 damage. <gray>No effect unless you have a sword equipped.</gray>'],
388=>['Deadly Riposte','For 8 seconds, while you have a sword equipped, you block the next melee attack against you, and your attacker is struck for 15...90 damage and begins Bleeding for 3...25 seconds.','(8 seconds). You block the next melee attack and your attacker takes 15...90 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition. (3...25 seconds). <gray>No effect unless you have a sword equipped.</gray>'],
389=>['Flourish','All of your attack skills become recharged. You gain 2...7 Energy for each skill recharged by Flourish.','Recharges your attack skills. You gain 2...7 Energy for each skill recharged.'],
390=>['Savage Slash','If this attack hits, it interrupts target foe\'s action. If that action was a spell, you deal 1...40 extra damage.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: deals +1...40 damage if action was a spell.'],
391=>['Hunter\'s Shot','If this attack hits, your target bleeds for 3...25 seconds.','Inflicts Bleeding condition (3...25 seconds) if your target is hit.'],
392=>['Pin Down','If Pin Down hits, your target is Crippled for 3...15 seconds.','Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds).'],
393=>['Crippling Shot','If Crippling Shot hits, your target becomes Crippled for 1...11 seconds. This attack cannot be blocked.','Unblockable. Inflicts Crippled condition (1...11 seconds).'],
394=>['Power Shot','If Power Shot hits, target foe takes 25...50 damage.','Target foe takes 25...50 damage.'],
395=>['Barrage','All your preparations are removed. Shoot arrows at target foe and up to 5 foes adjacent to your target. These arrows strike for +5...20 damage if they hit.','Deals +5...20 damage. Hits 5 foes adjacent to your target. <gray>All your preparations are removed.</gray>'],
396=>['Dual Shot','Shoot two arrows simultaneously at target foe. These arrows deal 25% less damage.','You shoot two arrows simultaneously at target foe. <gray>These arrows deal 25% less damage</gray>'],
397=>['Quick Shot','Shoot an arrow that moves twice as fast.','You shoot an arrow that moves twice as fast.'],
398=>['Penetrating Attack','If Penetrating Attack hits, you strike for +5...25 damage and this attack has 10% armor penetration.','Deals +5...25 damage. 10% armor penetration.'],
399=>['Distracting Shot','If Distracting Shot hits, it interrupts target foe\'s action but deals only 1...16 damage. If the interrupted action was a skill, that skill is disabled for an additional 20 seconds.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: interrupted skill is disabled for +20 seconds. <gray>Hits for only 1...16 damage.</gray>'],
400=>['Precision Shot','If Precision Shot hits, you strike for +3...10 damage. Precision Shot cannot be blocked. This action is easily interrupted.','Deals +3...10 damage. Unblockable. <gray>Easily Interrupted.</gray>'],
402=>['Determined Shot','If Determined Shot hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. If Determined Shot fails to hit, all of your attack skills are recharged.','Deals +5...20 damage. Recharges your attack skills if it fails to hit.'],
403=>['Called Shot','Shoot an arrow that moves 3 times faster and cannot be blocked.','You shoot an arrow that moves 3 times faster. Unblockable.'],
404=>['Poison Arrow','If Poison Arrow hits, your target becomes Poisoned for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Poisoned condition. (5...20)'],
405=>['Oath Shot','If Oath Shot hits, all of your skills except Oath Shot are recharged. If it misses, all of your skills are disabled for 10...4 seconds. (50% miss chance with Expertise 7 or less.)','Recharges all skills except Oath Shot if it hits. <gray>Disables all skills if it misses (10...4 seconds). 50% miss chance unless Expertise 8 or higher.</gray>'],
406=>['Debilitating Shot','If Debilitating Shot hits, your target loses 1...10 Energy.','Causes 1...10 Energy loss.'],
407=>['Point Blank Shot','Shoot an arrow that has half the normal range, but strikes for +10...40 damage.','Half Range Bow Attack. Deals +10...40 damage.'],
408=>['Concussion Shot','If Concussion Shot hits while target foe is casting a spell, the spell is interrupted and your target is Dazed for 5...20 seconds. This attack deals only 1...16 damage.','Interrupts a spell. Interruption effect: inflicts Dazed condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>Hits for only 1...16 damage.</gray>'],
409=>['Punishing Shot','If Punishing Shot hits, you strike for +10...20 damage and your target is interrupted.','Deals +10...20 damage. Interrupts an action.'],
411=>['Charm Animal','Charm target animal. Once charmed, your animal companion will travel with you whenever you have Charm Animal equipped. You cannot charm an animal that is more than 4 levels above you.','Charm target animal. Once charmed, your animal companion will travel with you whenever you have Charm Animal equipped. <gray>You cannot charm an animal that is more than 4 levels above you.</gray>'],
412=>['Call of Protection','For 120 seconds, your animal companion has a 5...20 base damage reduction.','(120 seconds.) Your pet has 5...20 damage reduction.'],
415=>['Call of Haste','For 30 seconds, your animal companion has a 33% faster attack speed and moves 33% faster.','(30 seconds.) Your pet moves and attacks 33% faster.'],
422=>['Revive Animal','Resurrect all nearby allied animal companions. They come back to life with 10...94% Health.','Resurrects all nearby allied pets (10...94% Health).'],
423=>['Symbiotic Bond','For 120...300 seconds, your animal companion gains 1...3 Health regeneration, and half of all damage dealt to your animal companion is redirected to you.','(120...300 seconds.) Your pet has +1...3 Health regeneration. Half of all damage dealt to your pet is redirected to you.'],
424=>['Throw Dirt','Target touched foe and foes adjacent to your target become Blinded for 3...15 seconds.','Inflicts Blindness condition (3...15 seconds). Also affects foes adjacent to target foe.'],
425=>['Dodge','For 5...11 seconds, you move 33% faster and have a 27...75% chance to block incoming projectiles. Dodge ends if you attack.','(5...11 seconds.) You move 33% faster and have 27...75% chance to block projectile attacks. <gray>Ends if you attack.</gray>'],
426=>['Savage Shot','If Savage Shot hits, your target\'s action is interrupted. If that action was a spell, you strike for +13...28 damage.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: deals +13...28 damage if action was a spell.'],
427=>['Antidote Signet','Cleanse yourself of Poison, Disease, and Blindness, and one additional condition.','Remove Poison, Disease, and Blindness from yourself, and one additional condition.'],
428=>['Incendiary Arrows','Shoot arrows at target foe and up to 2 foes near your target. Those foes are set on fire for 1...3 seconds.','Hits 2 foes near your target and inflicts burning (1...3 seconds).'],
429=>['Melandru\'s Arrows','For 18 seconds, whenever your arrows hit, they cause Bleeding for 3...25 seconds, and if they hit a target who is under an enchantment, they do +8...28 damage.','(18 seconds.) Your arrows inflict Bleeding condition (3...25 seconds) and deal +8...28 damage to enchanted foes.'],
430=>['Marksman\'s Wager','For 18 seconds, you gain 5...10 Energy whenever your arrows hit, but lose 10 Energy whenever your arrows fail to strike.','(18 seconds.) Gain 5...10 Energy whenever your arrows hit. <gray>Lose 10 Energy whenever your arrows fail to hit.</gray>'],
431=>['Ignite Arrows','For 24 seconds, your arrows explode on contact, dealing 3...18 fire damage to target and all adjacent foes.','(24 seconds.) Your arrows deal 3...18 fire damage to target and foes adjacent to target.'],
432=>['Read the Wind','For 24 seconds, your arrows move twice as fast and deal 3...10 extra damage.','(24 seconds). +3...10 damage. Your arrows move twice as fast.'],
433=>['Kindle Arrows','For 24 seconds, your arrows deal fire damage and hit for an additional 3...24 fire damage.','(24 seconds.) +3...24 fire damage. Your arrows deal fire damage.'],
434=>['Choking Gas','For 1...12 seconds, your arrows deal 1...8 more damage and spread Choking Gas to all adjacent foes on impact. Choking Gas interrupts foes attempting to cast spells.','(1...12 seconds.) +1...8 damage. Spreads Choking Gas to foes adjacent to target. Choking Gas interrupts spells.'],
435=>['Apply Poison','For 24 seconds, foes struck by your physical attacks become Poisoned for 3...15 seconds.','(24 seconds.) Your physical attacks inflict Poisoned condition (3...15 seconds).'],
436=>['Comfort Animal','You heal your animal companion for 20...104 Health. If your companion is dead, it is resurrected with 10...58% Health. If you have Comfort Animal equipped, your animal companion will travel with you.','Your pet gains 20...104 Health. Resurrects your pet (10...58% Health.) If you have Comfort Animal equipped, your animal companion will travel with you.'],
437=>['Bestial Pounce','Your animal companion attempts a Bestial Pounce that deals +5...20 damage. If the attack strikes a foe who is casting a spell, that foe is knocked down.','Deals +5...20 damage. Causes knock-down if target foe is casting a spell.'],
438=>['Maiming Strike','Your animal companion attempts a Maiming Strike that deals +5...20 damage. If that attack hits a moving foe that foe becomes Crippled for 3...15 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds) if target foe is moving.'],
439=>['Feral Lunge','Your animal companion attempts a Feral Lunge that deals +5...35 damage. If the attack strikes a foe who is attacking, that foe suffers from Bleeding for 5...25 seconds.','Deals +5...35 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition if target foe is attacking (5...25 seconds).'],
440=>['Scavenger Strike','Your animal companion attempts a Scavenger Strike that deals +10...25 damage. If the attack strikes a foe who is suffering a condition, you gain 3...15 Energy.','Deals +10...25 damage. You gain 3...15 Energy if target foe has a condition.'],
441=>['Melandru\'s Assault','Your animal companion attempts a Melandru\'s Assault that deals +5...20 damage to all nearby foes.','Deals +5...20 damage to nearby foes.'],
442=>['Ferocious Strike','Your animal companion attempts a Ferocious Strike that deals +13...28 damage. If that attack hits, you gain adrenaline and 3...10 Energy.','Deals +13...28 damage. You gain adrenaline and 3...10 energy.'],
443=>['Predator\'s Pounce','Your animal companion attempts a Predator\'s Pounce that deals +5...35 damage. If that attack hits, your animal companion gains 5...50 Health.','Deals +5...35 damage. Your pet gains 5...50 Health if this attack hits.'],
444=>['Brutal Strike','Your animal companion attempts a Brutal Strike that deals +5...35 damage. If that attack strikes a foe whose Health is below 50%, that foe takes an additional +5...35 damage.','Deals +5...35 damage. Deals +5...35 more damage if target foe is under 50% health.'],
445=>['Disrupting Lunge','Your animal companion attempts a Disrupting Lunge that deals +1...12 damage. If that attack strikes a foe using a skill that skill is interrupted and is disabled for an additional 20 seconds.','Deals +1...12 damage. Interrupts a skill. Interruption effect: interrupted skill is disabled for +20 seconds.'],
446=>['Troll Unguent','For 13 seconds, you gain +3...10 Health regeneration.','(13 seconds.) You have +3...10 Health regeneration.'],
447=>['Otyugh\'s Cry','For 10...25 seconds, your animal companion gains +24 armor and cannot be blocked.','(10...25 seconds.) Your pet has +24 armor and is unblockable.'],
448=>['Escape','For 1...8 seconds, you move 33% faster and have a 75% chance to block attacks.','(1...8 seconds.) You move 33% faster and have 75% chance to block.'],
449=>['Practiced Stance','For 20...35 seconds, your Preparations recharge 50% faster and last 30...150% longer.','(20...35 seconds.) Your preparations recharge 50% faster and last 30...150% longer.'],
450=>['Whirling Defense','For 8...20 seconds, you have 75% chance to block attacks. Whenever you block a projectile in this way, adjacent foes take 5...11 damage.','(8...20 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. Deals 5...11 damage to adjacent foes whenever you block a projectile attack.'],
451=>['Melandru\'s Resilience','For 8...20 seconds, you gain +4 Health regeneration and +1 Energy regeneration for each condition and hex you are suffering.','(8...20 seconds.) You have +4 Health regeneration and +1 Energy regeneration for each condition and hex on you.'],
452=>['Dryder\'s Defenses','For 5...11 seconds, you gain 75% chance to block attacks and 34...60 armor against elemental damage.','(5...11 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block and +34...60 armor against elemental damage.'],
453=>['Lightning Reflexes','For 5...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block melee and projectile attacks, and you attack 33% faster.','(5...11 seconds.) You attack 33% faster and have 75% chance to block.'],
454=>['Tiger\'s Fury','All your non-attack skills are disabled for 5 seconds. For 5...11 seconds, you attack 25% faster.','(5...11 seconds.) You attack 25% faster. <gray>Disables your non-attack skills (5 seconds).</gray>'],
455=>['Storm Chaser','For 8...20 seconds, you move 25% faster, and you gain 1...5 Energy whenever you take elemental damage.','(8...20 seconds.) You move 25% faster and gain 1...5 Energy whenever you take elemental damage.'],
456=>['Serpent\'s Quickness','For 15...30 seconds, recharge times for your skills are reduced by 33%. Serpent\'s Quickness ends if your Health drops below 50%.','(15...30 seconds.) Your skills recharge 33% faster. <gray>Ends if your Health drops below 50%.</gray>'],
457=>['Dust Trap','When Dust Trap is triggered, every second (for 5 seconds total), all nearby foes are Blinded for 3...8 seconds and take 10...25 damage. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted. Dust Trap ends after 90 seconds.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 10...25 damage every second (5 seconds). Inflicts Blindness condition (3...8 seconds) every second (5 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
458=>['Barbed Trap','When Barbed Trap is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 7...23 piercing damage, become Crippled, and begin Bleeding for 3...25 seconds. Barbed Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 7...23 piercing damage. Inflicts Crippled and Bleeding conditions (3...25 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
459=>['Flame Trap','When Flame Trap is triggered, every second (for 3 seconds total), all nearby foes are struck for 5...20 fire damage and set on fire for 1...3 seconds. Flame Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 5...20 fire damage every second (3 seconds). Inflicts Burning condition (1...3 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
460=>['Healing Spring','For 10 seconds, all adjacent allies are healed for 15...60 every 2 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(10 seconds.) Affects adjacent allies. Heals for 15...60 every 2 seconds. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
461=>['Spike Trap','When Spike Trap is triggered, every second (for 2 seconds), all nearby foes are struck for 10...40 piercing damage, become Crippled for 3...25 seconds, and are knocked down. Spike Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Every second, (for 2 seconds), this trap deals 10...40 piercing damage, causes knockdown, and inflicts Crippled condition (3...25 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
462=>['Winter','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For creatures within its range, all elemental damage is cold damage instead. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Converts elemental damage to cold damage for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
463=>['Winnowing','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit creatures within range take 4 additional damage whenever they take physical damage. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Increases physical damage by +4 for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
464=>['Edge of Extinction','Create a level 1...10 spirit. If a non-spirit creature within range dies, Edge of Extinction deals 14...50 damage to all creatures of the same type that are below 90% Health and within range of the spirit. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Deals 14...50 damage to creatures in its range whenever a creature of the same type dies. Does not affect spirits. <gray>No damage to creatures above 90% Health.</gray>'],
465=>['Greater Conflagration','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all physical damage is fire damage instead. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Converts physical damage to fire damage for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
466=>['Conflagration','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all arrows that hit strike for fire damage. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). All arrows deal fire damage for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
467=>['Fertile Season','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit creatures within range have +50...150 maximum Health and gain +8 armor. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Creatures in range have +50...150 maximum health and +8 armor. Does not affect spirits.'],
468=>['Symbiosis','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For each enchantment on a non-spirit creature within range, that creature has +27...150 maximum Health. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Creatures in range have +27...150 maximum health for each enchantment on them. Does not affect spirits.'],
469=>['Primal Echoes','Create a level 1...10 Spirit. For non-Spirit creatures within its range, Signets cost 10 Energy to use. This Spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Signets cost 10 energy for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
470=>['Predatory Season','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all healing is reduced by 20%. If any of your attacks hit, you gain 5 Health. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Creatures in range receive 20% less from healing. Creatures gain 5 health each time they hit with an attack. Does not affect spirits.'],
471=>['Frozen Soil','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit creatures within its range cannot activate resurrection skills. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit. (30...90 second lifespan). Creatures in range cannot activate resurrection skills. Does not affect spirits.'],
472=>['Favorable Winds','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, arrows move twice as fast and strike for +6 damage. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Arrows move twice as fast and hit for +6 damage for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
474=>['Energizing Wind','Create a level 1...6 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all skills cost 15 less Energy (minimum cost 10 Energy), and skills recharge 25% slower. This spirit dies after 1...31 seconds.','Creates a level 1...6 spirit (1...31 seconds lifespan). Skills cost 15 less energy (minimum cost 10 energy) and recharge 25% slower for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
475=>['Quickening Zephyr','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For non-spirit creatures within its range, all skills recharge twice as fast and cost 30% more of the base Energy to cast. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Skills cost 30% more Energy and recharge twice as fast for creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
476=>['Nature\'s Renewal','Create a level 1...10 spirit. For 30...150 seconds, enchantments and hexes cast by non-spirit creatures in range take twice as long to cast, and it costs twice as much Energy to maintain enchantments. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). For creatures in range, enchantments and Hexes <sic/> take twice as long to cast and it costs twice as much Energy to maintain enchantments. Does not affect spirits.'],
477=>['Muddy Terrain','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit creatures within its range move 10% slower and speed boosts have no effect. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Creatures in range have 10% slower movement: also negates speed boosts. <gray>Does not affect spirits.</gray>'],
570=>['Mark of Insecurity','For 5...25 seconds, target foe suffers from -1...3 Health degeneration, and enchantments and stances on target foe expire 30...80% faster. All of your non-Assassin skills are disabled for 10 seconds.','(5...25 seconds.) Causes -1...3 Health degeneration. Enchantments and stances expire 30...80% faster on target foe. <gray>Disables your non-Assassin skills (10 seconds).</gray>'],
571=>['Disrupting Dagger','Send out a Disrupting Dagger at target foe that strikes for 10...35 earth damage. If that foe was activating a skill, that skill is interrupted. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Spell. Projectile: deals 10...35 earth damage. Interrupts a skill.'],
572=>['Deadly Paradox','All of your attack skills are disabled for 10 seconds. For 5...15 seconds, your Assassin skills activate and recharge 33% faster.','(5...15 seconds.) Your Assassin skills activate and recharge 33% faster. <gray>Disables your attack skills (10 seconds).</gray>'],
763=>['Jaundiced Gaze','Remove an enchantment from target foe. If an enchantment is removed, for the next 1...15 seconds, your next enchantment spell casts 0...1 seconds faster and costs 1...10 less Energy.','Removes an enchantment from target foe. Removal effect: your next enchantment casts 0...1 seconds faster and costs 1...10 less Energy. (1...15 seconds)'],
764=>['Wail of Doom','For 1...4 seconds, all of target foe\'s attributes are set to 0.','(1...4 seconds.) Target foe\'s attributes are 0.'],
766=>['Gaze of Contempt','If target foe has more than 50% Health, that foe loses all enchantments.','Removes target foe\'s enchantments. <gray>No effect unless this foe has more than 50% Health.</gray>'],
769=>['Viper\'s Defense','All adjacent foes are Poisoned for 5...20 seconds. Shadow Step to a nearby location directly away from your target.','Inflict Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds) on all adjacent foes and Shadow Step to a nearby location directly away from your target.'],
770=>['Return','All adjacent foes are Crippled for 3...8 seconds. Shadow Step to target other ally\'s location.','Inflicts Crippled condition (3...8 seconds) on all foes adjacent to you. You Shadow Step to target ally\'s location. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
771=>['Aura of Displacement','When you cast Aura of Displacement, Shadow Step to target foe. When you stop maintaining Aura of Displacement you return to your original location.','Shadow Step to target foe. End effect: return to your original location.'],
772=>['Generous Was Tsungrai','Hold Tsungrai\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds and gain +50...140 maximum Health. When you drop his ashes, you gain 100...280 Health.','(15...60 seconds.) You have +50...140 maximum Health. Drop effect: you gain 100...280 Health.'],
773=>['Mighty Was Vorizun','Hold Vorizun\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. While you hold his ashes, you gain +15 armor and +30 maximum Energy.','(15...60 seconds.) You have +15 armor and +30 maximum Energy.'],
775=>['Death Blossom','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, Death Blossom strikes target foe for +20...45 damage and all adjacent foes take 20...45 damage.','Deals +20...45 damage. Also affects foes adjacent to target foe. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
776=>['Twisting Fangs','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, Twisting Fangs strikes for +10...20 damage and struck foe suffers from Bleeding and Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +10...20 damage. Inflicts Bleeding and Deep Wound conditions (5...20 seconds). <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
777=>['Horns of the Ox','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, Horns of the Ox strikes for +1...11 damage. If struck foe is not adjacent to any allies, that foe is knocked down.','Deals +1...11 damage. Causes knock-down if the target foe is not adjacent to any of its allies. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
778=>['Falling Spider','Must strike a knocked-down foe. If it hits, Falling Spider strikes for +15...35 damage and target foe is Poisoned for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +15...35 damage. Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>No effect unless target foe is knocked-down.</gray>'],
779=>['Black Lotus Strike','If it hits, Black Lotus Strike strikes for +10...31 damage. If target foe is suffering from a Hex, you gain 5...13 Energy.','Deals +10...31 damage. You gain 5...13 Energy if target foe is hexed.'],
780=>['Fox Fangs','Must follow a lead attack. Fox Fangs cannot be blocked and strikes for +10...35 damage if it hits.','Deals +10...35 damage. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
781=>['Moebius Strike','Must follow a Dual Attack. If it hits, Moebius Strike strikes for +10...35 damage. If you strike a foe whose Health is below 50%, all your other attack skills are recharged.','Deals +10...35 damage. Recharges all your other attack skills if target foe\'s Health is below 50%. <gray>Must follow a dual attack.</gray>'],
782=>['Jagged Strike','If Jagged Strike hits, your target suffers from Bleeding for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds).'],
783=>['Unsuspecting Strike','If this attack hits, you strike for +19...31 damage. If your target was above 90% Health you deal an additional 15...75 damage.','Deals +19...31 damage. Deals 15...75 more damage if target foe\'s Health is above 90%.'],
784=>['Entangling Asp','Entangling Asp must follow a lead attack. Target foe is knocked down and becomes Poisoned for 5...20 seconds.','Causes knock-down. Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
785=>['Mark of Death','For 4...10 seconds, target foe gains 33% less benefit from healing.','(4...10 seconds.) Target foe receives 33% less from healing.'],
786=>['Iron Palm','Target touched foe suffers 5...50 damage, and if that foe is suffering from a hex or condition that foe is knocked down. Iron Palm counts as a lead attack.','Deals 5...50 damage. Causes knock-down if target foe is hexed or has a condition. Counts as a lead attack.'],
787=>['Resilient Weapon','For 3...12 seconds, target ally has a Resilient Weapon. While suffering from a hex or condition, that ally gains +1...6 Health regeneration and +24 armor.','(3...12 seconds.) +1...6 Health regeneration and +24 armor. <gray>No effect unless target ally is hexed or has a condition.</gray>'],
788=>['Blind Was Mingson','Hold Mingson\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. When you drop his ashes, all nearby foes are Blinded for 3...8 seconds.','(15...60 seconds.) Drop effect: inflicts Blindness condition (3...8 seconds) on all nearby foes.'],
789=>['Grasping Was Kuurong','Hold Kuurong\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. When you drop his ashes, all nearby foes are struck for 15...75 damage and knocked down.','(15...60 seconds.) Drop effect: deal 15...75 damage and knocks-down all nearby foes.'],
790=>['Vengeful Was Khanhei','Hold Khanhei\'s ashes for 5...11 seconds. Whenever a foe strikes you in combat while you are holding Khanhei\'s ashes, you steal 5...35 Health from that foe.','(5...11 seconds.) You steal 5...35 Health from every foe that hits you with an attack.'],
791=>['Flesh of My Flesh','Lose half your Health. Resurrect target party member with your current Health and 5...20% Energy.','Resurrect target party member (half your current Health and 5...20% Energy). <gray>Lose half your Health.</gray>'],
792=>['Splinter Weapon','For 20 seconds, target ally has a Splinter Weapon. Target ally\'s next 1...5 attacks deal 5...50 damage to up to 4 adjacent foes.','(20 seconds.) Attacks deal 5...50 damage to 3 <sic/> adjacent foes. <gray>Ends after 1...5 attacks.</gray>'],
793=>['Weapon of Warding','For 3...8 seconds, target ally has a Weapon of Warding that grants target ally +2...4 Health regeneration and a 50% chance to block.','(3...8 seconds.) +2...4 Health regeneration. 50% chance to block.'],
794=>['Wailing Weapon','For 3...9 seconds, target ally has a Wailing Weapon. Whenever the Wailing Weapon strikes an attacking foe, that foe is interrupted.','(3...9 seconds.) Attacks interrupt attacking foes.'],
795=>['Nightmare Weapon','For 12 seconds, target ally has a Nightmare Weapon. Target ally\'s next 3 attacks are reduced by 10...50 damage and steal up to 10...50 Health.','(12 seconds.) Target ally\'s attacks steal 10...50 Health but deal 10...50 less damage. <gray>Ends after 3 attacks.</gray>'],
799=>['Beguiling Haze','Shadow Step to target foe. That foe becomes Dazed for 3...9 seconds.','You Shadow Step to this foe. Inflicts Dazed condition (3...9 seconds).'],
800=>['Enduring Toxin','For 5 seconds, target foe suffers -1...5 Health degeneration. If that foe is moving when Enduring Toxin would end, Enduring Toxin is renewed for another 5 seconds.','(5 seconds.) Causes -1...5 Health degeneration. Renewal: if the target foe is moving when this hex ends.'],
801=>['Shroud of Silence','All of your spells are disabled for 15 seconds. For 1...3 seconds, target touched foe cannot cast spells.','Elite Touch Hex Spell. (1...3 seconds.) Target foe cannot cast spells. <gray>Your spells are disabled for 15 seconds.</gray>'],
802=>['Expose Defenses','For 1...11 seconds, target foe cannot block your attacks.','(1...11 seconds.) Target foe cannot block your attacks.'],
803=>['Power Leech','If target foe is casting a spell or chant, that skill is interrupted and for 10 seconds, whenever that foe casts a spell, you steal up to 5...15 Energy from that foe.','Interrupt a spell or a chant. Interruption effect: steal 5...15 Energy whenever target foe casts a spell (10 seconds).'],
804=>['Arcane Languor','For 1...10 seconds, all spells cast by the target foe cause 10 Overcast.','(1...10 seconds.) Target foe\'s spells cause 10 Overcast.'],
805=>['Animate Vampiric Horror','Exploit nearest corpse to animate a level 1...17 Vampiric Horror. Whenever a Vampiric Horror you control deals damage, you gain the same amount of Health.','Creates a level 1...17 vampiric horror. You gain Health equal to the damage it deals. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse.</gray>'],
806=>['Cultist\'s Fervor','For 5 seconds and 3 seconds longer for every rank of Soul Reaping, your Necromancer spells cost 1...6 Energy to cast but you suffer from Bleeding for 10 seconds each time you cast a Necromancer spell.','(5 seconds plus 3 seconds more for every rank of Soul Reaping.) Your Necromancer spells cost 1...6 less Energy. <gray>You suffer from Bleeding (10 seconds) each time you cast a Necromancer spell.</gray>'],
808=>['Reaper\'s Mark','For 30 seconds, target foe suffers -1...5 Health degeneration. If that foe dies while hexed with Reaper\'s Mark, you gain 5...15 Energy.','(30 seconds.) Causes -1...5 Health degeneration. You gain 5...15 Energy if target foe dies while suffering from this hex.'],
809=>['Shatterstone','Target foe is struck for 25...100 cold damage and is hexed with Shatterstone for 3 seconds. When Shatterstone ends, that foe and all nearby foes are struck for 25...100 cold damage.','(3 seconds.) Initial effect: deals 25...100 cold damage. End effect: deals 25...100 cold damage to target and all nearby foes.'],
810=>['Protector\'s Defense','For 5...11 seconds, allies adjacent to you have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks. Protector\'s Defense ends if you move.','(5...11 seconds.) Allies adjacent to you have 75% chance to block. <gray>Ends if you move.</gray>'],
811=>['Run as One','For 5...15 seconds, you and your pet run 25% faster.','(5...15 seconds.) You and your pet move 25% faster.'],
812=>['Defiant Was Xinrae','Hold Xinrae\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. While you hold her ashes, you cannot lose more than 20% of your max Health from a single hit. When you drop her ashes, you steal 5...50 Health from all nearby foes.','(15...60 seconds.) You cannot lose more than 20% of your max Health from a single hit. Drop effect: steal 5...50 Health from nearby foes.'],
813=>['Lyssa\'s Aura','For 10 seconds, you have +0...5 Energy regeneration. This enchantment reapplies itself every time you cast a spell on a foe.','(10 seconds.) You have +0...5 Energy regeneration. Renewal: every time you cast a spell on an enemy.'],
814=>['Shadow Refuge','For 6 seconds, you gain 5...10 Health regeneration. When Shadow Refuge ends, you gain 40...100 Health if you are attacking.','(6 seconds.) You have +5...10 Health regeneration. End effect: heals you for 40...100 if you are attacking.'],
815=>['Scorpion Wire','For 8...20 seconds, the next time you and target foe are more than 100\' apart, you Shadow Step to that foe and that foe is knocked down. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Hex Spell. (8...20 seconds.) Shadow Step to target foe and cause knock-down the next time this foe is more than 100\' away from you.'],
816=>['Mirrored Stance','For 10...35 seconds, whenever target foe enters a stance, you enter the same stance.','(10...35 seconds.) You enter any stance used by target foe.'],
817=>['Discord','If target foe is suffering from a condition and under the effects of a hex or an enchantment, that foe suffers 30...110 damage.','Deals 30...110 damage. <gray>No effect unless target foe has a condition and is either hexed or enchanted.</gray>'],
818=>['Well of Weariness','Exploit target corpse to create a Well of Weariness for 10...55 seconds. Enemies within the Well of Weariness suffer -1 Energy degeneration.','(10...55 seconds.) Foes in this well have -1 Energy degeneration. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse.</gray>'],
819=>['Vampiric Spirit','Steal up to 5...50 Health from target foe. For 10 seconds, you have +5...10 Health regeneration.','Steal 5...50 Health from target foe. You have +5...10 Health regeneration (10 seconds).'],
820=>['Depravity','For 5...20 seconds, whenever target foe casts a spell, that foe and one nearby foe lose 1...5 Energy.','(5...20 seconds.) Causes 1...5 Energy loss whenever target foe casts a spell. One foe near your target also loses Energy.'],
821=>['Icy Veins','Target foe is struck for 10...90 cold damage. For 10...35 seconds, if target foe dies all nearby foes are struck for 20...110 cold damage.','(10...35 seconds.) Deals 20...110 cold damage to nearby foes if target foe dies. Initial effect: deals 10...90 cold damage.'],
822=>['Weaken Knees','For 1...16 seconds, target foe suffers -1...4 Health degeneration and takes 5...10 damage while moving.','(1...16 seconds.) Target foe has -1...4 Health degeneration and takes 5...10 damage while moving.'],
823=>['Burning Speed','For 7 seconds, you are set on fire and move 30...45% faster. When Burning Speed ends, all adjacent foes are set on fire for 3...9 seconds.','(7 seconds.) You move 30...45% faster. <gray>You suffer from Burning (7 seconds).</gray> End effect: inflicts Burning condition (3...9 seconds) on adjacent foes.'],
824=>['Lava Arrows','Lava Arrows fly toward up to 3 foes near your target and strike for 20...65 fire damage if they hit.','Projectile: deals 20...65 fire damage. Bonus effect: sends projectiles at 2 other foes near your target.'],
825=>['Bed of Coals','Create a Bed of Coals at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, foes adjacent to target foe are struck for 5...29 fire damage each second. Any foe knocked down on the Bed of Coals is set on fire for 3...7 seconds.','Deals 5...29 fire damage each second (5 seconds) to location of target foe. Hits foes adjacent to your target. Inflicts Burning condition (3...7 seconds) on knocked down foes.'],
826=>['Shadow Form','For 5...21 seconds, you cannot be the target of enemy spells, and you gain 5 damage reduction for each Assassin enchantment on you. You cannot deal more than 5...25 damage with a single skill or attack.','(5...21 seconds.) Enemy spells cannot target you. Gain 5 damage reduction for each Assassin enchantment on you. <gray>You cannot deal more than 5...25 damage with a single skill or attack.</gray>'],
827=>['Siphon Strength','For 5...20 seconds, target foe deals 5...50 less damage with attacks and all of your attacks against that foe have an additional 33% chance of being a critical hit.','(5...20 seconds.) Target foe deals 5...50 attack damage. You have +33% chance to land a critical hit on this foe.'],
828=>['Vile Miasma','Target foe is struck for 10...65 cold damage. If suffering from a condition, that foe is hexed with Vile Miasma and suffers -1...5 Health degeneration for 10 seconds.','Causes -1...5 Health degeneration (10 seconds). Initial effect: deals 10...65 cold damage. <gray>Hex is only applied if target foe has a condition.</gray>'],
830=>['Ray of Judgment','Invoke a Ray of Judgment at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, target foe and all foes adjacent to this location take 5...45 holy damage each second and begin Burning for 1...3 seconds.','Deals 5...45 holy damage and inflicts Burning (1...3 seconds) every second (5 seconds). Hits foes adjacent to target\'s initial location.'],
831=>['Primal Rage','For 1...15 seconds, you attack 33% faster and move 25% faster, but you take double damage.','(1...15 seconds.) You attack 33% faster and move 25% faster. <gray>You take double damage.</gray>'],
832=>['Animate Flesh Golem','Exploit nearest corpse to animate a level 3...25 Flesh Golem. The Flesh Golem leaves an exploitable corpse. You can have only one Flesh Golem at a time.','Creates a level 3...25 flesh golem which leaves a fresh corpse when it dies. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse. You can have only one flesh golem at a time.</gray>'],
834=>['Reckless Haste','For 6...12 seconds, target foe and all adjacent foes are hexed with Reckless Haste. While hexed, they attack 25% faster but have a 50% chance to miss with attacks.','Also hexes foes adjacent to your target (6...12 seconds). These foes have 50% chance to miss, but attack 25% faster.'],
835=>['Blood Bond','For 3...12 seconds, target foe and all adjacent foes are hexed with Blood Bond. Whenever an ally hits one of them with an attack, that ally gains 5...20 Health. If one of these foes dies while hexed, all allies adjacent to that foe are healed for 20...100 Health.','Also hexes foes adjacent to your target (3...12 seconds). Allies hitting these foes gain 5...20 health. If any of these foes dies while hexed, adjacent allies are healed for 20...100.'],
836=>['Ride the Lightning','You Ride the Lightning to target. All adjacent foes are Blinded for 1...5 seconds. If your target is a foe, it is struck for 10...70 lightning damage. This spell has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...70 lightning damage. 25% armor penetration. Blinds all adjacent foes (1...5 seconds). You instantly move to your target. May target allies.'],
837=>['Energy Boon','For 36...60 seconds, Energy Boon raises the maximum Health of you and target ally by 1...3 for each point of your respective maximum Energy. When this enchantment is first applied, you and your target gain 1...12 Energy. You gain an additional 1 Energy for every 2 points you have in Energy Storage.','(36...60 seconds.) Maximum Health for you and target ally is increased by 1...3 for each point of maximum Energy. Initial effect: Both gain 1...12 Energy. You gain +1 Energy for every 2 points of Energy Storage.'],
838=>['Dwayna\'s Sorrow','For 30 seconds, target ally and all nearby allies are enchanted with Dwayna\'s Sorrow. If an ally dies while under the effects of Dwayna\'s Sorrow, your party is healed for 5...50.','Enchants allies near your target (30 seconds). Your party is healed for 5...50 whenever one of these allies dies.'],
839=>['"Retreat!"','If there are any dead allies within earshot, your party moves 33% faster for 5...11 seconds.','(5...11 seconds.) Party members in earshot move 33% faster. <gray>No effect unless there are dead allies within earshot.</gray>'],
840=>['Poisoned Heart','You and all adjacent foes are Poisoned for 5...15 seconds.','Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...15 seconds) to adjacent foes. <gray>You are also Poisoned.</gray>'],
841=>['Fetid Ground','Target foe is struck for 15...65 cold damage. If that foe is knocked down, that foe becomes Poisoned for 5...20 seconds.','Deals 15...65 cold damage. Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe is knocked-down.'],
842=>['Arc Lightning','Target foe is struck for 5...40 lightning damage. If you are Overcast, two foes near your target are struck for 15...85 lightning damage. Damage from Arc Lightning has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 5...40 lightning damage. Deals 15...85 lightning damage to two nearby foes if you are Overcast. 25% armor penetration.'],
843=>['Gust','For 5...11 seconds, both you and target ally move 33% faster. When you cast this spell, all foes near you and your target take 15...70 cold damage. Foes struck by Gust while attacking or moving are knocked down.','(5...11 seconds.) You and target ally move 33% faster. Initial effect: Foes near you and target ally are struck for 15...70 cold damage. Attacking or moving foes are knocked down.'],
844=>['Churning Earth','Create Churning Earth at target foe\'s location. For the next 5 seconds, Churning Earth strikes foes near that location for 10...40 earth damage each second. Any foe moving faster than normal when struck by Churning Earth is knocked down.','Deals 10...40 earth damage each second (5 seconds). Hits foes near target\'s initial location. Causes knock-down to foes moving faster than normal.'],
845=>['Liquid Flame','Target foe is struck for 7...112 fire damage. If that foe is attacking or casting a spell, nearby foes are also struck for 7...112 fire damage.','Deals 7...112 fire damage. Deals 7...112 fire damage to nearby foes if target was attacking or casting.'],
846=>['Steam','Target foe is struck for 20...60 cold damage. If target foe is on fire, Steam Blinds that foe for 5...10 seconds.','Deals 20...60 cold damage. Inflicts Blindness condition (5...10 seconds) if target foe is Burning.'],
847=>['Boon Signet','Heal target ally for 20...80 Health. Your next Healing or Protection Prayer <sic/> spell that targets an ally heals for an additional 20...80 Health.','Heals for 20...80. Your next Healing or Protection Prayer <sic/> spell that targets an ally heals for +20...80 Health.'],
848=>['Reverse Hex','Remove one hex from target ally. If a hex was removed in this way, for 5...10 seconds, the next time target ally would take damage, that damage is reduced by 5...50.','(5...10 seconds.) Removes one hex from target ally. The next damage this ally takes is reduced by 5...50. <gray>No effect unless this ally is hexed.</gray>'],
849=>['Lacerating Chop','If Lacerating Chop hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If it strikes a knocked down foe your target suffers from Bleeding for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe is knocked-down.'],
850=>['Fierce Blow','If Fierce Blow hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. If target foe was <sic/> suffering from Weakness, that foe also suffers from a Deep Wound for 1...8 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound (1...8 seconds) if target foe is Weakened.'],
851=>['Sun and Moon Slash','Attack target foe twice. These attacks cannot be blocked.','You attack target foe twice. Unblockable.'],
852=>['Splinter Shot','If Splinter Shot hits, you deal +3...15 damage. If Splinter Shot is blocked, all foes adjacent to your target take 5...65 damage.','Deals +3...15 damage. Deals 5...65 damage to adjacent foes if blocked.'],
853=>['Melandru\'s Shot','If Melandru\'s Shot hits, your target begins Bleeding for 5...25 seconds. If it hits a foe that is moving or knocked down, that foe takes +10...25 damage and is Crippled for 5...15 seconds.','Inflicts Bleeding (5...25 seconds). Deals +10...25 damage and inflicts Crippled (5...15 seconds) if target foe was moving or knocked down.'],
854=>['Snare','When Snare is triggered, all nearby foes become Crippled for 3...15 seconds. Snare ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
858=>['Dancing Daggers','Send out three Dancing Daggers at target foe, each striking for 5...35 earth damage if they hit. Dancing Daggers has half the normal range. This skill counts as a lead attack.','Half Range Spell. Three projectiles: each deals 5...35 earth damage. Counts as a lead attack.'],
859=>['Conjure Nightmare','For 2...16 seconds, target foe suffers -8 Health degeneration.','(2...16 seconds.) Causes -8 Health degeneration.'],
860=>['Signet of Disruption','If target foe is casting a spell, the spell is interrupted and that foe suffers 10...51 damage. If that foe is hexed, Signet of Disruption can interrupt any non-spell skills.','Interrupts a spell. Can interrupt any skill if target foe is hexed. Interruption effect: deals 10...51 damage.'],
862=>['Ravenous Gaze','Deal 15...30 damage and steal 15...30 Health from target foe and all nearby foes.','Deals 15...30 damage and steals 15...30 Health from target and nearby foes.'],
863=>['Order of Apostasy','For 5 seconds, whenever a party member hits a foe with physical damage, that foe loses one enchantment. For each Monk enchantment removed, you lose 25...15% maximum Health.','Enchants all party members (5 seconds). These party members remove one enchantment when they deal physical damage. <gray>Removal cost: for each Monk enchantment, you lose 25...15% maximum Health.</gray>'],
864=>['Oppressive Gaze','Target foe and adjacent foes take 10...30 shadow damage. Foes already suffering from a condition are Poisoned and Weakened for 3...12 seconds.','Deals 10...30 damage to target and adjacent foes. Inflicts Poison and Weakness (3...12 second) on foes suffering from a condition.'],
865=>['Lightning Hammer','Target foe is struck for 10...100 lightning damage and applies<sic/> Cracked Armor for 5...20 seconds. Lightning Hammer has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...100 lightning damage. Applies Cracked Armor (5...20 seconds). 25% armor penetration.'],
866=>['Vapor Blade','Target foe is struck for 15...135 cold damage. Vapor Blade deals half damage if that foe has any enchantments on them.','Deals 15...135 cold damage. Half damage if target foe is enchanted.'],
867=>['Healing Light','Heal target ally for 40...100 Health. If your target has an enchantment, you gain 1...3 Energy.','Heals for 40...100. You gain 1...3 Energy if target ally is enchanted.'],
869=>['"Coward!"','If target foe is moving, that foe is knocked down.','Causes knock-down if target foe is moving.'],
870=>['Pestilence','Create a level 1...10 spirit. When any creature within its range dies, conditions on that creature spread to any creature in the area already suffering from a condition. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). When any creature in range dies, conditions on this creature spread to any creature in the area with a condition. Spirits are not affected.'],
871=>['Shadowsong','Create a level 1...10 spirit. The spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage and cause Blindness for 1...6 seconds. This spirit dies after 30 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30-second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and inflict Blindness condition (1...6 seconds).'],
876=>['Signet of Shadows','Target foe takes 5...35 damage. If your target was Blinded, that foe suffers an additional 15...60 damage.','Deals 5...35 damage. Deals 15...60 more damage if target foe is Blinded.'],
877=>['Lyssa\'s Balance','Target foe loses one Enchantment. If you have more Enchantments than target foe, this skill has no effect.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. <gray>No effect if you have more enchantments than this foe.</gray>'],
878=>['Visions of Regret','For 10 seconds, target foe and adjacent foes take 15...45 damage whenever they use a skill and 5...50 additional damage if not under the effects of another Mesmer hex.','Also hexes foes adjacent to target (10 seconds). These foes take 15...45 damage whenever they use a skill and 5...50 additional damage if not under the effects of another Mesmer hex.'],
879=>['Illusion of Pain','For 8 seconds, target foe has -3...10 Health degeneration and takes 3...10 damage each second. When Illusion of Pain ends, that foe is healed for 36...120.','(8 seconds.) Causes -3...10 Health degeneration and target foe takes 3...10 damage each second. End effect: that foe is healed for 36...120.'],
880=>['Stolen Speed','For 1...10 seconds, spells cast by the target foe and all adjacent foes take 100% longer to cast. Spells targeting these foes that are cast by you or your allies take 50% less time to cast.','Also hexes adjacent foes (1...10 seconds). Doubles spell casting time. Spells cast by you or your allies have -50% casting times.'],
881=>['Ether Signet','If you have less than 5...10 Energy, gain 10...20 Energy.','You gain 10...20 Energy. <gray>No effect unless you have less than 5...10 Energy.</gray>'],
882=>['Signet of Disenchantment','Lose all Energy. Target foe loses one enchantment.','Removes one enchantment. <gray>You lose all Energy.</gray>'],
883=>['Vocal Minority','For 5...20 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes cannot use shouts or chants.','Also hexes foes near target (5...20 seconds). These foes cannot use shouts or chants.'],
884=>['Searing Flames','Target foe and all nearby foes are struck with Searing Flames. Foes already on fire when this skill is cast are struck for 10...100 fire damage. Foes not already on fire begin Burning for 1...7 seconds.','Hits foes near your target. Deals 10...100 fire damage to foes already Burning. Inflicts Burning condition (1...7 seconds) to foes not Burning.'],
885=>['Shield Guardian','For 1...4 seconds, all party members in earshot have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks. If an attack is blocked, all allies in earshot are healed for 10...40 and Shield Guardian ends.','(1...4 seconds). Party members in earshot have a 75% chance to block attacks. Block effect: Allies in earshot are healed for 10...40, and Shield Guardian ends.'],
886=>['Restful Breeze','For 8...18 seconds, target ally has +10 Health regeneration. This enchantment ends if that ally attacks or uses a skill.','(8...18 seconds.) +10 Health regeneration. <gray>Ends if target ally attacks or uses a skill.</gray>'],
887=>['Signet of Rejuvenation','Heal target ally for 15...75. If target ally is casting a spell or attacking, that ally is healed for an additional 15...75 Health.','Heals for 15...75. Heals for 15...75 more if target ally is casting a spell or attacking.'],
888=>['Whirling Axe','If Whirling Axe hits, you strike for +5...20 damage and any stance being used by your target ends. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +5...20 damage and removes a stance. Unblockable.'],
889=>['Forceful Blow','If Forceful Blow hits, you strike for +10...30 damage and any stance being used by target foe ends. Target foe suffers from Weakness for 5...20 seconds. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...30 damage. Remove target foe\'s stance. Inflicts Weakness condition (5...20 seconds). Unblockable.'],
891=>['"None Shall Pass!"','All nearby foes that are moving are knocked down. This skill recharges 1...8 seconds faster for each foe knocked down (maximum 25 seconds).','Knocks down all nearby moving foes. Recharges 1...8 seconds faster for each affected foe (maximum 25 seconds).'],
892=>['Quivering Blade','If Quivering Blade hits, you strike for +10...40 damage. If this attack hits a moving foe, that foe is Dazed for 5 seconds.','Deals +10...40 damage. Inflicts Dazed condition (5 seconds) if target foe was moving.'],
893=>['Seeking Arrows','For 3...14 seconds, your arrows cannot be blocked. Seeking Arrows ends if you fail to hit.','(3...14 seconds.) Your arrows are unblockable. <gray>Ends if you fail to hit.</gray>'],
898=>['Overload','For 5 seconds, target foe suffers -1...3 Health degeneration. If target foe is using a skill, then Overload deals 15...75 damage to that foe and all adjacent foes.','(5 seconds.) Causes -1...3 Health degeneration. If target foe is using a skill, that foe and all adjacent foes take 15...75 damage.'],
899=>['Images of Remorse','For 5...10 seconds, target foe suffers -1...3 Health degeneration. If that foe was attacking, that foe takes 10...52 damage.','(5...10 seconds.) Causes -1...3 Health degeneration. Initial effect: 10...52 damage if target foe is attacking.'],
900=>['Shared Burden','For 5...20 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes attack, cast spells, and move 50% slower.','Also hexes foes near your target (5...20 seconds). These foes attack, cast spells, and move 50% slower.'],
901=>['Soul Bind','For 30 seconds, every time target foe is healed, the healer takes 20...80 damage. This hex ends if target is suffering from a Smiting Prayers hex.','(30 seconds.) Every time target foe is healed, the healer takes 20...80 damage. <gray>Ends if target is suffering from a Smiting Prayers hex.</gray>'],
902=>['Blood of the Aggressor','Steal up to 5...45 Health from target foe. If that foe was attacking, that foe suffers Weakness for 3...12 seconds.','Steal 5...45 Health. Inflicts Weakness (3...12 seconds) if target foe was attacking.'],
903=>['Icy Prism','Target foe is struck for 15...75 cold damage. If that foe has a Water Magic hex, Icy Prism deals +<sic/>15...75 cold damage to all other nearby foes.','Deals 15...75 cold damage. Deals +<sic/>15...75 cold damage to other nearby foes if target has a Water Magic hex.'],
904=>['Furious Axe','If Furious Axe hits, you strike for +5...35 damage. If it is blocked you gain 3 strikes worth of adrenaline.','Deals +5...35 damage. Gives you 3 strikes of adrenaline if blocked.'],
905=>['Auspicious Blow','If Auspicious Blow hits, you strike for +5...20 damage and gain 3...8 Energy. If target foe is suffering from Weakness, this attack is unblockable.','Deals +5...20 damage and you gain 3...8 Energy. Unblockable if target foe is Weakened.'],
906=>['"On Your Knees!"','Lose all adrenaline. If any adjacent foes are knocked down, all of your stances are recharged.','Recharges all your stances if you are adjacent to a knocked-down foe. <gray>You lose all adrenaline.</gray>'],
907=>['Dragon Slash','If Dragon Slash hits, you strike for +10...40 damage and gain 1...5 strikes of adrenaline.','Deals +10...40 damage. You gain 1...5 strikes of adrenaline if it hits.'],
908=>['Marauder\'s Shot','If Marauder\'s Shot hits, you strike for +10...35 damage and all your non-attack skills are disabled for 10 seconds.','Deals +10...35 damage. <gray>Your non-attack skills are disabled (10 seconds) if this attack hits.</gray>'],
909=>['Focused Shot','If Focused Shot hits, you strike for +10...25 damage but all of your other attack skills are disabled for 5...3 seconds.','Deals +10...25 damage. <gray>Your other attack skills are disabled (5...3 seconds) if this attack hits.</gray>'],
910=>['Spirit Rift','Open a Spirit Rift at target foe\'s location. After 3 seconds, all adjacent foes are struck for 25...125 lightning damage and suffer from Cracked Armor for 1...20 seconds.','After 3 seconds, affects foes adjacent to target\'s initial location. Deals 25...125 lightning damage and inflicts Cracked Armor (1...20 seconds).'],
911=>['Union','Create a level 1...12 spirit. Whenever a non-spirit ally in its range takes damage or life steal, it is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Whenever a non-spirit ally within range takes damage or life steal, it is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage.'],
913=>['Tranquil Was Tanasen','Hold Tanasen\'s ashes for up to 5...20 seconds. While you hold his ashes, you have +10...25 armor and cannot be interrupted.','(5...20 seconds.) You have +10...25 armor. You cannot be interrupted.'],
914=>['Consume Soul','You steal 5...60 Health from target foe. All hostile summoned creatures in the area of that foe take 25...125 damage.','Steals 5...60 Health. Deal 25...125 damage to hostile summoned creatures in the area of target foe.'],
915=>['Spirit Light','Target ally is healed for 60...180. If any spirits are within earshot, you don\'t sacrifice Health.','Heals for 60...180. You don\'t sacrifice Health if you are within earshot of any spirits.'],
916=>['Lamentation','For 5...20 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes suffer -0...3 Health degeneration. When this hex is applied, these foes take 10...50 damage if you are within earshot of a spirit or corpse.','Also hexes foes near your target (5...20 seconds). Causes -0...3 Health degeneration. Initial effect: Deals 10...50 damage to these foes if you are within earshot of a spirit or corpse.'],
917=>['Rupture Soul','Target allied spirit is destroyed. All nearby enemies are struck for 50...140 lightning damage and become blinded for 3...12 seconds.','Destroys target allied spirit. Deals 50...140 lightning damage and inflicts Blindness condition (3...12 seconds) to nearby foes.'],
918=>['Spirit to Flesh','Target touched allied spirit is destroyed. All nearby allies are healed for 30...240.','Touch Spell. Destroys target touched allied spirit. Heals nearby allies for 30...240.'],
919=>['Spirit Burn','Target foe is struck for 5...50 lightning damage. If any spirits are within earshot, Spirit Burn causes Burning for 1...5 seconds.','Deals 5...50 lightning damage. Inflicts Burning condition (1...5 seconds) if you are within earshot of a spirit.'],
920=>['Destruction','Create a level 1...14 Spirit that dies after 30 seconds. When this Spirit dies, all foes in the area take 5...25 damage for each second the Spirit was alive (maximum 150 damage).','Create a level 1...14 Spirit that dies after 30 seconds. When this Spirit dies, all foes in the area take 5...25 damage for each second the Spirit was alive (maximum 150 damage).'],
921=>['Dissonance','Create a level 1...12 spirit. This spirit deals 5...20 damage and anyone struck by its attack is interrupted. This spirit dies after 10...25 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (10...25 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and interrupt actions.'],
923=>['Disenchantment','Create a level 1...12 spirit. This spirit deals 5...20 damage and anyone struck by its attack loses one enchantment. This spirit dies after 10...35 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (10...35 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and remove one enchantment.'],
925=>['Recall','While you maintain Recall, nothing happens. When Recall ends, you Shadow Step to the ally you targeted when you activated this skill and all of your skills are disabled for 10 seconds.','End effect: Shadow Step to target ally. <gray>Cannot self-target and disables all of your skills for 10 seconds when it ends.</gray>'],
926=>['Sharpen Daggers','For 5...30 seconds, your dagger attacks cause Bleeding for 5...15 seconds.','(5...30 seconds.) Your dagger attacks inflict the Bleeding condition (5...15 seconds).'],
927=>['Shameful Fear','For 10 seconds, target foe moves 10% faster than normal. For each second, if that foe is moving, that foe takes 5...20 damage.','(10 seconds.) Target foe takes 5...20 damage each second while moving, but moves 10% faster.'],
928=>['Shadow Shroud','For 3...9 seconds, target foe cannot be the target of enchantments.','(3...9 seconds.) Target foe cannot be the target of enchantments.'],
929=>['Shadow of Haste','For 10...40 seconds you move 15% faster than normal. When Shadow of Haste ends, you shadow step to your original location.','(10...40 seconds.) You move 15% faster. End effect: return to your original location.'],
930=>['Auspicious Incantation','For 20 seconds, the next spell you cast is disabled for an additional 10...5 seconds, and you gain 110...200% of that spell\'s Energy cost.','(20 seconds.) Your next spell gives you 110...200% of its Energy cost. <gray>That spell takes 10...5 seconds longer to recharge.</gray>'],
931=>['Power Return','If target foe is casting a spell or chant, that skill is interrupted and target foe gains 10...5 Energy.','Interrupts a spell or chant. Interruption effect: target foe gains 10...5 Energy.'],
932=>['Complicate','If target foe is using a skill, that skill is interrupted and disabled for target foe and all foes in the area for an additional 5...12 seconds.','Interrupt a skill. Interruption effect: disables interrupted skill (+5...12 seconds) for target foe and all foes in the area.'],
933=>['Shatter Storm','Target foe loses all enchantments. For each enchantment removed this way, Shatter Storm is disabled for an additional 7 seconds.','Removes all enchantments. <gray>Removal cost: Shatter Storm is disabled for +7 seconds for each enchantment removed.</gray>'],
934=>['Unnatural Signet','Target foe takes 15...75 damage. If that foe is under the effects of a hex or enchantment, foes adjacent to your target take 5...50 damage.','Deals 15...75 damage. Deals 5...50 damage to other adjacent foes if the target is hexed or enchanted.'],
935=>['Rising Bile','For 20 seconds, this hex does nothing. When Rising Bile ends, that foe and all foes in the area take 1...6 damage for each second Rising Bile was in effect.','(20 seconds.) End effect: deals 1...6 damage for each second Rising Bile was in effect. Also damages other foes in the area.'],
936=>['Envenom Enchantments','Target foe loses one enchantment. For every remaining enchantment, target foe is poisoned for 3...10 seconds.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. Inflicts Poisoned condition (3...10 seconds for each remaining enchantment on that foe).'],
937=>['Shockwave','All foes in the area take 15...60 earth damage and are Weakened for 1...10 seconds. Nearby foes also take +15...60 earth damage and have Cracked Armor for 1...10 seconds. Adjacent foes suffer the previous effects, take +15...60 earth damage, and are Blinded for 1...10 seconds.','Foes in the area take 15...60 earth damage and are Weakened (1...10 seconds). Nearby foes also take +15...60 earth damage and have Cracked Armor (1...10 seconds). Adjacent foes also take +15...60 earth damage and are Blinded (1...10 seconds).'],
938=>['Ward of Stability','Create a Ward of Stability at your current location. For 10...25 seconds, non-spirit allies cannot be knocked down.','(10...25 seconds.) Allies in this ward cannot be knocked-down. <gray>Allied spirits are not affected.</gray>'],
939=>['Icy Shackles','For 1...10 seconds, target foe\'s movement speed is reduced by 66%. While under the effects of an enchantment, that foe\'s movement is reduced by 90%.','(1...10 seconds.) Target foe moves 66% slower. This foe moves 90% slower if enchanted.'],
941=>['Blessed Light','Heal target ally for 10...140 Health and remove one condition and one hex.','Heals for 10...140. Removes one condition and one hex.'],
942=>['Withdraw Hexes','Remove all hexes from target ally and all adjacent allies. This spell takes an additional 20...5 seconds to recharge for each hex removed in this way.','Removes all hexes. Also affects adjacent allies. <gray>Removal cost: +20...5 seconds recharge for each hex removed.</gray>'],
943=>['Extinguish','Remove one condition from each party member. Party members relieved of Burning are healed for 10...100 Health.','Affects all party members. Removes one condition. Party members relieved of Burning are healed for 10...100.'],
944=>['Signet of Strength','Your next 1...16 attacks deal +5 damage.','Your attacks deal +5 damage. <gray>Ends after 1...16 attacks.</gray>'],
946=>['Trapper\'s Focus','For 12...24 seconds, your trap skills are not easily interruptible and your Wilderness Survival attribute is increased by +0...2.','(12...24 seconds.) Your trap skills are no longer easy to interrupt. You gain +0...2 to your Wilderness Survival attribute.'],
947=>['Brambles','Create a level 1...10 Spirit. Non-Spirit creatures that are knocked down in its range take 5 damage and begin Bleeding for 5...20 seconds. This Spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Knocked-down creatures take 5 damage and begin Bleeding (5...20 seconds). Does not affect spirits.'],
948=>['Desperate Strike','If you have less than 50...80% Health, you deal +15...60 damage.','Deals +15...60 damage if you have less than 50...80% Health.'],
949=>['Way of the Fox','For 10...35 seconds, your next 1...6 attacks cannot be blocked.','(10...35 seconds.) Your attacks are unblockable. <gray>Ends after 1...6 attacks.</gray>'],
950=>['Shadowy Burden','For 3...15 seconds, target foe moves 25% slower and while target foe has no other hexes, that foe has 20 less armor against your attacks.','(3...15 seconds.) Target foe moves 25% slower and has 20 less armor against your attacks. <gray>Armor reduction only affects this foe while it has no other hexes.</gray>'],
951=>['Siphon Speed','For 5...15 seconds, target foe moves 33% slower and you move 33% faster. This spell has half the normal range. This spell recharges 50% faster if cast on a moving foe.','Half Range Hex Spell. (5...15 seconds.) Target foe moves 33% slower and you move 33% faster. Recharges 50% faster if cast on a moving foe.'],
952=>['Death\'s Charge','Shadow Step to target foe. If that foe has more Health than you, you are healed for 65...200.','You Shadow Step to target foe. You are healed for 65...200 if this foe has more Health than you.'],
953=>['Power Flux','If target foe is casting a spell or chant, that skill is interrupted and for 4...10 seconds, that foe has -2 Energy degeneration.','Interrupts a spell or chant. Interruption effect: -2 Energy degeneration (4...10 seconds).'],
954=>['Expel Hexes','Remove up to 2 Hexes from target ally.','Removes 2 hexes from target ally.'],
955=>['Rip Enchantment','Remove 1 enchantment from target foe. If an enchantment was removed, that foe suffers from Bleeding for 5...25 seconds.','Removes 1 enchantment. Removal effect: inflicts Bleeding (5...25 seconds).'],
957=>['Spell Shield','For 5...20 seconds, while you are casting spells, foes cannot target you with spells. When Spell Shield ends, all your skills are disabled for 10...5 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) While casting spells, you cannot be the target of spells. <gray>End effect: your skills are disabled (10...5 seconds).</gray>'],
958=>['Healing Whisper','Target other ally is healed for 40...100. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Spell. Heals for 40...100. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
959=>['Ethereal Light','Target ally is healed for 25...100. This spell is easily interrupted.','Heals for 25...100. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
960=>['Release Enchantments','Lose all enchantments. Each party member is healed for 5...35 Health for each Monk enchantment lost.','Removes all of your enchantments. Heals all party members for 5...35 for each Monk Enchantment removed.'],
961=>['Lacerate','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Bleeding creatures within its range suffer -2 Health degeneration. When this spirit dies, all non-spirit creatures within its range that have less than 90% Health begin Bleeding for 5...25 seconds. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Bleeding creatures in range have -2 Health degeneration. End effect: Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...25 seconds) on creatures in range that have less than 90% health. Does not affect spirits.'],
962=>['Spirit Transfer','The spirit nearest you loses 5...50 Health. Target ally is healed for 5 for each point of Health lost.','The spirit nearest you loses 5...50 Health. Heals target ally for 5 for each point of Health lost.'],
963=>['Restoration','Create a level 1...14 spirit. When this spirit dies, all party members in the area are resurrected with 5...50% Health and zero Energy. This spirit dies after 30 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (30 second lifespan). End effect: resurrects party members in the area with 5...50% Health and zero Energy.'],
964=>['Vengeful Weapon','For 8 seconds, the next time target ally takes damage or life steal from a foe, that ally steals up to 15...60 Health from that foe.','(8 seconds.) Steals 15...60 Health from the next foe that deals damage or life steal to target ally.'],
973=>['Blinding Powder','Must follow an off-hand attack. Target foe and all adjacent foes become Blinded for 3...15 seconds.','Inflicts Blindness condition (3...15 seconds) on target and adjacent foes. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
974=>['Mantis Touch','Must follow a lead attack. Target foe becomes Crippled for 5...20 seconds. This skill counts as an off-hand attack.','Inflicts Crippled condition (5...20 seconds). This skill counts as an off-hand attack. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
975=>['Exhausting Assault','Must follow a lead attack. Target foe\'s action is interrupted. If that action was casting a spell, target foe suffers 10 Overcast.','Interrupts an action. Inflicts 10 Overcast if the interrupted action was a spell. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
976=>['Repeating Strike','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...30 damage. If it misses, it takes an additional 15 seconds to recharge.','Deals +10...30 damage. <gray>This skill has +15 second recharge time if it misses. Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
977=>['Way of the Lotus','For 20 seconds, the next time you hit with a dual attack skill, you gain 5...20 Energy.','(20 seconds.) You gain 5...20 Energy the next time you hit with a dual attack.'],
978=>['Mark of Instability','For 20 seconds, the next time you hit target foe with a dual attack skill that foe is knocked down.','(20 seconds.) Causes knock-down the next time you hit target foe with a dual attack.'],
979=>['Mistrust','For 6 seconds, the next spell that target foe casts on one of your allies fails and deals 10...100 damage to that foe and all nearby foes.','(6 seconds.) The next spell that target foe casts on one of your allies fails and deals 10...100 damage to target and nearby foes.'],
980=>['Feast of Souls','Destroy all nearby allies\' spirits. For each spirit destroyed in this way, all party members are healed for 50...100 Health.','Heals all party members for 50...100 for each nearby allied spirit. <gray>All nearby allied spirits are destroyed.</gray>'],
981=>['Recuperation','Create a level 1...14 spirit. Non-spirit allies within its range gain +1...3 Health regeneration. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range have +1...3 Health regeneration.'],
982=>['Shelter','Create a level 1...12 spirit. Non-spirit allies within its range cannot lose more than 10% maximum Health from a single attack. When this spirit prevents damage, it loses 75...45 Health. This spirit lasts 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range cannot lose more than 10% maximum Health from a single attack. <gray>Damage prevention cost: this spirit loses 75...45 Health.</gray>'],
983=>['Weapon of Shadow','For 1...7 seconds, target ally has a Weapon of Shadow. Whenever that ally is struck by an attack, that ally\'s attacker becomes Blinded for 5 seconds. The next 1...3 times <sic/> that ally hits with an attack, his target is Blinded for 5 seconds.','(1...7 seconds.) Inflicts Blindness condition (5 seconds) on anyone who attacks target ally. Target ally\'s next 1...3 attacks inflict Blindness (5 seconds) if they hit.'],
985=>['Caltrops','Target foe and all foes adjacent to your target are Crippled for 5...15 seconds. Caltrops has half the normal range.','Half Range Spell. Inflicts Crippled condition (5...15 seconds) on target and adjacent foes.'],
986=>['Nine Tail Strike','Must follow an off-hand attack. Nine Tail Strike cannot be blocked and strikes for +15...40 damage if it hits.','Deals +15...40 damage. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
987=>['Way of the Empty Palm','For 5...20 seconds, off-hand and dual attacks cost no Energy.','(5...20 seconds.) Your off-hand and dual attacks cost no Energy.'],
988=>['Temple Strike','Must follow a lead attack. If this attack hits, target foe is Dazed and Blinded for 1...10 seconds, and if target foe is casting a spell, that foe is interrupted.','Interrupts a spell. Inflicts Dazed and Blindness conditions (1...10 seconds). <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
989=>['Golden Phoenix Strike','If you are not under the effects of an enchantment, this skill misses. If it hits, Golden Phoenix Strike deals +10...30 damage and all adjacent foes take 10...30 damage.','Deals +10...30 damage to target and deals 10...30 damage to adjacent foes. <gray>Fails if you are not enchanted.</gray>'],
990=>['Expunge Enchantments','Target foe loses 1 enchantment. All of your other non-attack skills are disabled for 10...5 seconds. For each skill disabled in this way, target touched foe loses 1 additional enchantment.','Removes one enchantment for each non-attack skill you have. <gray>All your non-attack skills are disabled (10...5 seconds).</gray>'],
991=>['Deny Hexes','Remove one hex from target ally and one additional hex for each recharging Divine Favor skill you have.','Removes one hex from target ally and one additional hex for each recharging Divine Favor skill you have.'],
992=>['Triple Chop','Attack target foe and adjacent foes. Each attack that hits deals +10...40 damage.','Deals +10...40 damage. Also hits adjacent foes.'],
993=>['Enraged Smash','If Enraged Smash hits, you gain 1...4 strikes of adrenaline. If you hit a moving foe, you strike for +10...40 damage, and target foe is knocked down.','Gives you 1...4 strikes of adrenaline if you hit. Deals +10...40 damage and causes knockdown if target foe was moving.'],
994=>['Renewing Smash','If Renewing Smash hits, it deals +10...40 damage. If you hit a knocked-down foe, you gain 3 Energy and this attack recharges instantly.','Deals +10...40 damage. You gain 3 Energy and this attack recharges instantly if target foe was knocked down.'],
995=>['Tiger Stance','For 4...10 seconds, you attack 33% faster. Tiger Stance ends if any of your attacks fail to hit.','(4...10 seconds.) You attack 33% faster. <gray>Ends if you fail to hit.</gray>'],
996=>['Standing Slash','If it hits, Standing Slash deals +5...20 damage plus an additional 5...20 damage if you are in a stance.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals 5...20 more damage if you are in a stance.'],
997=>['Famine','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Whenever a non-spirit creature in its range reaches 0 Energy, that creature takes 10...35 damage. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...90 lifespan). Deals 10...35 damage to creatures in range that reach 0 energy. Does not affect spirits.'],
1018=>['Critical Eye','For 10...35 seconds, you have an additional 3...15% chance to land a critical hit when attacking. You gain 1 Energy whenever you score a critical hit.','(10...35 seconds.) You have +3...15% chance to land a critical hit. You gain 1 Energy whenever you land a critical hit.'],
1019=>['Critical Strike','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...30 damage, results in a critical hit, and you gain 1...3 Energy.','Deals +10...30 damage. Automatic critical hit. You gain 1...3 Energy. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
1020=>['Blades of Steel','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +5...16 damage (maximum bonus 60) for each recharging dagger attack.','Deals +5...16 damage (maximum 60) for each recharging dagger attack. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
1021=>['Jungle Strike','Must follow a lead attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...25 damage. If it hits a foe that was Crippled, that foe and all adjacent foes take +1...31 damage.','Deals +10...25 damage. Deals +1...31 damage to target and adjacent foes if target foe is Crippled. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
1022=>['Wild Strike','Must follow a lead attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...35 damage and any stance being used by target foe ends. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...35 damage. Removes target foe\'s stance. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
1023=>['Leaping Mantis Sting','If Mantis Sting hits, target foe takes +5...15 damage. If this attack strikes a moving foe, that foe is Crippled for 3...15 seconds.','Deals +5...15 damage. Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds) if target foe is moving.'],
1024=>['Black Mantis Thrust','If this attack hits, you strike for +8...20 damage. If target foe is suffering from a Hex, that foe is Crippled for 3...15 seconds.','Deals +8...20 damage. Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds) if target foe is hexed.'],
1025=>['Disrupting Stab','If this attack hits, it interrupts target foe\'s action. If that action was a spell, it is disabled for 3...10 seconds.','Interrupts an action. If the interrupted action was a spell, it is disabled (3...10 seconds).'],
1026=>['Golden Lotus Strike','If it hits, this attack strikes for +5...20 damage. If you are under the effects of an Enchantment, you gain 5...8 Energy.','Deals +5...20 damage. You gain 5...8 Energy if you are enchanted.'],
1027=>['Critical Defenses','For 4...10 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block. Critical Defenses refreshes every time you land a critical hit.','(4...10 seconds.) You have a 75% chance to block. Renewal: every time you land a critical hit.'],
1028=>['Way of Perfection','For 60 seconds, whenever you successfully land a critical hit, you gain 10...40 Health.','(60 seconds.) Your critical hits heal you for 10...40.'],
1029=>['Dark Apostasy','For 3...17 seconds, every time you successfully land a critical hit, you remove one enchantment from your target. If you remove an enchantment in this way, you lose 10...4 Energy or Dark Apostasy ends.','(3...17 seconds.) Your critical hits remove an enchantment. <gray>Removal cost: lose 10...4 Energy or Dark Apostasy ends.</gray>'],
1030=>['Locust\'s Fury','For 10...35 seconds, you have an additional 50% chance to double strike while using daggers.','(10...35 seconds.) You have +50% chance to double strike. <gray>No effect unless you are wielding daggers.</gray>'],
1031=>['Shroud of Distress','For 30...60 seconds, if you are below 50% Health, you have 3...8 health regeneration and a 75% chance to block attacks.','(30...60 seconds.) You have 3...8 health regeneration and a 75% chance to block. <gray>No effect unless your Health is below 50%.</gray>'],
1032=>['Heart of Shadow','You are healed for 30...150. Shadow Step to a nearby location directly away from your target.','You are healed for 30...150 and you Shadow Step to a nearby location directly away from your target.'],
1033=>['Impale','Must follow a dual attack. Target foe is struck for 25...100 earth damage and suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals 25...100 earth damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>Must follow a dual attack.</gray>'],
1034=>['Seeping Wound','For 1...7 seconds, target foe moves 33% slower. That foe takes 5...25 damage each second while suffering from a condition. This spell has half the normal range.','Elite Half Range Hex Spell. (1...7 seconds.) Target foe moves 33% slower. This foe takes 5...25 damage each second while suffering from a condition.'],
1035=>['Assassin\'s Promise','For 5...15 seconds, if target foe dies, you gain 5...20 Energy and all your skills are recharged.','(5...15 seconds.) You gain 5...20 Energy and all your skills recharge if target foe dies.'],
1036=>['Signet of Malice','For each condition suffered by target foe, you lose one condition.','You lose one condition for each condition on target foe.'],
1037=>['Dark Escape','For 5...15 seconds, you move 25% faster and take half damage. Dark Escape ends if you successfully hit with an attack.','(5...15 seconds.) You move 25% faster and take half damage. <gray>Ends if you hit with an attack.</gray>'],
1038=>['Crippling Dagger','Send out a Crippling Dagger at target foe. Crippling Dagger strikes for 15...60 earth damage if it hits, and Cripples moving foes for 3...15 seconds. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Spell. Projectile: deals 15...60 earth damage. Inflicts Crippled condition (3...15 seconds) if target foe is moving.'],
1040=>['Spirit Walk','Shadow Step to target spirit.','Shadow Step to target Spirit. <sic/>'],
1041=>['Unseen Fury','All adjacent foes are Blinded for 3...10 seconds. For 10...30 seconds, you cannot be blocked by Blinded foes.','Inflicts Blindness condition on adjacent foes (3...10). You cannot be blocked by Blinded foes for 10...30 seconds.'],
1042=>['Flashing Blades','For 5...30 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks while attacking. If you block an attack in this way, your attacker takes 5...20 damage.','(5...30 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block while attacking. Block effect: 5...20 damage to your attacker.'],
1043=>['Dash','For 3 seconds, you run 50% faster.','(3 seconds.) You move 50% faster.'],
1044=>['Dark Prison','Shadow Step to target foe. For 1...6 seconds, that foe moves 33% slower.','Shadow Step to target foe. This foe moves 33% slower (1...6 seconds).'],
1045=>['Palm Strike','Target touched foe takes 10...65 damage and is Crippled for 1...5 seconds. This skill counts as an off-hand attack.','Deals 10...65 damage and inflicts Crippled condition (1...5 seconds). This skill counts as an off-hand attack.'],
1048=>['Revealed Enchantment','Remove an enchantment from target foe and gain 3...15 Energy. For 20 seconds, Revealed Enchantment is replaced with the enchantment removed from target foe.','Removes an enchantment from target foe. Removal effects: you gain 3...15 Energy; this spell is replaced with that enchantment (20 seconds).'],
1049=>['Revealed Hex','Remove a hex from target ally and gain 4...10 Energy. For 20 seconds, Revealed Hex is replaced with the hex that was removed.','Removes a hex from target ally. Removal effects: you gain 4...10 Energy; this spell is replaced with that hex (20 seconds).'],
1052=>['Accumulated Pain','Target foe takes 15...75 damage. If target foe is suffering from 2 or more hexes, that foe suffers a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals 15...75 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe has 2 or more hexes.'],
1053=>['Psychic Distraction','All of your other skills are disabled for 8 seconds. If target foe is using a skill, that skill is interrupted and disabled for an additional 5...12 seconds.','Interrupts a skill. Interruption effect: disables interrupted skill (+5...12 seconds). <gray>Your other skills are disabled (8 seconds).</gray>'],
1054=>['Ancestor\'s Visage','For 4...10 seconds, whenever target ally is hit by a melee attack, all adjacent foes lose all adrenaline and 3 Energy.','(4...10 seconds.) All adjacent foes lose all adrenaline and 3 Energy whenever a melee attack hits target ally.'],
1055=>['Recurring Insecurity','For 10 seconds, target foe suffers from -1...5 Health degeneration. If that foe has another hex when Recurring Insecurity would end, it is reapplied.','(10 seconds.) Causes -1...5 Health degeneration. Renewal: if target foe has another hex when Recurring Insecurity would end.'],
1056=>['Kitah\'s Burden','For 10 seconds, target foe moves 50% slower. When Kitah\'s Burden ends you gain 10...18 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Target foe moves 50% slower. End effect: you gain 10...18 Energy.'],
1057=>['Psychic Instability','Interrupt the target foe\'s action. If that action was a skill, that foe and nearby foes are knocked down for 2...4 seconds. (50% failure chance with Fast Casting 4 or less.)','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: if the action is a skill, cause knockdown for 2...4 seconds on target foe and all nearby foes. <gray>50% failure chance unless Fast Casting 5 or higher.</gray>'],
1059=>['Hex Eater Signet','Target touched ally and up to 2...5 adjacent allies each lose one hex. You gain 1...4 Energy for each hex removed this way.','Touch Signet. Removes a hex from target and 2...5 adjacent allies. Removal effect: you gain 1...4 Energy for each hex removed.'],
1061=>['Feedback','Target foe loses one enchantment. If an enchantment is removed in this way, that foe also loses 4...10 Energy.','Removes one enchantment. Removal effect: target foe loses 4...10 Energy.'],
1062=>['Arcane Larceny','For 5...35 seconds, one random spell is disabled for target foe and Arcane Larceny is replaced by that spell.','(5...35 seconds.) Disables one random spell. This skill becomes that spell.'],
1066=>['Spoil Victor','For 3...15 seconds, whenever target foe attacks or casts a spell on a creature with less Health, that foe loses 25...100 Health.','(3...15 seconds.) Causes 25...100 Health loss whenever target foe attacks or casts spells on a creature with less Health.'],
1067=>['Lifebane Strike','Target foe takes 12...48 shadow damage. If that foe\'s Health is above 50%, you steal up to 12...48 Health.','Deals 12...48 damage. Steals 12...48 Health if target foe\'s Health is above 50%.'],
1068=>['Bitter Chill','Target foe is struck for 15...60 cold damage. If that foe had more Health than you, Bitter Chill recharges instantly.','Deals 15...60 cold damage. Recharges instantly if target foe had more Health than you.'],
1069=>['Taste of Pain','If target foe is below 50% Health, you gain 30...150 Health.','Heals you for 30...150. <gray>No effect unless target foe is below 50% Health.</gray>'],
1070=>['Defile Enchantments','Target foe and all nearby foes take 6...60 shadow damage and 4...20 shadow damage for each enchantment on them.','Deals 6...60 damage to target and nearby foes. Deals 4...20 more damage for each enchantment on them.'],
1071=>['Shivers of Dread','For 10...40 seconds, whenever target foe is struck for cold damage while using a skill, that foe is interrupted and you lose 10...5 Energy or Shivers of Dread ends.','(10...40 seconds.) Cold damage interrupts target foe\'s skills. <gray>Interruption cost: you lose 10...5 Energy or this hex ends.</gray>'],
1075=>['Vampiric Swarm','Vampiric Swarm steals up to 15...60 Health from up to three foes in the area.','Steals 15...60 Health. Hits 2 additional foes in the area.'],
1076=>['Blood Drinker','If your Health is above 50%, you begin Bleeding for 10 seconds. Steal up to 20...65 Health from target foe.','Steals 20...65 Health. <gray>You begin Bleeding (10 seconds) if your Health is above 50%.</gray>'],
1077=>['Vampiric Bite','Touch target foe to steal up to 29...74 Health.','Steals 29...74 Health.'],
1078=>['Wallow\'s Bite','Target touched foe takes 20...58 damage.','Deals 20...58 damage.'],
1079=>['Enfeebling Touch','Target touched foe loses 5...50 Health and suffers from Weakness for 5...20 seconds.','Causes 5...50 Health loss. Inflicts Weakness condition (5...20 seconds).'],
1081=>['Teinai\'s Wind','Target foe and all adjacent foes take 10...40 cold damage. Burning foes struck by Teinai\'s Wind take an additional 40...80 damage and are interrupted.','Deals 10...40 cold damage. Burning foes take +40...80 damage and are interrupted. Also strikes adjacent.'],
1082=>['Shock Arrow','Send out a shocking arrow that flies swiftly toward target foe, striking for 5...50 lightning damage. If Shock Arrow strikes a foe suffering from Cracked Armor, you gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage. Shock Arrow has 25% armor penetration.','Rapid projectile: deals 5...50 lightning damage. Gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage if you hit a foe suffering from Cracked Armor. 25% armor penetration.'],
1083=>['Unsteady Ground','You create Unsteady Ground at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, nearby foes take 10...40 earth damage each second. Attacking foes struck by Unsteady Ground are knocked down.','Deals 10...40 earth damage each second (5 seconds) and causes knock-down to attacking foes. Hits foes near target\'s initial location.'],
1084=>['Sliver Armor','For 5...11 seconds, you have 25...50% chance to block attacks and whenever you are the target of a hostile spell or attack one nearby foe is struck for 5...35 earth damage.','(5...11 seconds.) You have 25...50% chance to block. Deals 5...35 earth damage to one nearby foe whenever you are the target of a hostile spell or attack.'],
1085=>['Ash Blast','Target and adjacent foes are struck for 35...65 earth damage. Burning foes struck by Ash Blast are hexed for 5 seconds and have a 20...75% chance to miss with attacks.','Deals 35...65 earth damage. Burning foes are hexed for 5 seconds and miss 20...75% of attacks. Also strikes adjacent.'],
1086=>['Dragon\'s Stomp','You invoke a Dragon\'s Stomp at target foe\'s location. All foes near this location are knocked down and are struck for 26...100 earth damage.','Deals 26...100 earth damage. Causes knock-down. Also hits foes near this foe.'],
1088=>['Second Wind','You gain 1 Energy and 5 Health for each point of Energy restricted by Overcast. You lose all enchantments.','You gain 1 Energy and 5 Health for each point of Overcast. You lose all enchantments.'],
1090=>['Smoldering Embers','Target foe is struck for 10...70 fire damage. If you are Overcast, that foe is hexed with Smoldering Embers for 3 seconds and takes 5...25 additional fire damage each second.','Deals 10...70 fire damage to target. If you are Overcast, foe is hexed for 3 seconds, taking 5...25 fire damage each second.'],
1091=>['Double Dragon','Invoke the power of the Dragon. For 8 seconds, you and target ally are enchanted with Double Dragon. Adjacent foes are dealt 5...30 fire damage each second. Additionally, when you or your ally use skills that target a foe, that foe is set on fire for 0...3 seconds.','(8 seconds.) Enchants you and target ally. Adjacent foes take 5...30 fire damage each second. Skills that target a foe also inflict Burning (0...3 seconds).'],
1093=>['Teinai\'s Heat','Place a ward of Teinai\'s Heat at your location for 10...15 seconds. Foes within the ward suffer 2...5 health <sic/> degeneration. Weakened foes attack 33% slower. This skill is disabled for 20 seconds.','(10...15 seconds.) Causes 2...5 health <sic/> degeneration. Weakened foes in the ward attack 33% slower. Disabled for 20 seconds.'],
1094=>['Breath of Fire','Create Breath of Fire at target foe\'s current location. For 5 seconds, foes adjacent to that location are struck for 10...40 fire damage each second.','Deals 10...40 fire damage each second (5 seconds). Hits foes adjacent to target\'s initial location.'],
1095=>['Star Burst','Target touched foe and all foes in the area are struck for 7...112 fire damage and set on fire for 1...4 seconds. For each foe you hit, gain 2 Energy.','Elite Touch Spell. Deals 7...112 fire damage. Inflicts Burning (1...4 seconds). <sic/> Gain 2 Energy for each foe struck. Also hits foes in the area.'],
1096=>['Glyph of Essence','For 15 seconds, your next spell casts instantly but causes you to lose all Energy.','(15 seconds.) Your next spell casts instantly. <gray>You lose all Energy.</gray>'],
1097=>['Teinai\'s Prison','For 1...6 seconds, target foe\'s legs are encased in ice, causing the foe to move 66% slower. If that foe has Cracked Armor, the chill seeps through causing -5...9 Health degeneration.','(1...6 seconds.) Target foe moves 66% slower. Foes with Cracked Armor have -5...9 Health degeneration.'],
1098=>['Mirror of Ice','Shatter a Mirror of Ice. All foes near you and target ally take 15...70 cold damage and move 66% slower for 2...6 seconds. If you strike a foe hexed with Water Magic, Mirror of Ice recharges 50% faster.','Deals 15...70 cold damage and slows foes by 66% (2...6 seconds). Hits foes near you and target ally. Recharges 50% faster if it hits a foe hexed with Water Magic.'],
1099=>['Teinai\'s Crystals','Target foe takes 20...40 damage. If target foe has a Water Magic hex, this spell strikes target and nearby foes for an additional 20...40 damage, and nearby foes also suffer Cracked Armor for 5...15 seconds.','Deals 20...40 damage to target. Deals +20...40 more <sic/> damage and causes Cracked Armor (5...15 seconds) nearby if that foe had a Water Magic hex.'],
1113=>['Kirin\'s Wrath','For 5 seconds, foes adjacent to the location in which the spell was cast take 8...32 holy damage each second.','Deals 8...32 holy damage each second (5 seconds). Hits foes adjacent to your initial location.'],
1114=>['Spirit Bond','For 8 seconds, whenever target ally takes more than 50 damage from the next 10 attacks or spells, that ally is healed for 30...90 Health.','(8 seconds.) Heals for 30...90 whenever target ally takes more than 50 damage. <gray>Ends after this ally takes damage from 10 attacks or spells.</gray>'],
1115=>['Air of Enchantment','For 4...10 seconds, enchantments cast on target other ally cost 5 less Energy (minimum 1 Energy).','(4...10 seconds.) Enchantments cast on target ally cost 5 less Energy (minimum 1 Energy). <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1117=>['Heaven\'s Delight','Heals you and party members within earshot for 15...60 points.','Heals you and party members within earshot for 15...60 points.'],
1118=>['Healing Burst','Target ally is healed for 10...160. All party members in earshot of your target gain Health equal to the Divine Favor bonus from this spell. Your Smiting Prayers are disabled for 20 seconds.','Heals for 10...160. Party members in earshot of your target gain Health equal to the Divine Favor bonus. <gray>Disables your Smiting Prayers (20 seconds).</gray>'],
1119=>['Karei\'s Healing Circle','Heal yourself and all adjacent creatures for 30...180 points.','Heals you for 30...180. Also heals adjacent creatures.'],
1120=>['Jamei\'s Gaze','Heal target other ally for 35...180 Health.','Heals for 35...180. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1121=>['Gift of Health','All of your other Healing Prayers skills are disabled for 10...5 seconds. Target other ally is healed for 15...150 Health.','Heals for 15...150. <gray>Disables your other Healing Prayers skills (10...5 seconds). Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1123=>['Life Sheath','Remove 0...2 conditions from target ally. For 8 seconds, the next time that ally would take damage or life steal, that ally gains that amount of Health instead (maximum 20...100).','(8 seconds.) Converts the next incoming damage or life steal (maximum 20...100) to healing. Initial effect: Removes 0...2 conditions.'],
1126=>['Empathic Removal','You and target other ally lose 1 condition and 1 hex, and are healed for 50.','Removes one condition and hex from target ally and yourself, and heals for 50. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1128=>['Resurrection Chant','Resurrect target party member with up to your current Health and 5...35% Energy. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Spell. Resurrects target party member at your current Health and with 5...35% Energy.'],
1129=>['Word of Censure','Target foe takes 15...75 holy damage. If your target was below 33% Health, Word of Censure takes 20 additional seconds to recharge.','Deals 15...75 holy damage. <gray>+20 recharge time if target foe is below 33% Health.</gray>'],
1130=>['Spear of Light','Spear of Light flies toward target foe and deals 26...56 holy damage if it hits. Spear of Light deals +15...60 damage if it hits an attacking foe.','Projectile: deals 26...56 holy damage. Deals 15...60 more damage if target foe is attacking.'],
1131=>['Stonesoul Strike','Touched target foe takes 10...55 holy damage. If knocked down, your target takes an additional 10...55 holy damage.','Deals 10...55 holy damage. Deals 10...55 more holy damage if target is knocked down.'],
1133=>['Drunken Blow','If this attack hits, you strike for +10...40 damage and your target suffers from one of the following conditions: Deep Wound (for 20 seconds), Weakness (for 20 seconds), Bleeding (for 25 seconds), or Crippled (for 15 seconds). After making a Drunken Blow, you are knocked down.','Deals +10...40 damage. Inflicts one of the following random conditions: Deep Wound (20 seconds), Weakness (20 seconds), Bleeding (25 seconds), or Crippled (15 seconds). <gray>You are knocked-down.</gray>'],
1134=>['Leviathan\'s Sweep','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. If this attack is blocked, your target is knocked down and suffers 10...34 damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Causes knock-down and deals 10...34 damage if blocked.'],
1135=>['Jaizhenju Strike','If Jaizhenju Strike hits, you strike for +1...30 damage. If you are not using a stance, Jaizhenju Strike cannot be blocked.','Deals +1...30 damage. Unblockable unless you are in a stance.'],
1136=>['Penetrating Chop','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. This axe attack has 20% armor penetration.','Deals +5...20 damage. 20% armor penetration.'],
1137=>['Yeti Smash','Lose all adrenaline. Attack all adjacent foes. If this attack strikes a foe suffering from a condition, that foe is knocked down. (50% failure chance with Hammer Mastery 4 or less.)','Attack all adjacent foes. Knocks down foes suffering from a condition. <gray>You lose all adrenaline. 50% failure chance unless Hammer Mastery is 5 or more.</gray>'],
1141=>['"You Will Die!"','If target foe is below 50% Health, you gain 1...3 strikes of adrenaline.','You gain 1...3 strikes of adrenaline. <gray>No effect unless target foe is under 50% Health.</gray>'],
1142=>['Auspicious Parry','For 8 seconds, the next attack against you is blocked. You gain 1...4 strikes of adrenaline when this stance ends.','(8 seconds.) Blocks one attack. End effect: you gain 1...4 strikes of adrenaline.'],
1144=>['Silverwing Slash','This attack strikes for +1...40 damage if it hits.','Deals +1...40 damage.'],
1146=>['Shove','Target touched foe is knocked down. If that foe was moving, that foe\'s stance ends and that foe takes 15...75 damage before being knocked down.','Causes knockdown. Initial effect: ends foe\'s stance and deals 15...75 damage if target foe is moving.'],
1191=>['Sundering Attack','If Sundering Attack hits, you strike for +5...25 damage and this attack has 10% armor penetration.','Deals +5...25 damage. 10% armor penetration.'],
1192=>['Zojun\'s Shot','Shoot an arrow that has half the normal range, but strikes for +10...40 damage.','Half Range Bow Attack. Deals +10...40 damage.'],
1194=>['Predatory Bond','For 5...20 seconds, your animal companion attacks 25% faster and heals you for 1...31 Health with each successful attack.','(5...20 seconds.) Your pet attacks 25% faster and you gain 1...31 Health whenever your pet makes a successful attack.'],
1195=>['Heal as One','For 15 seconds, your animal companion steals 1...20 Health whenever it hits with an attack. You and your companion are both healed for 20...104 Health. If your companion is dead, it\'s resurrected with 50% Health. If you have this skill equipped, your companion will travel with you.','(15 seconds.) Your pet\'s attacks steal 1...20 Health. Initial effect: heals you and your pet for 20...104; resurrects your pet (50% Health) if dead. If you have this equipped, your pet will travel with you.'],
1196=>['Zojun\'s Haste','For 5...11 seconds, you move 33% faster and have a 27...75% chance to block incoming projectiles. Zojun\'s Haste ends if you attack.','(5...11 seconds.) You move 33% faster and have 27...75% chance to block projectiles. <gray>Ends if you attack.</gray>'],
1197=>['Needling Shot','Needling Shot strikes for only 10...30 damage and moves faster than normal. If Needling Shot strikes a foe below 50% Health, Needling Shot recharges instantly. Your other attack skills are disabled for 2 seconds.','Fast-moving arrow. Deals 10...30 damage. Recharges instantly if target foe is below 50% Health. <gray>Your other attack skills are disabled (2 seconds).</gray>'],
1198=>['Broad Head Arrow','You shoot a broad head arrow that moves slower than normal. If it hits, target foe is Dazed for 5...20 seconds, and if target foe is casting a spell that spell is interrupted.','Slow moving arrow. Interrupts a spell. Inflicts Dazed condition (5...20 seconds).'],
1199=>['Glass Arrows','For 10...35 seconds, your arrows strike for +5...20 damage if they hit and cause Bleeding for 10...20 seconds if they are blocked.','(10...35 seconds.) Your arrows deal +5...20 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition if blocked (10...20 seconds).'],
1200=>['Archer\'s Signet','For 1...24 seconds, conditions you apply while wielding a bow last 100% longer.','(1...24 seconds.) Conditions you apply while wielding a bow last 100% longer.'],
1201=>['Savage Pounce','Your animal companion attempts a Savage Pounce that deals +5...20 damage. If the attack strikes a foe who is casting a spell, that foe is knocked down.','Deals +5...20 damage. Causes knock-down if target foe is casting a spell.'],
1202=>['Enraged Lunge','Your animal companion attempts an Enraged Lunge that applies a Deep Wound to target foe for 5...20 seconds and deals +10...50 damage.','Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) and deals +10...50 damage.'],
1203=>['Bestial Mauling','Your animal companion attempts a Bestial Mauling that deals +5...20 damage. If the attack strikes a knocked-down foe, that foe is Dazed for 4...10 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Dazed condition (4...10 seconds) if target foe is knocked-down.'],
1205=>['Poisonous Bite','Your animal companion attempts a Poisonous Bite that Poisons target foe for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds).'],
1206=>['Pounce','Your animal companion\'s next attack is a Pounce that deals +5...20 damage. If the attack strikes a moving foe, that foe is knocked down.','Deals +5...20 damage. Causes knock-down if target foe is moving.'],
1209=>['Bestial Fury','All your non-attack skills are disabled for 5 seconds. For 5...11 seconds, you attack 25% faster.','(5...11 seconds.) You attack 25% faster. <gray>Your non-attack skills are disabled (5 seconds).</gray>'],
1211=>['Viper\'s Nest','Create a Viper\'s Nest. When it is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 5...35 piercing damage and become Poisoned for 5...20 seconds. Viper\'s Nest expires after 90 seconds. This Trap is easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 5...35 piercing damage. Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
1212=>['Equinox','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Spells cast within its range that cause Overcast cause an additional 10 Overcast. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Overcast-causing spells cast within range cause an additional 10 Overcast.'],
1213=>['Tranquility','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Enchantments cast by non-spirit creatures within its range expire 20...50% faster. This spirit dies after 15...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...60 second lifespan). Enchantments expire 20...50% faster on creatures in range. Does not affect spirits.'],
1215=>['Clamor of Souls','Target foe and all nearby foes take 10...65 lightning damage. If you are within earshot of a spirit or holding a bundle item, you gain 10 Energy.','Deals 10...65 lightning damage to target and nearby foes. You gain 10 Energy if you are within earshot of a spirit or holding a bundle item.'],
1217=>['Ritual Lord','For 5...35 seconds, your Ritualist attributes are boosted by 2...4 for your next skill. If that skill is a Binding Ritual, it recharges 10...60% faster and Ritual Lord recharges instantly.','(5...35 seconds.) You have +2...4 to all Ritualist attributes for your next skill. If that skill is a Binding Ritual, it recharges 10...60% faster and Ritual Lord recharges instantly.'],
1218=>['Cruel Was Daoshen','Hold Daoshen\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. While you hold his ashes, all Ritualist skills have 10% armor penetration. When you drop his ashes, all nearby foes are struck for 15...85 lightning damage.','(15...60 seconds.) Your Ritualist skills have 10% armor penetration. Drop effect: deals 15...85 lightning damage to all nearby foes.'],
1219=>['Protective Was Kaolai','Hold Kaolai\'s ashes for up to 15...60 seconds. While you hold his ashes, you gain 10 armor. When you drop his ashes, all party members are healed for 10...85 Health.','(15...60 seconds.) You have +10 armor. Drop effect: all party members are healed for 10...85.'],
1220=>['Attuned Was Songkai','Hold Songkai\'s ashes for up to 45 seconds. While you hold her ashes, your spells and binding rituals cost 5...50% of the base Energy to cast.','(45 seconds.) Your spells and binding rituals cost 5...50% of the base Energy.'],
1221=>['Resilient Was Xiko','Hold Xiko\'s ashes for up to 5...20 seconds. For each hex or condition you are suffering from while holding her ashes, you gain +3 Health regeneration. When you drop her ashes, you lose 1...4 conditions.<sic/>','(5...20 seconds.) You have +3 Health regeneration for each hex or condition on you. Drop effect: you lose 1...4 conditions.'],
1222=>['Lively Was Naomei','Hold Naomei\'s ashes for up to 45 seconds. When you drop her ashes, all party members in the area are resurrected with 15...75% Health and zero Energy.','(45 seconds.) Drop effect: resurrects party members in the area (15...75% Health and zero Energy).'],
1223=>['Anguished Was Lingwah','Hold Lingwah\'s ashes for up to 10...60 seconds. While you hold her ashes, your Ritualist hexes cost 1...5 less energy and last 33% longer. When you drop her ashes all your Ritualist hexes are recharged.','(10...60 seconds.) Your Ritualist hexes cost 1...5 less energy and last 33% longer. Drop effect: all your Ritualist hexes are recharged.'],
1224=>['Draw Spirit','Teleport target allied spirit to your location.','Teleports target allied spirit to your location.'],
1225=>['Channeled Strike','Target foe is struck for 5...95 lightning damage. That foe is struck for an additional 5...35 lightning damage if you are holding an item.','Deals 5...95 lightning damage. Deals 5...35 additional lightning damage if you are holding an item.'],
1226=>['Spirit Boon Strike','Target foe is struck for 20...65 lightning damage, and all spirits you control within earshot gain 20...65 Health.','Deals 20...65 lightning damage. Spirits you control within earshot gain 20...65 Health.'],
1227=>['Essence Strike','Target foe is struck for 15...60 lightning damage. If any spirits are within earshot, you gain 1...9 Energy.','Deals 15...60 lightning damage. You gain 1...9 Energy if any spirits are within earshot.'],
1228=>['Spirit Siphon','The spirit nearest you loses all Energy. You gain 15...50% of that Energy.','The spirit nearest you loses all Energy. You gain 15...50% of that Energy.'],
1229=>['Explosive Growth','For 15...60 seconds, whenever you create a creature, up to 5 foes near that creature are struck for 20...65 lightning damage.','(15...60 seconds.) Deals 20...65 lightning damage each time you create a creature to 5 foes near that creature.'],
1230=>['Boon of Creation','For 15...60 seconds, whenever you create a creature, you gain 5...50 Health and 1...6 Energy.','(15...60 seconds.) You gain 5...50 Health and 1...6 Energy whenever you create a creature.'],
1231=>['Spirit Channeling','For 12 seconds, you have +1...6 Energy regeneration. When you cast this spell, you gain 3...12 Energy if you are within earshot of a spirit.','(12 seconds.) You have +1...6 Energy regeneration. Initial effect: you gain 3...12 Energy if you are within earshot of a spirit.'],
1232=>['Armor of Unfeeling','For 10...35 seconds, your spirits within earshot take 50% less damage and are immune to critical attacks.','(10...35 seconds.) Your spirits within earshot take 50% less damage and are immune to critical attacks.'],
1233=>['Soothing Memories','Target ally is healed for 10...100 Health. If you are holding an item, you gain 3 Energy.','Heals for 10...100. You gain 3 Energy if you are holding an item.'],
1234=>['Mend Body and Soul','Target ally is healed for 20...115 Health. That ally loses one condition for each spirit within earshot.','Heals for 20...115. Removes one condition for each spirit within earshot.'],
1235=>['Dulled Weapon','For 5...15 seconds, target foe and all adjacent foes cannot achieve a critical hit and deal 1...15 less damage.','Also hexes foes adjacent to your target (5...15 seconds). Removes ability to land a critical hit. Reduces damage by 1...15.'],
1236=>['Binding Chains','For 3 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes move 90% slower and take 1...30 damage each second while moving.','Also hexes foes near your target. (3 seconds.) These foes move 90% slower and takes 1...30 damage each second while moving.'],
1237=>['Painful Bond','For 10...20 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes are hexed with Painful Bond and take 8...20 damage whenever hit by a spirit\'s attack.','Also hexes foes near your target (10...20 seconds). Spirits do 8...20 more damage against these foes.'],
1238=>['Signet of Creation','You gain 4 Energy for every summoned creature you control within earshot (maximum 3...12 Energy).','Gain 4 Energy (maximum 3...12 Energy) for each summoned creature you control within earshot.'],
1239=>['Signet of Spirits','Create 3 level 1...12 spirits. These spirits deal 5...20 damage with attacks and die after 60 seconds.','Creates 3 level 1...12 spirits (60 second lifespan). These spirits deal 5...20 damage with attacks.'],
1240=>['Soul Twisting','For 5...45 seconds, your Binding Rituals cost 15 less Energy (minimum 10) and recharge instantly. Soul Twisting ends after 1...3 Binding Rituals.','(5...45 seconds.) Your Binding Rituals cost 15 less Energy (minimum 10) and recharge instantly. <gray>Ends after 1...3 Binding Rituals.</gray>'],
1244=>['Ghostly Haste','For 5...20 seconds, spells you cast while within earshot of a spirit recharge 25% faster.','(5...20 seconds.) Spells you cast recharge 25% faster. <gray>No effect unless you are within earshot of a spirit.</gray>'],
1245=>['Gaze from Beyond','Target foe is struck for 20...65 lightning damage. If you are within earshot of a spirit, that foe is Blinded for 2...6 seconds.','Deals 20...65 lightning damage. Inflicts Blindness condition for 2...6 seconds if you are within earshot of a spirit.'],
1246=>['Ancestors\' Rage','For 1 second, nothing happens. When this skill ends, all foes adjacent to target ally are struck for 5...110 lightning damage.','(1 second.) End Effect: deals 5...110 lightning damage to foes adjacent to target ally.'],
1247=>['Pain','Create a level 1...12 spirit. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...30 damage. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...30 damage.'],
1249=>['Displacement','Create a level 1...14 spirit. All non-spirit allies within its range have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks. Every time an attack is blocked in this way, this spirit takes 60 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range have 75% chance to block. <gray>Block effect: this spirit takes 60 damage.</gray>'],
1250=>['Preservation','Create a level 1...14 spirit. Every 4 seconds, this spirit heals one non-spirit ally in the area for 10...115 Health. This spirit dies after 90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (90 second lifespan). Every 4 seconds this spirit heals one non-spirit ally for 10...115.'],
1251=>['Life','Create a level 1...14 spirit. When this spirit dies, all non-spirit allies within its range are healed for 1...7 Health for each second this spirit was alive. This spirit dies after 20 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (20 second lifespan). Affects non-spirit allies within range. End effect: heals for 1...7 for each second this spirit was alive.'],
1252=>['Earthbind','Create a level 1...14 spirit. All non-spirit foes knocked down within its range are knocked down for at least 3 seconds. Whenever this happens, this spirit loses 50...25 Health. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Any time non-spirit foes within range are knocked down, they are knocked down for at least 3 seconds. <gray>Knock-down cost: this spirit loses 50...25 Health.</gray>'],
1253=>['Bloodsong','Create a level 1...12 spirit who dies after 30...150 seconds. Attacks by that spirit steal up to 5...25 Health.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Its attacks steal 5...25 Health.'],
1255=>['Wanderlust','Create a level 1...12 spirit. Whenever this spirit\'s attack hits a stationary foe, that foe is knocked down and the spirit loses 70...50 Health. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Its attacks against stationary foes cause knock-down. <gray>Knock-down cost: this spirit loses 70...50 Health.</gray>'],
1257=>['Spirit Light Weapon','For 10 seconds, target ally gains 1...15 Health per second and an additional 1...15 Health per second if that ally is within earshot of a spirit.','(10 seconds.) Target ally gains 1...15 Health each second. 1...15 more healing per second while within earshot of a spirit.'],
1258=>['Brutal Weapon','Give target ally a Brutal Weapon for 10...40 seconds. The bearer\'s weapon strikes for +5...15 damage as long as the bearer is under no enchantments.','(10...40 seconds.) Attacks deal +5...15 damage. <gray>No effect while target ally is enchanted.</gray>'],
1259=>['Guided Weapon','For 4...10 seconds, target ally\'s attacks cannot be blocked.','(4...10 seconds.) Attacks are unblockable.'],
1260=>['Meekness','For 5...30 seconds, target foe and all foes in the area attack 50% slower.','Also hexes foes in the area of target (5...30 seconds). These foes attack 50% slower.'],
1261=>['Frigid Armor','For 10...25 seconds, you have +10...40 armor against physical damage and cannot be set on fire.','(10...25 seconds.) You have +10...40 armor against physical damage and immunity to Burning.'],
1262=>['Healing Ring','Heal adjacent creatures for 30...180 Health. The caster is not healed.','Heals adjacent allies and foes for 30...180. <gray>The caster is not healed.</gray>'],
1263=>['Renew Life','Resurrect target touched dead target <sic/> party member with 50% Health and 5...20% Energy. That party member and all allies within earshot are healed for 55...130 Health.','Touch Spell. Resurrects target party member (50% Health and 5...20% Energy). Heals allies within earshot for 55...130.'],
1264=>['Doom','Strike target foe for 10...40 lightning (maximum 135) damage for every recharging binding ritual you have.','Deals 10...40 lightning damage (maximum 135) for each of your recharging binding rituals.'],
1265=>['Wielder\'s Boon','Heal target ally for 15...60 points. If that ally is under the effects of a weapon spell, Wielder\'s Boon heals for an additional 15...75 Health.','Heals for 15...60. Heals for 15...75 more if this ally is under a Weapon <sic/> spell.'],
1266=>['Soothing','Create a level 1...12 spirit. All foes within its range take twice as long to build adrenaline. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Building adrenaline takes twice as long for foes within range.'],
1267=>['Vital Weapon','For 5...30 seconds, target ally has a Vital Weapon and has +40...175 maximum Health.','(5...30 seconds.) +40...175 maximum Health.'],
1268=>['Weapon of Quickening','For 5...25 seconds, target ally has a Weapon of Quickening, and spells and binding rituals recharge 33% faster.','(5...25 seconds.) Spells and binding rituals recharge 33% faster.'],
1269=>['Signet of Rage','Target foe takes 5...50 holy damage and +5...10 holy damage for each adrenaline skill that foe has.','Deals 5...50 holy damage. Deals 5...10 more holy damage for each of target foe\'s adrenaline skills.'],
1333=>['Extend Conditions','Spread all conditions from target foe to foes near your target. The durations of those conditions are increased by 5...100% (maximum 30 seconds).','Spread all conditions from target foe to foes near your target. Those <sic/> durations of those conditions are increased by 5...100% (maximum 30 seconds).'],
1334=>['Hypochondria','Transfer all conditions from all foes in the area to target foe.','Transfer all conditions from foes in the area to target foe.'],
1335=>['Wastrel\'s Demise','For 5 seconds, target foe is hexed with Wastrel\'s Demise. Each second while hexed, target foe and all foes adjacent to that foe take 1...10 damage and an additional 1...10 damage for each second this spell is in effect. This hex ends prematurely if target foe uses a skill.','(5 seconds.) Each second while hexed, target foe and all foes adjacent to that foe take 1...10 damage. Foes take +1...10 damage each second this hex is in effect. <gray>Ends early if target foe uses a skill.</gray>'],
1336=>['Spiritual Pain','Target foe takes 15...75 damage. All hostile summoned creatures in the area of that foe take 25...125 damage.','Deals 15...75 damage. Deals 25...125 damage to hostile summoned creatures in the area of your target foe.'],
1337=>['Drain Delusions','Remove one Mesmer hex from target foe. If a hex was removed in this way, that foe loses 1...5 Energy and you gain 4 Energy for each point lost.','Removes one Mesmer hex from target foe. Causes 1...5 Energy loss. You gain 4 Energy for each point lost. <gray>No effect unless a hex was removed.</gray>'],
1338=>['Persistence of Memory','For 5...20 seconds, whenever a spell you cast is interrupted, that spell is instantly recharged.','(5...20 seconds.) Your interrupted spells recharge instantly.'],
1339=>['Symbols of Inspiration','For 1...31 seconds, this skill becomes the Elite of target foe. Elite spells you cast use your Fast Casting attribute instead of their normal attributes.','(1...31 seconds.) This skill becomes the Elite of target foe. Elite spells you cast use your Fast Casting attribute instead of their normal attributes.'],
1340=>['Symbolic Celerity','For 36...60 seconds, all of your signets use your Fast Casting attribute instead of their normal attributes.','(36...60 seconds.) Your signets use your Fast Casting attribute.'],
1341=>['Frustration','For 5...20 seconds, target foe casts spells 50% slower and takes 5...50 damage whenever interrupted. If a skill is interrupted, Frustration deals double damage.','(5...20 seconds.) Causes 50% slower spell casting. Target foe takes 5...50 damage whenever interrupted. Deals double damage on skill interrupt.'],
1342=>['Tease','If target foe is using a skill, that foe and other foes in the area are interrupted and you steal 0...5 Energy from all foes in the area.','Interrupts a skill. Interruption effect: also interrupts other foes in the area, and you steal 0...5 Energy from all foes in the area.'],
1343=>['Ether Phantom','For 10 seconds, target foe has -1 Energy degeneration. If this hex is removed prematurely, that foe loses 1...5 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Causes -1 Energy degeneration. Causes 1...5 Energy loss if this hex ends early.'],
1344=>['Web of Disruption','Interrupt target foe. For 10 seconds, target foe is hexed with Web of Disruption. When this hex ends, that foe is interrupted again.','(10 seconds.) Initial effect: interrupts a skill. End effect: interrupts a skill.'],
1345=>['Enchanter\'s Conundrum','For 10 seconds, target foe casts enchantments 100...200% slower. If target foe is not under the effects of an enchantment when this hex is applied, that foe and all adjacent foes take 10...100 damage.','Causes 100...200% slower enchantment casting (10 seconds). Initial effect: deals 10...100 damage to target and adjacent foes if target foe is not enchanted.'],
1346=>['Signet of Illusions','Your next 1...3 spells use your Illusion attribute instead of its normal attribute.','Your next 1...3 spells use your Illusion attribute instead of its normal attribute.'],
1347=>['Discharge Enchantment','Remove one enchantment from target foe. If that foe is hexed, this skill recharges 20...50% faster.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. 20...50% faster recharge if that foe was hexed.'],
1348=>['Hex Eater Vortex','Remove a hex from target ally. If a hex is removed in this way, foes near that ally take 30...90 damage and lose one enchantment.','Removes one hex from target ally. Removal effect: deals 30...90 damage and removes one enchantment from foes near this ally.'],
1349=>['Mirror of Disenchantment','Remove one enchantment from target foe. All of that foe\'s party members also lose that same enchantment.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. That foe\'s party members also lose this enchantment.'],
1350=>['Simple Thievery','Interrupt target foe\'s action. If that action was a skill, that skill is disabled for 5...20 seconds, and Simple Thievery is replaced by that skill.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: If a skill was interrupted, that skill is disabled and Simple Thievery becomes that skill (5...20 seconds).'],
1351=>['Animate Shambling Horror','Exploit nearest corpse to create a level 1...17 shambling horror. When the shambling horror dies, it is replaced by a level 0...15 jagged horror that causes Bleeding with each of its attacks.','Creates a level 1...17 shambling horror. When the shambling horror dies, it is replaced by a level 0...15 jagged horror that causes Bleeding with each of its attacks. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse.</gray>'],
1352=>['Order of Undeath','For 5 seconds, your minions deal +3...16 damage, but you lose 2% of your maximum Health whenever one of your minions hits with an attack.','(5 seconds.) Your undead servants deal +3...16 damage. <gray>You lose 2% of your maximum Health whenever your servants hit.</gray>'],
1353=>['Putrid Flesh','Destroy one of your target animated undead minions. All foes near that creature are Diseased for 5...15 seconds.','Destroys one of your undead servants. Inflicts Diseased condition (5...15 seconds) to foes near this servant.'],
1354=>['Feast for the Dead','Destroy target animated undead ally. All of your other animated undead allies are healed for 10...100 Health.','Destroys one of your undead servants. Heals your servants for 10...100.'],
1355=>['Jagged Bones','For 30 seconds, whenever target undead servant dies, it is replaced by a level 0...15 jagged horror that causes Bleeding with each of its attacks.','(30 seconds.) When target undead servant dies, it is replaced by a level 0...15 jagged horror that inflicts Bleeding with attacks.'],
1356=>['Contagion','For 60 seconds, whenever you suffer from a new condition, all foes in the area suffer from that same condition and you sacrifice 10...5% maximum Health.','(60 seconds.) Whenever you gain a condition, all foes in the area gain that same condition. <gray>You sacrifice 10...5% maximum Health each time this happens.</gray>'],
1358=>['Ulcerous Lungs','For 10...25 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes suffer from -4 Health degeneration when Bleeding, and whenever they use a shout or chant, they Bleed for 3...15 seconds.','Also hexes foes near your target (10...25 seconds). Causes -4 Health degeneration to any of these foes that are Bleeding. Inflicts Bleeding (3...15 seconds) whenever these foes use a shout or chant.'],
1359=>['Pain of Disenchantment','Target foe loses 1...3 enchantments. If an enchantment was lost in this way, that foe and all adjacent foes lose 10...100 Health.','Target foe loses 1...3 enchantments. Removal effect: that foe and all adjacent foes lose 10...100 Health.'],
1360=>['Mark of Fury','For 5 seconds, allies hitting target foe gain 0...2 strikes of adrenaline. When this hex ends, that foe suffers from Cracked Armor for 1...15 seconds.','(5 seconds.) Allies hitting target foe gain 0...2 strikes of adrenaline. End effect: inflicts Cracked Armor (1...15 seconds.)'],
1362=>['Corrupt Enchantment','Remove one enchantment from target foe. If an enchantment is removed in this way, that foe suffers from -1...8 Health degeneration for 10 seconds.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. Removal effect: -1...8 Health degeneration (10 seconds).'],
1363=>['Signet of Sorrow','Target foe takes 15...75 damage. If target foe is near a corpse or has a dead pet, this skill recharges instantly.','Deals 15...75 damage. Recharges instantly if target foe is near a corpse or has a dead pet.'],
1364=>['Signet of Suffering','You suffer from Bleeding for 6 seconds. The next Necromancer skill that targets a foe causes Bleeding for 2...16 seconds.','You Bleed for 6 seconds. Applies Bleeding (2...16 seconds) to the target of your next Necromancer skill.'],
1365=>['Signet of Lost Souls','If target foe is below 50% Health, you gain 10...100 Health and 1...10 Energy.','You gain 10...100 Health and 1...10 Energy if target foe is below 50% Health.'],
1366=>['Well of Darkness','Exploit nearest corpse to create a Well of Darkness for 5...50 seconds. Hexed foes within the Well of Darkness miss 50% of the time.','(5...50 seconds.) Hexed foes in this well have 50% chance to miss. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse</gray>.'],
1367=>['Blinding Surge','Target foe is struck for 5...50 lightning damage. That foe and all adjacent foes are Blinded for 3...8 seconds. This spell has 25% armor penetration. If this spell strikes an attacking foe, all adjacent foes are also struck and this spell deals 50% more damage.','Deals 5...50 lightning damage. Inflicts Blindness condition (3...8 seconds) on target and adjacent foes. 25% armor penetration. If target was attacking, also hits adjacent foes and deals 50% more damage.'],
1368=>['Chilling Winds','Target foe and all adjacent foes are struck for 30...60 cold damage. For 10 seconds, the next Water Magic hex targeting a hexed foe lasts 25...100% longer.','(10 seconds.) The next water hex on target foe lasts 25...100% longer. Initial effect: 30...60 cold damage. Also strikes adjacent.'],
1369=>['Lightning Bolt','Send out a Lightning Bolt that strikes for 5...50 lightning damage if it hits. If Lightning Bolt strikes a moving foe, that foe is struck for 5...50 additional lightning damage. This spell has 25% armor penetration.','Projectile: deals 5...50 lightning damage. Deals 5...50 more lightning damage if target foe is moving. 25% armor penetration.'],
1370=>['Storm Djinn\'s Haste','For 10...25 seconds, you move 25% faster. Each second that you are moving, you lose 1 Energy.','(10...25 seconds.) You move 25% faster. <gray>Lose 1 Energy each second while moving.</gray>'],
1371=>['Stone Striker','For 5...30 seconds, whenever you take or deal elemental or physical damage, that damage is converted to earth damage.','(5...30 seconds.) Converts elemental and physical damage you take or deal to earth damage.'],
1372=>['Sandstorm','Create a Sandstorm at target foe\'s location. For 10 seconds, nearby foes are struck for 10...30 earth damage each second and attacking foes are struck for an additional 10...30 earth damage each second.','Deals 10...30 earth damage each second (10 seconds). Hits foes near target foe\'s initial location. Hits attacking foes for 10...30 more earth damage each second.'],
1373=>['Stone Sheath','For 5...20 seconds, you and target ally have +1...30 armor and are immune to critical hits. When you cast this spell, all foes near you and your target take 15...70 earth damage and are Weakened for 5...20 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) Gives you and target ally +1...30 armor and immunity to critical hits. Initial effect: Foes near you and target ally are struck for 15...70 earth damage and are Weakened (5...20 seconds).'],
1374=>['Ebon Hawk','Send a projectile that strikes target foe for 10...85 earth damage and causes Weakness for 5...15 seconds if it hits.','Projectile: deals 10...85 earth damage and inflicts Weakness condition (5...15 seconds).'],
1375=>['Stoneflesh Aura','For 5...15 seconds, damage you receive is reduced by 1...31, and you are immune to critical attacks.','(5...15 seconds.) Reduces damage you take by 1...31, and you are immune to critical hits.'],
1376=>['Glyph of Restoration','For 15 seconds, your next 2 spells heal you for 30...105 Health, and you are healed for 150...400% of the Energy cost of each spell.','(15 seconds.) Your next 2 spells heal you for 30...105, and you are healed for 150...400% of the Energy cost of each spell.'],
1377=>['Ether Prism','For 3 seconds, all damage you take is reduced by 75%. When Ether Prism ends, you gain 5...20 Energy.','(3 seconds.) All damage you take is reduced by 75%. End effect: gain 5...20 Energy.'],
1378=>['Master of Magic','For 1...61 seconds, all of your elemental attributes are set to 8...14 and your elemental spells return 30% of their Energy cost.','(1...61 seconds). Your elemental attributes are set to 8...14 and elemental spells return 30% of their Energy cost.'],
1379=>['Glowing Gaze','Target foe takes 5...50 fire damage. If that foe is on Fire, <sic/> you gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage.','Deals 5...50 fire damage. You gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage if target foe is Burning.'],
1380=>['Savannah Heat','You create Savannah Heat at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, all nearby foes take 5...20 fire damage for each second this spell has been in effect.','Deals 5...20 fire damage for each second since casting this spell (5 seconds). <gray>Hits foes near target\'s initial location.</gray>'],
1381=>['Flame Djinn\'s Haste','All adjacent foes are struck for 15...120 fire damage. For 8...14 seconds, you move 25% faster. Flame Djinn\'s Haste recharges 50% faster if a foe was struck by this spell.','(8...14 seconds.) You move 25% faster. Initial effect: deals 15...120 fire damage to foes adjacent to you. If you damage a foe with this spell, it recharges 50% faster.'],
1382=>['Freezing Gust','If target foe is under the effect of a Water Magic hex, that foe is struck for 20...80 cold damage. Otherwise, that foe moves 66% slower for 1...5 seconds.','Deals 20...80 cold damage if target foe is hexed with Water Magic. Otherwise, this foe moves 66% slower (1...5 seconds).'],
1390=>['Judge\'s Intervention','For 10 seconds, the next time target ally receives damage that would be fatal, the damage is negated and one nearby foe takes 30...180 holy damage.','(10 seconds.) Negates the next fatal damage. Negation effect: deals 30...180 holy damage to one foe near target ally.'],
1391=>['Supportive Spirit','For 5...23 seconds, whenever target ally takes damage while knocked down, that ally is healed for 5...35 Health.','(5...23 seconds.) Heals for 5...35 whenever target ally takes damage while knocked-down.'],
1392=>['Watchful Healing','For 10 seconds, target ally gains +1...4 Health regeneration. If this skill ends prematurely, that ally gains 30...120 Health.','(10 seconds.) Target ally has +1...4 Health regeneration and gains 30...120 Health if this enchantment ends early.'],
1393=>['Healer\'s Boon','For 10...55 seconds. <sic/> Healing Prayers spells cast 50% faster and heal for 50% more Health.','(10...55 seconds.) Healing Prayers spells cast 50% faster and heal for 50% more.'],
1394=>['Healer\'s Covenant','While you maintain this enchantment, your Healing Prayers spells heal for 25% less Health, but cost 1...3 Energy.','Your Healing Prayers spells cost 1...3 less Energy. <gray>These spells heal for 25% less.</gray>'],
1395=>['Balthazar\'s Pendulum','For 5...10 seconds, the next time target ally would be knocked down by a foe, that foe is knocked down instead.','(5...10 seconds.) Causes knock-down to the next foe attempting to knock-down target ally.'],
1396=>['Words of Comfort','Target ally is healed for 15...60 Health and an additional 15...45 Health if that ally is suffering from a condition.','Heals for 15...60. Heals for 15...45 more if target ally has a condition.'],
1397=>['Light of Deliverance','All party members are healed for 5...70 Health.','Heals entire party for 5...70.'],
1398=>['Scourge Enchantment','For 30 seconds, each time target foe is the target of an enchantment, the caster of that enchantment takes 15...75 damage.','(30 seconds.) Deals 15...75 damage to anyone casting an enchantment on target foe.'],
1399=>['Shield of Absorption','For 3...7 seconds, damage received by target ally is reduced by 5 each time that ally is hit while under the effects of this enchantment.','(3...7 seconds.) Reduces incoming damage by 5 each time target ally takes damage.'],
1400=>['Reversal of Damage','For 8 seconds, the next time target ally would take damage, the foe dealing the damage takes that damage instead (maximum 5...75).','(8 seconds.) Negates the next damage and hits the source for that same amount (maximum 5...75).'],
1401=>['Mending Touch','Touched ally loses two conditions and is healed for 15...60 Health for each condition removed in this way.','Touch Spell. Removes two conditions. Heals for 15...60 for each condition removed.'],
1402=>['Critical Chop','If this attack hits, you inflict +5...20 damage. If this attack results in a critical hit, target foe is interrupted.','Deals +5...20 damage. Interrupts an action if you land a critical hit.'],
1403=>['Agonizing Chop','When this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If target foe is suffering from a Deep Wound, you interrupt that foe\'s action.','Deals +5...20 damage. Interrupts an action if target foe has a Deep Wound.'],
1404=>['Flail','For 1...15 seconds, you attack 33% faster but move 33% slower.','(1...15 seconds.) You attack 33% faster. <gray>You move 33% slower.</gray>'],
1405=>['Charging Strike','For 1...10 seconds, you run 33% faster. Your next successful melee hit does +10...40 damage and this stance ends. This stance ends if you use a skill.','(1...10 seconds.) You move 33% faster and deal +10...40 damage with your next melee hit. <gray>Ends when you hit or if you use a skill.</gray>'],
1406=>['Headbutt','Target touched foe takes 40...100 damage. You are Dazed for 5...20 seconds.','Deals 40...100 damage. <gray>You are Dazed (5...20 seconds).</gray>'],
1407=>['Lion\'s Comfort','All of your signets are disabled for 12 seconds. You are healed for 50...110 Health, and gain 0...3 strikes of adrenaline.','You are healed for 50...110 and gain 0...3 strikes of adrenaline. <gray>Disables your signets (12 seconds).</gray>'],
1408=>['Rage of the Ntouka','Gain 1...7 strikes of adrenaline. For 10 seconds, whenever you use an adrenal skill, that skill recharges for 5 seconds.','You gain 1...7 adrenaline. <gray>For 10 seconds, adrenal skills have a 5 second recharge when used.</gray>'],
1409=>['Mokele Smash','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...20 damage and gain 2 strikes of adrenaline.','Deals +5...20 damage and you gain 2 strikes of adrenaline.'],
1410=>['Overbearing Smash','If this attack hits, you deal +1...20 damage. If target foe is knocked down, that foe is Dazed for 1...8 seconds.','Deals +1...20 damage. If target foe is knocked down, they are Dazed (1...8 seconds).'],
1411=>['Signet of Stamina','You have +50...300 maximum Health. This signet ends if you successfully hit with an attack.','You have +50...300 maximum Health. <gray>Ends if you hit with an attack.</gray>'],
1412=>['"You\'re All Alone!"','If target foe isn\'t near an ally, that foe suffers from Cripple and Weakness for 8 seconds.','Inflicts Cripple and Weakness conditions (8 seconds). <gray>No effect if target foe is near one of its allies.</gray>'],
1413=>['Burst of Aggression','For 2...10 seconds, you attack 33% faster. When this stance ends, you lose all adrenaline.','(2...10 seconds.) You attack 33% faster. <gray>End effect: lose all adrenaline.</gray>'],
1414=>['Enraging Charge','For 5...15 seconds, you move 25% faster. Enraging Charge ends when you successfully strike a target, at which point you gain 0...3 strikes of adrenaline if you hit with a melee attack.','(5...15 seconds.) You move 25% faster. Gain +0...3 adrenaline on your next melee attack. <gray>Ends after your next hit.</gray>'],
1415=>['Crippling Slash','If this attack hits, target foe is Crippled for 5...15 seconds and begins Bleeding for 10...25 seconds.','Inflicts Crippled condition (5...15 seconds) and Bleeding condition (10...25 seconds).'],
1416=>['Barbarous Slice','If this attack hits, you deal +5...30 damage. If you are currently not in a stance, you also inflict Bleeding for 5...15 seconds.','Deals +5...30 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...15 seconds) if you are not in a stance.'],
1465=>['Prepared Shot','If this attack hits, you strike for +10...25 damage. If you are under the effects of a preparation, you gain 1...9 Energy.','Deals +10...25 damage. You gain 1...9 Energy if you have a preparation active.'],
1466=>['Burning Arrow','If this attack hits, you strike for +10...30 damage and cause Burning for 1...7 seconds.','Deals +10...30 damage. Inflicts Burning condition (1...7 seconds).'],
1467=>['Arcing Shot','If this arrow hits, it strikes for +10...25 damage. This arrow cannot be blocked, but it moves 50% slower.','Deals +10...25 damage. Unblockable. <gray>This arrow moves 50% slower.</gray>'],
1468=>['Strike as One','Your animal companion instantly moves to your target and causes Bleeding for 5...15 seconds with its next attack. The next time you hit with an attack, target foe is Crippled for 5...15 seconds.','Your animal companion instantly moves to your target and inflicts Bleeding (5...15 seconds) with its next attack. The next time you hit with an attack, you inflict Crippled condition (5...15 seconds).'],
1469=>['Crossfire','If this attack hits target foe, it deals +5...20 damage. If that foe is near any of your allies, this attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +5...20 damage. Unblockable if target foe is near any of your allies.'],
1470=>['Barbed Arrows','For 24 seconds, your arrows cause Bleeding for 3...15 seconds. You have -40 armor while activating this skill.','(24 seconds.) Your arrows inflict Bleeding condition (3...15 seconds). <gray>You have -40 armor while activating this skill.</gray>'],
1471=>['Scavenger\'s Focus','For 10 seconds if you strike a foe who is suffering from a condition you gain 3...12 Energy.','(10 seconds). You gain 3...12 Energy if you strike a foe who has a condition.'],
1472=>['Toxicity','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Poisoned or Diseased creatures within its range suffer -2 Health degeneration. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...90 second lifespan.) Poisoned or Diseased creatures within range have -2 Health degeneration.'],
1473=>['Quicksand','Create a level 1...10 spirit. All non-spirit creatures within its range lose 1 Energy each time they attack or use a skill. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Creatures lose 1 Energy each time they attack or use a skill. Does not affect spirits.'],
1474=>['Storm\'s Embrace','For 10 seconds, you move 25% faster. This stance is refreshed whenever you take Elemental damage.','(10 seconds.) You move 25% faster. Renewal: whenever you take elemental damage.'],
1475=>['Trapper\'s Speed','For 5...30 seconds, your Traps recharge 25% faster and activate 25% faster. This Stance ends if you successfully hit with an attack.','(5...30 seconds.) Your traps recharge 25% faster and activate 25% faster. <gray>Ends if you hit with an attack.</gray>'],
1476=>['Tripwire','When Tripwire is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 5...20 piercing damage. Any Crippled foes are knocked down. Tripwire ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Deals 5...20 piercing damage to nearby foes. Causes knock-down to Crippled foes. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
1478=>['Renewing Surge','For 8 seconds, target foe suffers 2...12 damage each second. When this hex ends, you gain 1...8 Energy.','(8 seconds.) Deals 2...12 damage each second. End effect: You gain 1...8 energy.'],
1479=>['Offering of Spirit','Gain 8...17 Energy. If any spirits are within earshot, you do not sacrifice Health.','You gain 8...17 Energy. You do not sacrifice Health if any spirits are within earshot.'],
1480=>['Spirit\'s Gift','For 60 seconds, whenever you create a creature, all allies near that creature gain 5...50 Health and lose 1 condition.','(60 seconds.) Whenever you create a creature, all nearby allies gain 5...50 Health and lose one condition.'],
1481=>['Death Pact Signet','Resurrect target party member with your current Health and 15...100% Energy. The next time that ally dies within 120 seconds, so do you.','Resurrects target party member with your current Health and 15...100% maximum Energy. <gray>For 120 seconds, you die the next time this party member dies.</gray>'],
1482=>['Reclaim Essence','All of your Spirits die. You gain 5...20 Energy and all of your Binding Rituals are recharged if a Spirit died in this way.','All of your Spirits die. If a Spirit dies in this way, you gain 5...20 Energy and all of your Binding Rituals are recharged.'],
1483=>['Banishing Strike','If it hits, this attack deals 10...60 holy damage. It deals double damage to summoned creatures.','Deals 10...60 holy damage. Deals double damage to summoned creatures.'],
1484=>['Mystic Sweep','If this attack hits, you deal +3...12 damage. If you are enchanted, this attack deals an additional +3...12 damage.','Deals +3...12 damage. Deals an additional +3...12 damage if you are enchanted.'],
1485=>['Eremite\'s Attack','If it hits, this attack deals +1...10 damage and removes a Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment is removed, you do an additional +1...10 damage and strike all adjacent foes.','Deals +1...10 damage and removes a Dervish enchantment. Removal Effect: Deals +1...10 damage and strikes all adjacent foes.'],
1486=>['Reap Impurities','If this attack hits, you deal +3...15 damage. Each foe you hit loses 1 condition. For each foe who loses a condition, all foes adjacent to that target foe take 10...40 holy damage.','Deals +3...15 damage. Struck foes lose 1 condition. Removal Effect: all foes adjacent to those struck take 10...40 holy damage.'],
1487=>['Twin Moon Sweep','You lose 1 Dervish enchantment and gain 10...50 Health. If an enchantment is lost in this way, you cannot be blocked, you strike twice, and you gain an additional 10...70 Health.','Remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Gain 10...50 Health. Removal effect: unblockable, attack twice, and gain 10...70 more Health.'],
1488=>['Victorious Sweep','If this attack hits, you deal +5...25 damage. If target foe has less Health than you, you gain 30...80 Health.','Deals +5...25 damage. You gain 30...80 Health for each foe you hit that has less Health than you.'],
1489=>['Irresistible Sweep','Deal +3...15 damage and lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If you lose an enchantment in this way, Irresistible Sweep cannot be blocked, removes a stance, and deals +3...15 additional damage.','Deals +3...15 damage. Remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: unblockable, removes a stance, deals +3...15 additional damage.'],
1490=>['Pious Assault','If it hits, this attack deals +10...20 damage and removes 1 Dervish enchantment. If a Dervish enchantment was removed, this skill recharges 75% faster and adjacent foes take 10...30 damage.','Deals +10...20 damage. Removes 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal Effect: this skill recharges 75% faster and adjacent foes take 10...30 damage.'],
1491=>['Mystic Twister','Deals 10...60 cold damage to all nearby foes. If you are enchanted, this spell deals an additional 10...60 cold damage.','Deals 10...60 cold damage to all nearby foes. Deals 10...60 more cold damage if you are enchanted.'],
1493=>['Grenth\'s Fingers','All nearby foes are struck for 10...40 cold damage. For 30 seconds, your attacks deal cold damage. When this enchantment ends, you transfer 1...2 conditions to all nearby foes. <sic/>','(30 seconds.) Your attacks deal cold damage. Initial effect: hits nearby foes for 10...40 cold damage. End effect: transfers 1...2 conditions to all nearby foes.'],
1495=>['Aura of Thorns','All nearby foes begin Bleeding for 5...15 seconds. For 30 seconds, this enchantment does nothing. When this enchantment ends, all nearby foes are Crippled for 3...8 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Initial effect: inflicts Bleeding condition (5...15 seconds) on nearby foes. End effect: inflicts Crippled condition (3...8 seconds) on nearby foes.'],
1496=>['Balthazar\'s Rage','All nearby foes are set on fire for 1...3 seconds. For 20 seconds afterward, this enchantment does nothing. When this enchantment ends, you gain 1...2 strikes of adrenaline if any foes are within earshot.','(20 seconds.) Initial Effect: Inflicts burning (1...3 seconds) on nearby foes. End effect: gain 1...2 strikes of adrenaline if any foes are within earshot.'],
1497=>['Dust Cloak','All adjacent foes are struck for 10...40 earth damage. For 30 seconds, your attacks deal earth damage. When this enchantment ends, all adjacent foes are Blinded for 1...4 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Your attacks deal earth damage. Initial effect: deals 10...40 earth damage to adjacent foes. End effect: inflicts Blindness condition (1...4 seconds) on adjacent foes.'],
1498=>['Staggering Force','All nearby foes are struck for 10...40 earth damage. For 30 seconds, your attacks deal earth damage. When this enchantment ends, all nearby foes have Cracked Armor for 1...10 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Your attacks deal earth damage. Initial effect: deals 10...40 earth damage to nearby foes. End effect: inflicts Cracked Armor condition (1...10 seconds) on nearby foes.'],
1499=>['Pious Renewal','For 8 seconds, nothing happens. When this enchantment ends, Pious Renewal is recharged and you gain 0...5 Energy and 0...30 Health.','(8 seconds.) End Effect: recharges itself and you gain 0...5 Energy and 0...30 Health.'],
1500=>['Mirage Cloak','For 1...7 seconds, you have a 40...80% chance to block incoming attacks. When you cast this enchantment, all nearby foes are struck for 10...40 earth damage.','(1...7 seconds.) You have 40...80% chance to block. Initial Effect: deals 10...40 earth damage to nearby foes.'],
1502=>['Arcane Zeal','For 10 seconds, whenever you cast a spell, you gain 1 Energy for each enchantment on you (maximum 1...7 Energy).','(10 seconds.) You gain 1 Energy (maximum 1...7) for each enchantment on you whenever you cast a spell.'],
1503=>['Mystic Vigor','For 20 seconds, every time you successfully hit with an attack, you gain 3...15 Health for each enchantment on you (maximum 25 Health).','(20 seconds.) You gain 3...15 Health (maximum 25) for each enchantment on you whenever you hit with an attack.'],
1504=>['Watchful Intervention','For 60 seconds, the next time damage drops target ally\'s Health below 25%, that ally is healed for 50...200 Health.','(60 seconds.) Heals for 50...200 the next time damage drops target ally\'s Health below 25%.'],
1505=>['Vow of Piety','For 20 seconds, you have +24 armor and +1...4 Health regeneration. Vow of Piety renews whenever an enchantment on you ends.','(20 seconds) +24 armor and +1...4 Health regeneration. Renewal: Whenever an enchantment on you ends.'],
1506=>['Vital Boon','For 20 seconds, you have +40...100 maximum Health. When this enchantment ends, you are healed for 75...200 Health.','(20 seconds.) You have +40...100 maximum Health. End effect: Heals you for 75...200.'],
1507=>['Heart of Holy Flame','All nearby foes take 5...30 holy damage. For 30 seconds, your attacks deal holy damage. When this enchantment ends, all nearby foes are set on fire for 2...5 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Your attacks deal holy damage. Initial effect: deals 5...30 holy damage to nearby foes. End effect: inflicts Burning condition (2...5 seconds) on nearby foes.'],
1508=>['Extend Enchantments','For 10 seconds, your next Dervish enchantment lasts 10...150% longer.','(10 seconds.) Your next Dervish enchantment lasts 10...150% longer.'],
1509=>['Faithful Intervention','If damage drops your Health below 50%, Faithful Intervention ends. When Faithful Intervention ends, you are healed for 30...150 Health.','You gain 30...150 Health the next time damage drops your Health below 50%.'],
1510=>['Sand Shards','For 30 seconds, the next 1...5 times you hit with a scythe, all other adjacent foes take 10...60 earth damage.','(30 seconds.) Deal 10...60 earth damage to all other adjacent foes whenever you hit with your scythe. <gray>Ends after 1...5 hits.</gray>'],
1512=>['Lyssa\'s Haste','For 3...15 seconds, your Dervish enchantments recharge 33% faster. When you activate this enchantment, all adjacent foes are interrupted. When this enchantment ends, all adjacent foes are interrupted. 50% failure chance unless Wind Prayers 5 or higher.','(3...15 seconds.) Your Dervish enchantments recharge 33% faster. Initial Effect: interrupts all adjacent foes. End Effect: interrupts all adjacent foes. <gray>50% failure chance unless Wind Prayers 5 or higher.</gray>'],
1513=>['Guiding Hands','For 20 seconds, your next 0...3 attacks cannot be blocked. When activated, this skill removes the Blindness condition.','(20 seconds.) Your next 0...3 attacks cannot be blocked. Initial effect: removes Blindness.'],
1514=>['Fleeting Stability','For 2...6 seconds, you cannot be knocked down and move 25% faster. This enchantment ends prematurely if it prevents a knockdown.','(2...6 seconds.) You cannot be knocked down and move 25% faster. Ends if knockdown prevented.'],
1515=>['Armor of Sanctity','All adjacent foes suffer from Weakness for 5...15 seconds. For 15 seconds, you take 5...20 less damage from foes suffering from a condition.','Inflicts Weakness condition on all adjacent foes (5...15). You take 5...20 less damage from foes with a condition. (15 seconds.)'],
1516=>['Mystic Regeneration','For 5...20 seconds, you have +1...4 Health regeneration for each enchantment (maximum of 8) on you.','(5...20 seconds.) You have +1...4 Health regeneration for each enchantment (maximum of 8) on you.'],
1517=>['Vow of Silence','For 5...10 seconds, you cannot be the target of spells, and you cannot cast spells.','(5...10 seconds.) Spells cannot target you. <gray>You cannot cast spells.</gray>'],
1518=>['Avatar of Balthazar','For 10...90 seconds, you gain +20 armor against physical damage, you gain adrenaline 25% faster, your attacks deal holy damage, and whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, nearby foes are set on fire for 1...3 seconds. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) You gain +20 armor against physical damage, you gain adrenaline 25% faster, your attacks deal holy damage, you inflict Burning (1...3 seconds) on nearby foes whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.'],
1519=>['Avatar of Dwayna','For 10...90 seconds, your attacks deal holy damage. Whenever you use a Dervish attack skill, you lose 1 hex. Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, all allies in earshot are healed for 5...50 Health. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) You deal holy damage. Whenever you use a Dervish attack skill, you lose 1 hex. Heal allies in earshot for 5...50 Health when you lose a Dervish enchantment. <gray>This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.</gray>'],
1520=>['Avatar of Grenth','For 10...90 seconds, your scythe attacks deal dark damage, and steal 0...12 Health. You are immune to Disease, and inflict Disease on all adjacent foes for 3 seconds whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) Your scythe attacks deal dark damage and steal 0...12 Health. You are immune to Disease. Apply Disease to all adjacent foes (3 seconds) when you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.'],
1521=>['Avatar of Lyssa','For 10...90 seconds, your Dervish enchantments recharge 50% faster and your attacks deal chaos damage. Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, steal 1 Energy from all nearby foes. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) Your Dervish enchantments recharge 50% faster and deal chaos damage with attacks. Steal 1 Energy from nearby foes when you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.'],
1522=>['Avatar of Melandru','For 10...90 seconds, you have +150 Health, +30 elemental armor, and your attacks deal earth damage. Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, all party members in earshot lose 1 condition. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) You have +150 maximum Health, +30 elemental armor, and your attacks deal earth damage. Cure 1 condition from all party members in earshot whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment. <gray>This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.</gray>'],
1523=>['Meditation','Lose all adrenaline. For 20 seconds, you gain 1...4 Energy every time an enchantment on you ends.','(20 seconds.) <gray>Lose all adrenaline.</gray> Gain 1...4 Energy whenever an enchantment on you ends.'],
1524=>['Eremite\'s Zeal','You gain 1...3 Energy for each foe within earshot, maximum 8 Energy. For 10 seconds afterward, this enchantment does nothing. When this enchantment ends, you gain 1...3 Energy for each foe within earshot, maximum 8 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Initial effect: you gain 1...3 Energy (maximum 8) for each foe in earshot. End effect: you gain 1...3 Energy (maximum 8) for each foe in earshot.'],
1525=>['Natural Healing','You are healed for 50...170 Health. If you are not enchanted, this spell activates 50% faster.','Heals you for 50...170. This skill activates 50% faster if you are not enchanted.'],
1526=>['Imbue Health','Target other ally is healed for 5...50% of your current Health (maximum 300 Health).','Heals for 5...50% of your current Health (maximum 300). <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1527=>['Mystic Healing','You are healed for 5...65 Health. Also heals all enchanted party members for 5...65 Health.','Heals you for 5...65. Heals all enchanted party members for 5...65 Health.'],
1528=>['Dwayna\'s Touch','Target touched ally is healed for 15...60 Health for each Enchantment on you (maximum 150).','Touch Spell. Heals for 15...60 (maximum 150) for each enchantment on you.'],
1529=>['Pious Restoration','You gain 80...150 Health and remove 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment was removed in this way, you also lose 1...2 hexes.','Gain 80...150 Health and remove 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal effect: lose 1...2 hexes.'],
1530=>['Signet of Pious Light','Remove 1 Dervish enchantment. Target ally is healed for 30...150 Health. If an enchantment was removed in this way, this signet recharges 75% faster.','Heals for 30...150. Removes one of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: recharges 75% faster.'],
1531=>['Intimidating Aura','For 60 seconds, you have +40...100 max Health and take 1...10 less damage from foes with less Health than you.','(60 seconds.) You have +40...100 max Health and take 1...10 damage from foes with less Health than you.'],
1532=>['Mystic Sandstorm','Create a sandstorm at your location that lasts 3 seconds. Each second, foes nearby this location take 10...20 earth damage. Attacking foes take an additional 10...20 damage. If you are enchanted when you cast this spell, it lasts twice as long.','(3 seconds.) Deals 10...20 earth damage each second. Deals an additional 10...20 damage to attacking foes. Hits foes nearby your initial location. Lasts twice as long if you are enchanted.'],
1533=>['Winds of Disenchantment','Lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If a Dervish enchantment was removed in this way, all nearby foes lose 1 enchantment and take 20...80 cold damage.','Remove one of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: all nearby foes lose 1 enchantment and take 20...80 cold damage.'],
1534=>['Rending Touch','Deals 15...65 cold damage to target foe. You lose one Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment was removed, target foe loses 1 enchantment and you gain 1 strike of adrenaline.','Touch Spell. Deals 15...65 cold damage. Lose 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal effect: target foe loses 1 enchantment and you gain 1 strike of adrenaline.'],
1535=>['Crippling Sweep','If this attack hits a foe, that foe is Crippled for 3...12 seconds. This skill deals +3...15 extra damage if that foe is moving.','(3...12 seconds.) Inflicts Cripple <sic/> condition. Deals +3...15 damage to moving foes.'],
1536=>['Wounding Strike','If this attack hits, you do +5...20 damage, target foe suffers from Bleeding for 5...20 seconds, and you lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment is removed, target foe also suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage and inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds). Remove 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal Effect: inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds).'],
1537=>['Wearying Strike','You remove 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment was removed, you inflict a Deep Wound for 3...10 seconds. You suffer from Weakness for 10 seconds if an enchantment is not removed.','Remove 1 Dervish Enchantment. Removal Effect: Inflicts Deep Wound condition (3...10 seconds). <gray>You are Weakened (10 seconds) if an enchantment is not lost.</gray>'],
1538=>['Lyssa\'s Assault','This attack interrupts an action if it hits. If you are enchanted, any skill you interrupt is disabled for additional 1...10 seconds. This attack does 50% normal damage.','Interrupts an action. If you are enchanted, the interrupted skill is disabled for an additional 1...10 seconds. This attack does 50% of normal damage.'],
1539=>['Chilling Victory','If it hits, this attack strikes for +3...15 damage. For each foe hit who has less Health than you, that foe and all adjacent foes are struck for 10...30 cold damage.','Deals +3...15 damage. Deals 10...30 cold damage to each foe hit who has less Health than you and foes adjacent to those targets.'],
1540=>['Conviction','For 10 seconds, you gain +10 armor if you have a condition and gain 1...3 Health regen <sic/> for each condition you are suffering from. When this enchantment ends, you are cured of 1...2 conditions.','(10 seconds.) Gain +10 armor while conditioned. Gain 1...3 Health regeneration for each condition you have. End Effect: Remove 1...2 conditions.'],
1541=>['Enchanted Haste','For 7 seconds, you move 25% faster. If this enchantment ends prematurely, you lose 1 condition.','(7 seconds). You move 25% faster. Lose 1 condition if this enchantment ends prematurely.'],
1542=>['Pious Concentration','For 5...20 seconds, you cannot be interrupted, but each time you would have been interrupted, you lose 1 Dervish enchantment or Pious Concentration ends.','(5...20 seconds.) Prevents interrupts. <gray>Prevention cost: you lose one Dervish enchantment or Pious Concentration ends.</gray>'],
1543=>['Pious Haste','You remove 1 Dervish enchantment and for 1...7 seconds you move 25% faster. If an enchantment was removed you move 50% faster instead.','(1...7 seconds.) Lose 1 Dervish enchantment and move 25% faster. Removal Effect: Run 50% faster instead.'],
1544=>['Whirling Charge','For 1...6 seconds, you move 33% faster than normal. The next time you strike a foe, all other nearby foes take 10...60 cold damage and this enchantment ends.','(1...6 seconds.) You move 33% faster. Deal 10...60 cold damage to all other nearby foes the next time you hit a foe and this enchantment ends.'],
1545=>['Test of Faith','Deals 15...65 cold damage and takes 1 enchantment from target foe. If that foe was not enchanted, that foe is Dazed for 1...4 seconds.','Touch Spell. Deals 15...65 cold damage and removes 1 enchantment. Target foe is Dazed for 1...4 seconds if that foe was not enchanted.'],
1546=>['Blazing Spear','If this attack hits, it deals +5...25 damage and sets target foe on Fire <sic/> for 1...3 seconds.','Deals +5...25 damage. Inflicts Burning condition (1...3 seconds).'],
1547=>['Mighty Throw','Your spear moves three times faster. If it hits, you deal +10...40 damage.','Deals +10...40 damage. This spear moves three times faster.'],
1548=>['Cruel Spear','If this attack hits, you deal +1...31 damage. If it hits a non-moving target, you inflict a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +1...31 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if target is not moving.'],
1549=>['Harrier\'s Toss','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If this attack hits a moving foe, it deals an additional 5...30 damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals 5...30 more damage if target is moving.'],
1550=>['Unblockable Throw','If this attack hits, you deal +10...40 damage. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...40 damage. Unblockable.'],
1551=>['Spear of Lightning','If this attack hits, it deals +8...20 lightning damage. This attack has 25% armor penetration.','Deals +8...20 lightning damage. 25% armor penetration.'],
1552=>['Wearying Spear','If this attack hits, you deal +10...40 damage. You are Weakened for 5 seconds.','Deals +10...40 damage. <gray>You are Weakened (5 seconds).</gray>'],
1553=>['Anthem of Fury','For 10 seconds, all party members within earshot gain 1...4 strikes of adrenaline the next time they use an attack skill.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 1...4 adrenaline with their next attack skill.'],
1554=>['Crippling Anthem','For 10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot causes Crippling for 5...15 seconds.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot inflict Crippled condition (5...15 seconds) with their next attack skill.'],
1555=>['Defensive Anthem','For 4...10 seconds, each party member within earshot has a 50% chance to block incoming attacks. This chant ends if that party member hits with an attack skill.','(4...10 seconds.) Party members in earshot have 50% chance to block. <gray>Ends when hitting with an attack skill.</gray>'],
1556=>['Godspeed','For 5...20 seconds, all allies within earshot move 25% faster while under the effects of an enchantment.','(5...20 seconds.) Allies in earshot move 25% faster while enchanted.'],
1557=>['Anthem of Flame','For 10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each party member within earshot also causes Burning for 1...3 seconds.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot inflict Burning condition (1...3 seconds) with their next attack skill.'],
1558=>['"Go for the Eyes!"','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot makes an attack, that attack has an additional 30...100% chance to critical.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot have +30...100% to land a critical hit with their next attack.'],
1559=>['Anthem of Envy','For 10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot deals +10...25 damage against foes with more than 50% Health.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot do +10...25 damage with their next attack skill. <gray>Damage bonus only applies to foes with more than 50% Health.</gray>'],
1560=>['Song of Power','For 5...20 seconds, each ally within earshot gains 4 Energy regeneration until that ally uses a Skill.','(5...20 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain +4 Energy regeneration. <gray>Ends when using a skill.</gray>'],
1561=>['Zealous Anthem','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot uses an attack skill, that ally gains 1...8 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain 1...8 Energy with their next attack skill.'],
1562=>['Aria of Zeal','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot uses a Spell, that ally gains 1...6 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain 1...6 Energy with their next spell.'],
1563=>['Lyric of Zeal','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot uses a signet, that ally gains 1...8 Energy.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain 1...8 Energy with their next signet.'],
1564=>['Ballad of Restoration','For 10 seconds, the next time each party member within earshot takes damage, that party member gains 15...75 Health.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 15...75 Health the next time they take damage.'],
1565=>['Chorus of Restoration','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot uses a shout or chant, that ally is healed for 30...90 Health.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot are healed for 30...90 with their next shout or chant.'],
1566=>['Aria of Restoration','For 10 seconds, the next time each party member within earshot uses a spell, that party member gains 30...90 Health.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 30...90 Health with their next spell.'],
1567=>['Song of Concentration','For 10 seconds, the next skill used by each ally within earshot cannot be interrupted.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot are uninterruptible with their next skill.'],
1568=>['Anthem of Guidance','For 10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each party member within earshot cannot be blocked.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot are unblockable with their next attack skill.'],
1569=>['Energizing Chorus','For 10 seconds, the next Shout or Chant used by each ally within earshot costs 3...7 less Energy.','(10 seconds.) The next shout or chant costs 3...7 less Energy for allies within earshot.'],
1570=>['Song of Purification','For 20 seconds, the next 1...3 skills used by each ally within earshot remove 1 condition from that ally.','(20 seconds.) Allies in earshot lose one condition with their next 1...3 skills.'],
1571=>['Hexbreaker Aria','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot casts a spell, that ally loses 1 hex.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot lose one hex with their next spell.'],
1572=>['"Brace Yourself!"','For 5...15 seconds, the next time target other ally would be knocked down, all nearby foes take 15...75 damage instead.','(5...15 seconds.) Prevents the next knock-down and deals 15...75 damage to all foes near target ally. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1573=>['Awe','If this skill hits a knocked-down foe, that foe becomes Dazed for 5...15 seconds. Awe has half the normal range.','Half Range Skill. Inflicts Dazed condition (5...15 seconds). <gray>No effect unless target is knocked-down.</gray>'],
1574=>['Enduring Harmony','For 10...35 seconds, chants and shouts last 50% longer on target non-spirit ally.','(10...35 seconds.) Chants and shouts last 50% longer on target ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1575=>['Blazing Finale','For 10...35 seconds, whenever a chant or shout ends on target non-spirit ally, all foes adjacent to that ally are set on Fire for 1...7 seconds.','(10...35 seconds.) Inflicts Burning condition (1...7 seconds) to adjacent foes whenever a chant or shout ends on target ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1576=>['Burning Refrain','For 20 seconds, if target non-spirit ally hits a foe with more Health than that ally, that foe is set on Fire <sic/> for 1...3 seconds. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(20 seconds.) Inflicts Burning condition (1...3 seconds) if target ally hits a foe with more Health. Renewal: Whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1577=>['Finale of Restoration','For 10...35 seconds, whenever a chant or shout ends on target non-spirit ally, that ally is healed for 15...75 Health.','(10...35 seconds.) Target ally gains <sic/> 15...75 Health whenever a shout or chant ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1578=>['Mending Refrain','For 15 seconds, target non-spirit ally has +2...3 Health regeneration. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(15 seconds.) Target ally has +2...3 Health regeneration. Renewal: whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1579=>['Purifying Finale','For 10...35 seconds, target non-spirit ally loses 1 condition whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(10...35 seconds.) Target ally loses one condition whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1580=>['Bladeturn Refrain','For 20 seconds, target non-spirit ally has a 5...20% chance to block incoming attacks. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(20 seconds.) Target ally has 5...20% chance to block. Renewal: Whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1581=>['Glowing Signet','If target foe is Burning, you gain 5...15 Energy.','You gain 5...15 Energy if target foe is Burning.'],
1583=>['Leader\'s Zeal','For each nearby ally, you gain 2 Energy (maximum 8...12 Energy).','You gain 2 Energy (maximum 8...12 Energy) for each nearby ally.'],
1584=>['Leader\'s Comfort','You gain 30...75 Health. For each ally within earshot, you also gain +10...20 Health (maximum 140 Health).','You gain 30...75 Health. You also gain 10...20 Health (maximum 140) for each ally in earshot.'],
1585=>['Signet of Synergy','Target other ally is healed for 40...100 Health. If you are not under the effects of an enchantment, you are also healed for 40...100 Health.','Heal target ally for 40...100. You are also healed for 40...100 if you are not enchanted. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1586=>['Angelic Protection','For 10 seconds, any time target other ally takes more than 250...100 damage per second, that ally is healed for any damage over that amount.','(10 seconds.) Each second that target ally takes damage over 250...100, that ally is healed for any damage over that amount. <gray>Cannot self target.</gray>'],
1587=>['Angelic Bond','For 10 seconds, the next time an ally within earshot would take fatal damage, that damage is negated and that ally is healed for 20...200 Health. Angelic Bond ends on all other allies.','(10 seconds.) The next time an ally within earshot would take fatal damage, that damage is negated and that ally is healed for 20...200. <gray>Ends on other allies.</gray>'],
1588=>['Cautery Signet','All party members lose all conditions. You are set on Fire <sic/> for 1 second for each condition removed in this way.','All party members lose all conditions. <gray>You begin Burning (one second for each condition removed).</gray>'],
1589=>['"Stand Your Ground!"','For 5...20 seconds, all party members within earshot receive +24 armor when not moving.','(5...20 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain +24 armor when not moving.'],
1590=>['"Lead the Way!"','Target ally moves 25% faster for 1...5 seconds for each ally within earshot (maximum of 20 seconds).','Target ally moves 25% faster for 1...5 seconds (maximum of 20 seconds) for each ally in earshot.'],
1591=>['"Make Haste!"','For 5...20 seconds, target other ally moves 33% faster. This skill ends if that ally successfully hits with an attack.','(5...20 seconds.) Target ally moves 33% faster. <gray>Ends if target ally hits with an attack. Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1592=>['"We Shall Return!"','All party members in earshot are resurrected with 25...50% Health and 5...20% Energy.','All party members in earshot are resurrected (25...50% Health and 5...20% Energy).'],
1593=>['"Never Give Up!"','All allies within earshot and below 75% Health gain 1...10 Energy.','Allies in earshot gain 1...10 Energy. <gray>Only affects allies below 75% Health.</gray>'],
1594=>['"Help Me!"','You gain 15...90 Health. For 1...10 seconds, other allies\' spells targeting you cast 50% faster.','(1...10 seconds.) Other allies\' spells targeting you cast 50% faster. You gain 15...90 Health.'],
1595=>['"Fall Back!"','For 4...10 seconds, all allies within earshot gain 5...15 Health per second while moving and move 33% faster. "Fall Back!" ends on an ally affected by this shout when that ally successfully hits with an attack.','(4...10 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain 5...15 Health per second while moving and move 33% faster. <gray>Ends for an ally if that ally hits with an attack.</gray>'],
1596=>['"Incoming!"','For 4...10 seconds, all allies within earshot move 33% faster, and gain 5...15 Health while moving.','(4...10 seconds) Allies in earshot move 33% faster and gain 5...15 Health while moving.'],
1597=>['"They\'re on Fire!"','For 10 seconds, party members within earshot take 5...35% less damage from foes suffering from Burning.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot take 5...35% less damage from Burning foes.'],
1598=>['"Never Surrender!"','For 15 seconds, all party members within earshot and below 75% Health gain +1...5 Health regeneration.','(15 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain +1...5 Health regeneration. <gray>Only affects party members below 75% Health.</gray>'],
1599=>['"It\'s Just a Flesh Wound."','Target other ally loses all conditions. If a condition was removed in this way, that ally moves 25% faster for 1...10 seconds.','Remove all conditions from target ally. That ally moves 25% faster (1...10 seconds) if a condition was removed. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1600=>['Barbed Spear','If this attack hits, your target begins Bleeding for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds).'],
1601=>['Vicious Attack','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If you land a critical hit with this attack, target foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...15 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...15 seconds) with a critical hit.'],
1602=>['Stunning Strike','If this attack hits, you deal +5...30 damage. If it hits a foe suffering from a condition, that foe is also Dazed for 4...10 seconds.','Deals +5...30 damage. Inflicts Dazed condition (4...10 seconds) if target has a condition.'],
1603=>['Merciless Spear','If this attack hits a foe with less than 50% Health, that foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>No effect unless target has less than 50% Health.</gray>'],
1604=>['Disrupting Throw','If this attack hits a foe suffering from a condition, that foe is interrupted.','Interrupts actions. <gray>No effect unless target has a condition.</gray>'],
1605=>['Wild Throw','If this attack hits, it deals +5...20 damage, and any stance being used by your target ends. This attack cannot be blocked. All of your non-spear attack skills are disabled for 3 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Unblockable. Ends target\'s stance. <gray>Disables <sic/> your non-spear attack skills for 3 seconds.</gray>'],
1633=>['Malicious Strike','If this attack hits a foe suffering from a condition, you deal +10...30 damage and this attack results in a critical hit.','If target foe has a condition, this attack deals +10...30 damage and is a critical hit.'],
1634=>['Shattering Assault','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, you deal 5...50 damage and target foe loses one enchantment. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals 5...50 damage. Removes one enchantment. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
1635=>['Golden Skull Strike','If you are under the effects of an enchantment and this attack hits, target foe is Dazed 1...5 seconds.','Inflicts Dazed condition (1...5 seconds). <gray>No effect unless you are enchanted.</gray>'],
1636=>['Black Spider Strike','Must strike a hexed foe. If it hits, this attack strikes for +5...20 damage and target foe is Poisoned for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Inflicts Poisoned condition (5...20 seconds). <gray>Must strike a hexed foe.</gray>'],
1637=>['Golden Fox Strike','If this attack hits, target foe takes +10...30 damage. If you are under the effects of an Enchantment, this attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...30 damage. Unblockable if you are Enchanted.'],
1638=>['Deadly Haste','For 10...35 seconds, half-ranged spells cast 5...50% faster and recharge 5...50% faster.','(10...35 seconds.) Your half-ranged spells cast 5...50% faster and recharge 5...50% faster.'],
1639=>['Assassin\'s Remedy','For 30 seconds, the next 1...10 attack skills you use remove one condition.','(30 seconds.) Your next 1...10 attack skills each remove one condition.'],
1640=>['Fox\'s Promise','For 5...20 seconds, your dagger attacks cannot be blocked. This enchantment ends the next time you fail to hit.','(5...20 seconds.) Your dagger attacks are unblockable. <gray>Ends the next time you fail to hit.</gray>'],
1641=>['Feigned Neutrality','For 4...10 seconds, you have +7 Health regeneration and +80 armor. This enchantment ends if you successfully hit with an attack or use a skill.','(4...10 seconds.) You have +7 Health regeneration and +80 armor. <gray>Ends if you hit with an attack or use a skill.</gray>'],
1642=>['Hidden Caltrops','Your non-Assassin skills are disabled for 10 seconds. For 1...10 seconds, target foe moves 50% slower. When this hex ends that foe is Crippled for 1...15 seconds.','(1...10 seconds.) Causes 50% slower movement. End effect: inflicts Crippled condition (1...15 seconds). Your non-Assassin skills are disabled (10 seconds.)'],
1643=>['Assault Enchantments','Must follow a dual attack. Target foe loses all enchantments.','Removes all enchantments. <gray>Must follow a dual attack.</gray>'],
1644=>['Wastrel\'s Collapse','Shadow Step to target foe. If target foe is not using a skill, that foe is knocked down. All of your non-dagger attack skills are disabled for 10 seconds.','Shadow Step to target foe. Causes knock-down if target foe is not using a skill. <gray>Disables your non-dagger attack skills (10 seconds).</gray>'],
1645=>['Lift Enchantment','If target touched foe is knocked down, that foe loses one enchantment.','Removes one enchantment. <gray>No <sic/> effect unless target foe is knocked-down.</gray>'],
1646=>['Augury of Death','For 5...35 seconds, the next time damage would drop target foe\'s Health below 50%, you inflict a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds and Shadow Step to that foe. This spell has half the normal range.','Half Range Hex Spell. (5...35 seconds.) Inflict Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) and Shadow Step to target foe the next time damage would drop this foe\'s Health below 50%.'],
1647=>['Signet of Toxic Shock','If target foe is suffering from Poison, that foe takes 10...100 damage.','Deals 10...100 damage. <gray>No effect unless target foe is Poisoned</gray>'],
1648=>['Signet of Twilight','For each hex on target foe, that foe loses one enchantment.','Removes one enchantment for each hex on target foe.'],
1649=>['Way of the Assassin','For the next 20 seconds while wielding daggers, you attack 5...20% faster and have a +5...35% chance to land a critical hit.','(20 seconds.) While wielding daggers, you attack 5...20% faster and have +5...35% chance to land a critical hit.'],
1650=>['Shadow Walk','Shadow Step to target foe. For 15 seconds nothing happens. Your attack skills are disabled for 1 second, and your stances and enchantments are disabled for 10 seconds. When this stance ends, you return to your original location.','(15 seconds.) Shadow Step to target foe. End effect: return to your original location. <gray>Disables your attack skills for 1 second. Disables your stances and enchantments for 10 seconds.</gray>'],
1651=>['Death\'s Retreat','Shadow Step to target ally. If you have less Health than that ally, you gain 40...130 Health.','Gain 40...130 Health if you have less Health than target ally. Initial effect: Shadow Step to this ally. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1652=>['Shadow Prison','Shadow Step to target foe. For 1...7 seconds, that foe moves 66% slower.','Shadow Step to target foe. This foe moves 66% slower (1...7 seconds).'],
1653=>['Swap','You and target summoned creature Shadow Step to each other\'s location.','You and target summoned creature Shadow Step to each other\'s locations.'],
1654=>['Shadow Meld','Shadow Step to target other ally. When you stop maintaining this Enchantment, you return to your original location.','Shadow Step to target ally. End effect: return to your original location. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1655=>['Price of Pride','For 5...20 seconds, the next time target foe uses an elite skill, that foe loses 1...7 Energy.','(5...20 seconds.) Causes 1...7 Energy loss the next time target foe uses an elite skill.'],
1656=>['Air of Disenchantment','Remove one enchantment from target foe and all nearby foes. For 5...20 seconds, enchantments expire 150...300% faster on those foes.','Also hexes foes near your target (5...20 seconds). Remove one enchantment from target and nearby foes. Enchantments expire 150...300% faster on those foes.'],
1657=>['Signet of Clumsiness','If target foe is attacking, that foe and all adjacent foes are interrupted and take 15...60 damage. Any foes using attack skills are knocked down.','Interrupts an attack for target foe and all adjacent foes. Interruption effect: deals 15...60 damage; knocks down foes using attack skills.'],
1658=>['Symbolic Posture','For 5...20 seconds, the next signet you activate recharges 20...80% faster.','(5...20 seconds.) Your next signet recharges 20...80% faster.'],
1659=>['Toxic Chill','Target foe is struck for 15...75 cold damage. If that foe is under the effects of a hex or enchantment, that foe becomes Poisoned for 10...25 seconds.','Deals 15...75 cold damage. Inflicts Poisoned condition (10...25 seconds) if target foe is hexed or enchanted.'],
1660=>['Well of Silence','Exploit target corpse to create a Well of Silence for 10...30 seconds. Foes within the well cannot use shouts or chants and suffer -1...4 Health degeneration.','(10...30 seconds.) Foes in this well cannot use shouts and chants and have -1...4 Health degeneration. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse.</gray>'],
1661=>['Glowstone','Send a projectile that strikes for 5...50 earth damage if it hits. If this spell hits a weakened <sic/> foe, you gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage.','Projectile: deals 5...50 earth damage. You gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage if target foe is Weakened.'],
1662=>['Mind Blast','Target foe is struck for 15...60 fire damage. If you have more Energy than target foe, you gain 1...8 Energy.','Deals 15...60 fire damage. You gain 1...8 Energy if you have more Energy than target foe.'],
1663=>['Elemental Flame','For 10...35 seconds, whenever you apply an Elemental hex to a foe, that foe is set on fire for 1...5 seconds.','(10...35 seconds.) Inflicts Burning condition (1...5 seconds) whenever you apply an Elemental hex to a target.'],
1664=>['Invoke Lightning','Target foe and up to two other foes near your target are struck for 10...90 lightning damage. This spell has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...90 lightning damage. Hits two foes near target. 25% armor penetration.'],
1683=>['Pensive Guardian','For 5...11 seconds, target ally has a 50% chance to block attacks from enchanted foes.','(5...11 seconds.) 50% chance to block enchanted foes.'],
1684=>['Scribe\'s Insight','For 10...35 seconds, you gain 3 Energy whenever you use a Signet.','(10...35 seconds.) You gain 3 Energy whenever you use a signet.'],
1685=>['Holy Haste','For 1...60 seconds, your Healing Prayers spells cast 50% faster. This enchantment ends if you cast another enchantment.','(1...60 seconds.) Your Healing Prayers spells cast 50% faster. <gray>Ends if you cast an enchantment.</gray>'],
1686=>['Glimmer of Light','Heal target ally for 10...115 Health.','Heals for 10...115.'],
1687=>['Zealous Benediction','Heal target ally for 30...180 Health. If target was below 50% Health, you gain 7 Energy.','Heals for 30...180. You gain 7 Energy if target ally was below 50% Health.'],
1688=>['Defender\'s Zeal','For 5...25 seconds, whenever target foe hits with an attack, you gain 2 Energy.','(5...25 seconds.) You gain 2 Energy whenever target foe hits with an attack.'],
1689=>['Signet of Mystic Wrath','Target foe takes 5...35 holy damage for each enchantment on you (maximum 100 holy damage).','Deals 5...35 holy damage for each enchantment on you (maximum 100 holy damage).'],
1690=>['Signet of Removal','If target ally is under the effects of an enchantment, that ally loses one hex and one condition.','Removes one hex and one condition. <gray>No effect unless target ally is enchanted.</gray>'],
1691=>['Dismiss Condition','Remove one condition from target ally. If that ally is under the effects of an enchantment, that ally is healed for 15...75 Health.','Removes one condition. Heals for 15...75 if target ally is enchanted.'],
1692=>['Divert Hexes','Remove up to 1...3 hexes from target ally. For each hex removed in this way, that ally loses one condition and gains 15...75 Health.','Removes 1...3 hexes. For each hex removed, target ally loses one condition and gains 15...75 Health.'],
1693=>['Counterattack','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...35 damage. If you hit an attacking foe, you gain 2...6 Energy.','Deals +5...35 damage. You gain 2...6 Energy if target foe is attacking.'],
1694=>['Magehunter Strike','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. If your target is under the effects of an enchantment, this attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +5...20 damage. Unblockable if target foe is enchanted.'],
1695=>['Soldier\'s Strike','If this attack hits, you deal +10...40 more damage. If you are under the effects of a chant or shout, this attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...40 damage. Unblockable if you are under the effects of a chant or shout.'],
1696=>['Decapitate','You lose all adrenaline and all Energy. If this attack hits, you deal +5...50 damage and cause a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds. This attack always results in a critical hit.','Deals +5...50 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds). Automatic critical hit. <gray>You lose all adrenaline and Energy.</gray>'],
1697=>['Magehunter\'s Smash','If this attack hits, target foe is knocked down. If your target is under the effects of an enchantment, this attack cannot be blocked.','Causes knock-down. Unblockable if target foe is enchanted.'],
1698=>['Soldier\'s Stance','For 5...15 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block. You attack 33% faster while under the effects of a shout or chant.','(5...15 seconds.) You have a 75% chance to block. You attack 33% faster while under the effects of a chant or shout.'],
1699=>['Soldier\'s Defense','For 1...6 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block attacks while under the effects of a shout or chant. You gain 1 strike of adrenaline for each blocked attack.','(1...6 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block while under the effects of a shout or chant. Block effect: gain 1 adrenaline.'],
1700=>['Frenzied Defense','For 8 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks, but take double damage.','(8 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. <gray>You take double damage.</gray>'],
1701=>['Steady Stance','For 10 seconds, the next time you would be knocked down, you gain 1...3 strikes of adrenaline and 1...7 Energy instead.','(10 seconds.) The next time you would be knocked-down, you gain 1...3 adrenaline and 1...7 Energy instead.'],
1702=>['Steelfang Slash','If this attack hits, you deal +1...31 damage. If you hit a foe that is knocked down, you gain 1...5 adrenaline.','Deals +1...31 damage. You gain 1...5 adrenaline if target foe is knocked down.'],
1719=>['Screaming Shot','If this attack hits, you deal +10...25 damage. If your target is within earshot, that foe begins Bleeding for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +10...25 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe is within earshot.'],
1720=>['Keen Arrow','If this attack hits, you strike for +5...20 damage. If you land a critical hit, you deal an additional +5...25 damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals +5...25 more damage if you land a critical hit.'],
1721=>['Rampage as One','For 3...15 seconds, both you and your animal companion attack 33% faster and run 25% faster.','(3...15 seconds.) You and your pet attack 33% faster and move 25% faster. <gray>No effect unless your pet is alive.</gray>'],
1722=>['Forked Arrow','Shoot two arrows simultaneously at target foe. If you are under the effects of an enchantment or hex, you shoot only one arrow.','You shoot two arrows simultaneously. <gray>Shoot only one arrow if you are enchanted or hexed.</gray>'],
1723=>['Disrupting Accuracy','For 36 seconds, whenever your arrows critical, they also interrupt your target.','(36 seconds.) Interrupts an action whenever your arrows critical.'],
1724=>['Expert\'s Dexterity','For 1...20 seconds, you attack 33% faster and your Marksmanship attribute is increased by 2.','(1...20 seconds.) You attack 33% faster and you gain +2 to your Marksmanship attribute.'],
1725=>['Roaring Winds','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Chants and shouts cost 1...5 more Energy. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Chants and shouts cost 1...5 more Energy for creatures in range.'],
1726=>['Magebane Shot','If this attack hits, it interrupts target foe\'s action. If that action was a spell, it is disabled for an additional 10 seconds. This attack cannot be blocked.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: an interrupted spell is disabled for +10 seconds. Unblockable.'],
1727=>['Natural Stride','For 1...8 seconds, you run 33% faster and have a 50% chance to block incoming attacks. Natural Stride ends if you become hexed or enchanted.','(1...8 seconds.) You move 33% faster and have 50% chance to block. <gray>Ends if you become hexed or enchanted.</gray>'],
1728=>['Heket\'s Rampage','For 5...11 seconds, you attack 33% faster. This stance ends if you use an attack skill.','(5...11 seconds). You attack 33% faster. <gray>Ends if you use an attack skill.</gray>'],
1729=>['Smoke Trap','When Smoke Trap is triggered, nearby foes are Blinded and Dazed for 5...10 seconds. Smoke Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Inflicts Blinded and Dazed conditions (5...10 seconds) to nearby foes. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
1730=>['Infuriating Heat','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit creatures within its range gain adrenaline twice as fast. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Doubles adrenaline gain for creatures in range.'],
1731=>['Vocal Was Sogolon','For 60 seconds, all shouts and chants you use last 20...50% longer.','(60 seconds.) Shouts and chants you use last 20...50% longer.'],
1732=>['Destructive Was Glaive','Hold Glaive\'s ashes for up to 30...60 seconds. While you hold her ashes, all Ritualist skills have 20% armor penetration. When you drop her ashes, all foes in the area are struck for 15...85 lightning damage.','(30...60 seconds.) Your Ritualist skills have 20% armor penetration. Drop effect: deals 15...85 lightning damage to all foes in the area.'],
1733=>['Wielder\'s Strike','Target foe is struck for 5...50 lightning damage. If you are under the effects of a weapon spell, you deal an additional 10...40 lightning damage.','Deals 5...50 lightning damage. Deals 10...40 more lightning damage if you are under a weapon spell.'],
1734=>['Gaze of Fury','Destroy target spirit and create a level 1...14 Spirit of Fury. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Destroys a spirit. Creates a level 1...14 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage.'],
1736=>['Spirit\'s Strength','For 15...60 seconds, your attacks deal 5...35 more damage while under the effects of a weapon spell.','(15...60 seconds.) Your attacks deal +5...35 damage if you are under a weapon spell.'],
1737=>['Wielder\'s Zeal','For 10...30 seconds, whenever you cast a Weapon Spell on an ally, you gain 1...5 Energy.','(10...30 seconds.) You gain 1...5 Energy whenever you cast a weapon spell.'],
1738=>['Sight Beyond Sight','For 8...20 seconds, you cannot be Blinded.','(8...20 seconds). You are immune to Blindness.'],
1739=>['Renewing Memories','For 5...20 seconds, while holding an item, any weapon and item Spells you cast cost 5...35% less Energy.','(5...20 seconds.) Your weapon and item spells cost 5...35% less Energy. <gray>No effect unless holding an item.</gray>'],
1740=>['Wielder\'s Remedy','For 10...30 seconds, whenever you cast a weapon spell on an ally, that ally loses 1 condition.','(10...30 seconds.) Whenever you cast a weapon spell, the targeted ally loses one condition.'],
1741=>['Ghostmirror Light','Target other ally is healed for 15...90 Health. If you are within earshot of a spirit, you are also healed for 15...90 Health.','Heals for 15...90. You gain 15...90 Health if you are within earshot of a spirit. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
1742=>['Signet of Ghostly Might','For 5...20 seconds, all spirits you control within earshot attack 33% faster and deal 5...10 additional damage.','(5...20 seconds.) All spirits you control within earshot attack 33% faster and deal +5...10 damage.'],
1743=>['Signet of Binding','You lose 200...50 Health and take control of target enemy-controlled spirit. (50% failure chance with Spawning Power 4 or less.)','You lose 200...50 Health. Gain control of target enemy-controlled spirit. <gray>50% failure chance unless Spawning Power 5 or more.</gray>'],
1744=>['Caretaker\'s Charge','Target foe is struck for 20...75 lightning damage. If you are holding an item, you gain 5 Energy and 5...50 Health.','Deals 20...75 lightning damage. You gain 5 Energy and 5...50 Health if you are holding an item.'],
1745=>['Anguish','Create a level 1...11 spirit. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage and deal double damage to hexed foes. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...11 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage. Double damage to hexed foes.'],
1747=>['Empowerment','Create a level 1...14 spirit. All allies within its range holding an item gain 15...45 maximum Health and 10 maximum Energy. This spirit dies after 15...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (15...60 second lifespan). Allies in range holding an item gain 15...45 maximum Health and 10 maximum Energy.'],
1748=>['Recovery','Create a level 1...14 spirit. Conditions on allies within range of this spirit expire 20...50% faster. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...14 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Conditions on allies in range expire 20...50% faster.'],
1749=>['Weapon of Fury','For 5...20 seconds, target ally gains 5...50% more adrenaline and 1 Energy whenever that ally successfully hits with an attack.','(5...20 seconds.) 5...50% more adrenaline gain and +1 Energy whenever target ally hits with an attack.'],
1750=>['Xinrae\'s Weapon','For 8 seconds, the next time target ally takes damage from a foe that damage is limited to 5% of that ally\'s max Health and that ally steals up to 20...80 Health from that foe.','(8 seconds). The next time target ally takes damage from a foe, that damage is limited to 5% of target ally\'s max Health and that ally steals 20...80 Health from that foe.'],
1751=>['Warmonger\'s Weapon','For 3...13 seconds, if target ally attacks a foe who is not attacking, that foe is interrupted.','(3...13 seconds.) Attacks interrupt an action. Does not interrupt attacking foes.'],
1752=>['Weapon of Remedy','For 8 seconds, the next time target ally takes damage or life steal from a foe, that ally steals up to 15...75 Health from that foe and loses 1 condition.','(8 seconds.) The next time target ally takes damage or life steal from a foe, this ally steals 15...75 Health from that foe and loses 1 condition.'],
1753=>['Rending Sweep','You deal +5...20 and lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment was lost, you remove an enchantment from each foe you hit.','Deals +5...20 damage. You lose 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal effect: struck foes lose an enchantment.'],
1754=>['Onslaught','For 3...15 seconds, you attack, move and gain adrenaline 25% faster.','(3...15 seconds.) You attack, move and gain adrenaline 25% faster.'],
1755=>['Mystic Corruption','All adjacent foes suffer from Disease for 1...2 seconds. For 20 seconds, nothing happens. Disease duration is doubled if you are enchanted when you activate this skill. When this enchantment ends, all party members in earshot are cured of Disease.','(20 seconds.) Initial Effect: all adjacent foes are Diseased (1...2 seconds.) Double duration if you are already enchanted. End Effect: party members in earshot lose Disease.'],
1756=>['Grenth\'s Grasp','For 20 seconds, if you are wielding a cold weapon, your attack skills also Cripple that <sic/> foe for 1...11 seconds and you transfer 1 condition from yourself to that foe.','(20 seconds.) Inflicts Crippled condition (1...11 seconds) with your attack skills and transfer 1 condition. <gray>No effect unless wielding a cold weapon.</gray>'],
1757=>['Veil of Thorns','When you cast this enchantment, all nearby foes are struck for 5...50 piercing damage. For 5...25 seconds you take 5...35% less damage from spells.','(5...25 seconds.) Spell damage is reduced by 5...35%. Initial Effect: nearby foes are struck for 5...50 piercing damage.'],
1758=>['Harrier\'s Grasp','For 5...20 seconds, attacks against moving foes also Cripple that foe for 2...9 seconds. This enchantment ends after you apply Cripple 1...3 times. <sic/> When you cast this spell, you lose Cripple and 1 other condition.','(5...20 seconds.) Attacks on moving foes also Cripple them. <sic/> <gray>Ends after you apply Cripple 1...3 times. <sic/> </gray> Initial Effect: you lose Cripple and 1 other condition.'],
1759=>['Vow of Strength','For 15 seconds, whenever you attack a foe with your scythe, you deal 10...25 slashing damage to all adjacent foes.','(15 seconds.) When you attack with a scythe, deals 10...25 slashing damage to adjacent foes.'],
1760=>['Ebon Dust Aura','When you cast this enchantment, all nearby foes are Blinded for 1...7 seconds. For 30 seconds, if you are wielding an earth weapon, your melee attacks deal +3...15 earth damage. When this enchantment ends, you are cured of Blindness.','(30 seconds.) Deal +3...15 earth damage with your melee attacks. Initial Effect: Blinds nearby foes for 1...7 seconds. End Effect: removes Blindness. <gray>No effect unless wielding an earth weapon.</gray>'],
1761=>['Zealous Vow','For 20 seconds, you have -3 Energy regeneration, and you gain 1...6 Energy every time you hit with an attack.','(20 seconds.) You gain 1...6 Energy each time you hit with an attack. <gray>You have -3 Energy regeneration.</gray>'],
1762=>['Heart of Fury','For 2...10 seconds, you attack 25% faster.','(2...10 seconds.) You attack 25% faster.'],
1763=>['Zealous Renewal','All nearby foes take 5...30 holy damage. For 5...25 seconds, you have -1 Energy regeneration, and gain 1 Energy whenever you hit a foe. If this enchantment ends prematurely, you gain 1...5 Energy.','(5...25 seconds.) Initial effect: deals 5...30 holy damage to nearby foes. You have -1 Energy regeneration and gain 1 Energy when you hit. Gain 1...5 Energy if this enchantment ends early.'],
1764=>['Attacker\'s Insight','For 3...10 seconds you have a 50% chance to block while attacking. When this enchantment ends, you inflict Weakness on all adjacent foes for 3...15 seconds.','(3...10 seconds.) Gives 50% block chance while attacking. End Effect: Causes Weakness 3...15 seconds to adjacent foes.'],
1765=>['Rending Aura','When you cast this enchantment, all nearby foes take 10...40 cold damage. For 30 <sic/> seconds, your attack skills remove enchantments from knocked-down foes. When this enchantment ends, nearby foes are affected by Cracked Armor for 1...10 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Your attack skills remove enchantments from knocked-down foes. Initial effect: deals 10...40 cold damage to all nearby foes. End effect: nearby foes have Cracked Armor for 1...10 seconds.'],
1766=>['Featherfoot Grace','For 5...20 seconds, you move 25% faster, and conditions expire 25% faster.','(5...20 seconds.) You move 25% faster, and conditions expire 25% faster.'],
1767=>['Reaper\'s Sweep','If this attack hits, you Cripple your target for 3...15 seconds. You lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment was removed, this attack knocks down for 2...3 seconds.','(3...15 seconds.) Cause Cripple. Lose 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal Effect: cause knockdown for 2...3 seconds.'],
1768=>['Harrier\'s Haste','For 2...8 seconds, you move 25% faster and deal +3...12 more damage against moving foes.','(2...8 seconds.) You move 25% faster and deal +3...12 damage to moving foes.'],
1769=>['Focused Anger','For 45 seconds, you gain 0...150% more adrenaline.','(45 seconds.) You gain 0...150% more adrenaline.'],
1770=>['Natural Temper','For 4...10 seconds, you gain 33% more adrenaline while not under the effects of an Enchantment.','(4...10 seconds.) You gain 33% more adrenaline. <gray>No effect if you are enchanted.</gray>'],
1771=>['Song of Restoration','For 10 seconds, the next time each party member within earshot uses a skill, that party member gains 45...110 Health.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 45...110 Health with their next skill.'],
1772=>['Lyric of Purification','For 5...20 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot uses a Signet, that ally loses 1 Condition.','(5...20 seconds.) Allies in earshot lose one condition with their next signet.'],
1773=>['Soldier\'s Fury','For 10...35 seconds, if you are under the effects of a chant or a shout, you attack 33% faster and gain 33% more adrenaline, but you have -20 armor.','(10...35 seconds.) You attack 33% faster and gain 33% more adrenaline if under the effects of a shout or chant. <gray>You have -20 armor.</gray>'],
1774=>['Aggressive Refrain','For 5...25 seconds, you attack 25% faster but have -20 armor. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on you.','(5...25 seconds.) You attack 25% faster. Renewal: whenever a chant or shout ends on you. <gray>You have -20 armor.</gray>'],
1775=>['Energizing Finale','For 10...35 seconds, whenever a shout or chant ends on target non-spirit ally, that ally gains 1 Energy.','(10...35 seconds.) Target ally gains 1 Energy whenever a shout or chant ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
1776=>['Signet of Aggression','If you are under the effects of a shout or chant, you gain 2 strikes of adrenaline.','You gain 2 adrenaline if you are under the effects of a shout or chant.'],
1777=>['Remedy Signet','You lose 1 condition.','You lose one condition.'],
1778=>['Signet of Return','Resurrect target party member with 5...15% Health and 1...4% Energy for each party member within earshot.','Resurrects target party member (5...15% Health and 1...4% Energy for each party member in earshot).'],
1779=>['"Make Your Time!"','You gain 1 strike of adrenaline for each party member within earshot (maximum 1...5 adrenaline).','You gain one adrenaline (maximum 1...5) for each party member in earshot.'],
1780=>['"Can\'t Touch This!"','For 20 seconds, the next 1...5 touch skills used against allies <sic/> within earshot fails.','(20 seconds.) The next 1...5 touch-range skills used against allies <sic/> within earshot fails.'],
1781=>['"Find Their Weakness!"','For 5...20 seconds, the next time target ally attacks, that ally deals +5...50 damage and inflicts a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) Target ally deals +5...50 damage and inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) with the next attack.'],
1782=>['"The Power Is Yours!"','For 3 seconds, all allies within earshot gain 0...1 Energy regeneration.','(3 seconds.) Allies within earshot gain 0...1 Energy regeneration.'],
1783=>['Slayer\'s Spear','If this attack hits, you deal +5...25 damage. If that foe has more Health than you, that foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals +5...25 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if target has more Health than you.'],
1784=>['Swift Javelin','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If you are under the effects of an enchantment, this spear flies twice as fast and cannot be blocked.','Deals +5...20 damage. This spear moves twice as fast and is unblockable if you are enchanted.'],
1814=>['Lightbringer\'s Gaze','Target demonic servant of Abaddon takes 100 holy damage and is interrupted. This skill strikes one additional foe in the area for each rank of Lightbringer you have attained. This skill is disabled for 15 seconds after it is used.','Target demonic servant of Abaddon takes 100 holy damage and is interrupted. Hits one additional foe in the area for each rank of Lightbringer you have attained. <gray>This skill is disabled (15 seconds).</gray>'],
1815=>['Lightbringer Signet','If you are within the area of a demonic servant of Abaddon, you gain 4...5 strikes of adrenaline and 22...24 Energy.','You gain 4...5 strikes of adrenaline and 22...24 Energy if you are within the area of a demonic servant of Abaddon.'],
1816=>['Sunspear Rebirth Signet','Resurrect target dead party member at your location with full Health and 10% Energy for each Sunspear rank you have attained. This signet can only be used once per mission unless recharged by a morale boost.','Resurrect target dead ally <sic/> at your location (full Health and 10% Energy for each Sunspear Rank attained). <gray>This signet only recharges when you gain a morale boost.</gray>'],
1948=>['Shadow Sanctuary (Luxon)','You are Blinded for 5 seconds. For 10 seconds, you gain +7...10 Health regeneration and +40 armor.','(10 seconds.) You gain +7...10 Health regeneration and +40 armor. <gray>You are Blind (5 seconds).</gray>'],
1949=>['Ether Nightmare (Luxon)','Target foe loses 5...8 Energy. For each point of Energy lost in this way, that foe and all foes in the area suffer -1 Health degeneration for 10 seconds.','Causes 5...8 Energy loss. Target and foes in the area have -1 Health degeneration for each point of Energy lost (10 seconds).'],
1950=>['Signet of Corruption (Luxon)','Target foe and all nearby foes take 20...30 damage. For each affected foe suffering from a condition or hex, you gain 2 Energy (maximum 12...20 Energy).','Deals 20...30 damage to target and nearby foes. You gain 2 Energy (maximum 12...20) for each of these foes with a condition or hex.'],
1951=>['Elemental Lord (Luxon)','For 40...60 seconds, your elemental attributes are boosted by 1. Each time you cast a spell, you gain 1 Energy for every 10 ranks of Energy Storage and are healed for 100...300% of the spell\'s Energy cost.','(40...60 seconds.) Your elemental attributes are boosted by 1. Each time you cast a spell, you gain 1 energy for every 10 ranks of Energy Storage and are healed for 100...300% of the spell\'s Energy cost.'],
1952=>['Selfless Spirit (Luxon)','For 15...20 seconds, spells you cast that target another ally cost 3 less energy.','(15...20 seconds.) Spells you cast that target another ally cost 3 less Energy.'],
1953=>['Triple Shot (Luxon)','Shoot 3 arrows simultaneously at target foe. These arrows deal 40...25% less damage.','Shoot 3 arrows simultaneously at target foe. <gray>These arrows deal 40...25% less damage</gray>'],
1954=>['"Save Yourselves!" (Luxon)','For 4...6 seconds, all other party members gain +100 armor.','(4...6 seconds.) All other party members gain +100 armor.'],
1955=>['Aura of Holy Might (Luxon)','For 45 seconds, you deal 20...25 holy damage to all adjacent foes whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment.','(45 seconds.) Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, adjacent foes take 20...25 holy damage.'],
1957=>['Spear of Fury (Luxon)','This attack deals +30...40 damage. If this attack hits a foe suffering from a condition, you gain 3...6 strikes of adrenaline.','Deals +30...40 damage. Gain 3...6 strikes of adrenaline if you hit a foe with a condition.'],
1986=>['Vampiric Assault','Must follow an off-hand attack. If this attack hits, you steal 10...40 Health.','Steals 10...40 Health if this attack hits. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
1987=>['Lotus Strike','Must follow a lead attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...25 damage and you gain 5...20 Energy.','Deals +10...25 damage; you gain 5...20 Energy. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
1988=>['Golden Fang Strike','Must follow a lead attack. If you are under the effects of an enchantment and this attack hits, target foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if you are enchanted. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
1990=>['Falling Lotus Strike','Must strike a knocked-down foe. If it hits, you strike for +15...35 damage and gain 1...12 Energy.','Deals +15...35 damage; you gain 1...12 Energy. <gray>No effect unless target foe is knocked-down.</gray>'],
1991=>['Sadist\'s Signet','You gain 10...40 Health for each condition on target foe.','You gain 10...40 Health for each condition on target foe.'],
1992=>['Signet of Distraction','If target foe is casting a spell, that spell is interrupted and disabled for 1...5 seconds for each signet you have equipped.','Interrupts a spell. Interruption effect: target foe\'s spell is disabled for 1...5 seconds for each signet you have equipped.'],
1993=>['Signet of Recall','For 10 seconds, you have -4 Energy regeneration. When this effect ends, you gain 13...20 Energy.','(10 seconds.) You have -4 Energy regeneration. End effect: you gain 13...20 Energy.'],
1994=>['Power Lock','If target foe is casting a spell or chant, that skill is interrupted and disabled for an additional 5...13 seconds.','Interrupts a spell or chant. Interruption effect: interrupted spell or chant is disabled for +5...13 seconds.'],
1995=>['Waste Not, Want Not','If target foe is not casting a spell or attacking, you gain 8...13 Energy.','You gain 8...13 Energy if target foe is not attacking or casting a spell.'],
1996=>['Sum of All Fears','For 1...10 seconds, target foe moves, attacks, and casts spells 33% slower.','(1...10 seconds.) Target foe moves, attacks, and casts spells 33% slower.'],
1997=>['Withering Aura','For 5...20 seconds, target ally\'s melee attacks cause Weakness for 5...20 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) Target ally\'s melee attacks cause Weakness condition (5...20 seconds.)'],
1998=>['Cacophony','For 10 seconds, whenever target foe uses a shout or chant, that foe takes 35...105 damage.','(10 seconds.) Deals 35...105 damage whenever target foe uses a shout or chant.'],
1999=>['Winter\'s Embrace','For 2...6 seconds, target foe moves 66% slower and takes 5...15 damage while moving.','(2...6 seconds.) Target foe moves 66% slower and takes 5...15 damage while moving.'],
2000=>['Earthen Shackles','For 3 seconds, target and all nearby foes move 90% slower. When Earthen Shackles ends, it applies Weakness for 5...20 seconds.','(3 seconds.) Target and nearby foes move 90% slower. Applies Weakness for 5...20 seconds when it ends.'],
2001=>['Ward of Weakness','You create a Ward of Weakness at your current location. For 5...20 seconds, foes in this area become Weakened for 5...20 seconds whenever they take elemental damage.','(5...20 seconds). Inflicts Weakened condition (5...20 seconds) to any foes that take elemental damage in this ward.'],
2002=>['Glyph of Swiftness','For 15 seconds, your next 1...5 spells recharge 25% faster and projectiles from the affected spells move 200% faster.','(15 seconds.) Your next 1...5 spells recharge 25% faster and projectiles from them move 200% faster.'],
2003=>['Cure Hex','Remove one Hex from target ally. If a Hex was removed, that ally is healed for 30...120 Health.','Removes a Hex. Removal effect: Heals for 30...120.'],
2004=>['Smite Condition','Remove one condition from target ally. If a condition was removed, foes in the area take 10...60 holy damage.','Removes a condition. Removal effect: deals 10...60 holy damage to foes in the area of target ally.'],
2005=>['Smiter\'s Boon','For 30 seconds, your Smiting Prayers have double the Divine Favor bonus.','(30 seconds.) Your Smiting Prayers have double Divine Favor healing bonus.'],
2006=>['Castigation Signet','Target foe takes 26...56 holy damage. If that foe was attacking, you gain 1...10 Energy.','Deals 26...56 holy damage. You gain 1...10 Energy if target foe is attacking.'],
2007=>['Purifying Veil','While you maintain this enchantment, conditions expire 5...50% faster on target ally. When this enchantment ends, one condition is removed from that ally.','Conditions expire 5...50% faster on target ally. End effect: removes a condition.'],
2008=>['Pulverizing Smash','If you hit a knocked-down foe, that foe suffers from Weakness and a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Weakness and Deep Wound conditions (5...20 seconds) if target foe is knocked-down.'],
2009=>['Keen Chop','If it hits, this attack always results in a critical hit.','Always a critical hit.'],
2010=>['Knee Cutter','If this attack hits a Crippled foe, you gain 2...7 Energy and 1...3 strikes <sic/> of adrenaline.','You gain 2...7 Energy and 1...3 adrenaline if target foe is Crippled.'],
2011=>['Grapple','You and target touched foe are knocked down. You lose your current stance.','Causes knockdown. You are also knocked down. <gray>Your current stance ends.</gray>'],
2012=>['Radiant Scythe','This attack strikes for +1 damage for each point of Energy you currently have, maximum 5...30. You gain 1...7 Energy if this attack hits.','Deals +1 damage (maximum 5...30) for each point of Energy you have. Gain 1...7 Energy.'],
2013=>['Grenth\'s Aura','For 20 seconds, you deal 5...25 less damage and steal 5...25 Health whenever you hit with a scythe attack. When you cast this enchantment you steal 5...25 Health from all adjacent foes.','(20 seconds.) You deal 5...25 less damage and steal 5...25 Health when you hit with a scythe. Initial effect: steal 5...25 Health from all adjacent foes.'],
2014=>['Signet of Pious Restraint','Remove one Dervish enchantment. Target foe is Crippled for 5...15 seconds. If an enchantment was removed, all foes nearby your target are also Crippled and this signet recharges 75% faster.','Inflicts Crippled condition (5...15 seconds). Remove one of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: also causes Cripple to foes nearby your target and recharges 75% faster.'],
2015=>['Farmer\'s Scythe','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If you hit more than one foe, this attack recharges instantly.','Deals +5...20 damage. Instant recharge if you hit more than one foe.'],
2016=>['Energetic Was Lee Sa','Hold Lee Sa\'s ashes for 5...15 seconds. While you hold her ashes, you gain +2 Energy regeneration. When you drop her ashes, you gain +1...10 Energy.','(5...15 seconds.) You have +2 Energy regeneration. Drop effect: you gain +1...10 Energy.'],
2017=>['Anthem of Weariness','For 8 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot also causes Weakness for 1...16 seconds.','(8 seconds.) Allies in earshot inflict Weakness (1...16 seconds) with their next attack skill.'],
2018=>['Anthem of Disruption','For 1...10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot also interrupts an action.','(1...10 seconds.) Allies in earshot interrupt an action with their next attack skill.'],
