2052=>['Shadow Fang','Shadow Step to target foe. For 10 seconds, this hex does nothing. When this hex ends, you return to your original location and that foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Shadow Step to target foe. End effect after 10 seconds: inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds); you return to your original location.'],
2053=>['Calculated Risk','For 3...24 seconds, target foe\'s attacks do +10 damage, but there is a 50% chance that the damage from each attack will be done to that foe instead. (Maximum 15...100 damage.)','Target foe does +10 damage with attacks (3...24 seconds). There is a 50% chance that the damage from each attack (maximum 15...100) will be done to that foe instead.'],
2054=>['Shrinking Armor','For 10 seconds, target foe suffers from -1...4 Health degeneration. When this hex ends, that foe has Cracked Armor for 5...20 seconds.','(10 seconds.) Causes -1...4 Health degeneration. End effect: inflicts Cracked Armor condition (5...20 seconds).'],
2055=>['Aneurysm','Target foe regains all Energy. For each point of Energy gained in this way, that foe takes 1...3 damage and all adjacent foes lose 1 Energy. (Maximum 1...30).','Target foe regains all Energy. For each point of Energy gained, target takes 1...3 damage and all adjacent foes lose 1 Energy (maximum 1...30).'],
2056=>['Wandering Eye','For 4 seconds, the next time target foe attacks, that attack is interrupted and all nearby foes take 30...110 damage.','(4 seconds.) Interrupts target foe\'s next attack. Interruption effect: 30...110 damage to nearby foes.'],
2057=>['Foul Feast','All conditions are transferred from target other ally to yourself. For each condition acquired in this way, you gain 0...45 Health and 0...2 Energy. This skill recharges twice as fast if you remove Disease from your target.','Transfers all conditions from target ally to yourself. You gain 0...45 Health and 0...2 Energy for each condition transferred. Half recharge if you remove Disease. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2058=>['Putrid Bile','For 5...20 seconds, target foe suffers -1...3 Health degeneration. If that foe dies while under the effects of this hex, all nearby foes take 25...85 damage.','(5...20 seconds.) Causes -1...3 Health degeneration. Deals 25...85 damage to all nearby foes if target foe dies.'],
2059=>['Shell Shock','Target foe is struck for 10...30 lightning damage and has Cracked Armor for 5...20 seconds. This spell has 25% armor penetration. If you are Overcast, this spell strikes adjacent foes.','Deals 10...30 lightning damage. Inflicts Cracked Armor condition (5...20 seconds). 25% armor penetration. If Overcast, strikes adjacent.'],
2060=>['Glyph of Immolation','For 15 seconds, your next 1...4 spells that targets a foe also causes Burning for 1...4 seconds.','(15 seconds.) Your next 1...4 spells that targets a foe also inflicts Burning condition (1...4 seconds).'],
2061=>['Patient Spirit','For 2 seconds, target ally is enchanted with Patient Spirit. Unless this enchantment ends prematurely, that ally is healed for 30...120 Health when the enchantment ends.','(2 seconds.) End effect: heals for 30...120. <gray>No effect if ends early.</gray>'],
2062=>['Healing Ribbon','Target other ally is healed for 20...110 Health. Up to 2 additional allies near target ally are healed for 10...100 Health.','Heals for 20...110. Heals two additional allies near target ally for 10...100. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2063=>['Aura of Stability','For 3...8 seconds, target other ally cannot be knocked down.','(3...8 seconds.) Target ally cannot be knocked-down. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2064=>['Spotless Mind','For 1...15 seconds, target other ally loses a hex every 5 seconds.','(1...15 seconds.) Removes a hex every 5 seconds. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2065=>['Spotless Soul','For 1...15 seconds, target other ally loses a condition every 3 seconds.','(1...15 seconds.) Removes a condition every 3 seconds. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2066=>['Disarm','Interrupt target foe\'s action. If that action was an attack, all of that foe\'s attack skills are disabled for 0...3 seconds.','Interrupts target foe. Interruption effect: disables this foe\'s attack skills (0...3 seconds) if that action was an attack.'],
2067=>['"I Meant to Do That!"','If you are knocked down, you gain 1...5 strikes of adrenaline.','You gain 1...5 strikes of adrenaline if you are knocked-down.'],
