2069=>['Sloth Hunter\'s Shot','If this attack hits, target foe takes +10...25 damage. If that foe is not using a skill, Sloth Hunter\'s Shot does an additional +10...35 damage.','Deals +10...25 damage. Deals +10...35 more damage if target foe is not using a skill.'],
2070=>['Aura Slicer','If this attack hits, you inflict Bleeding for 5...15 seconds. If you are enchanted, you also inflict Cracked Armor for 1...10 seconds.','(5...15 seconds.)Inflicts <sic/> Bleeding condition. Also inflicts Cracked Armor (1...10 seconds) if you are enchanted.'],
2071=>['Zealous Sweep','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. You gain 3 Energy and 1 adrenaline for each foe you hit.','Deals +5...20 damage. You gain 3 Energy and 1 adrenaline for each foe you hit.'],
2072=>['Pure Was Li Ming','Hold Li Ming\'s ashes for 5...20 seconds. While you hold her ashes, conditions on you expire 10...50% faster. When you drop her ashes, all allies within earshot lose 1...4 conditions.','(5...20 seconds.) Conditions on you expire 10...50% faster. Drop effect: removes 1...4 conditions from allies in earshot.'],
