2108=>['Never Rampage Alone','For 18...25 seconds, you and your pet attack 25% faster and have 1...3 Health regeneration.','(18...25 seconds.) You and your pet attack 25% faster and have +1...3 Health regeneration.'],
2109=>['Eternal Aura','You have +100 max Health. When this enchantment ends, all party members in the area are resurrected with 40...50% Health and 20...30% Energy.','You have +100 max Health. End effect: all party members in the area are resurrected with 40...50% Health and 20...30% Energy.'],
2110=>['Vampirism','Create a level 4...14 spirit that dies after 75...150 seconds. Attacks by this spirit steal up to 10...20 Health, and you are healed for 10...20 Health.','Creates a level 4...14 spirit (lifespan 75...150 seconds). Its attacks steal 10...20 Health, and you are healed for 10...20.'],
2112=>['"There\'s Nothing to Fear!"','For 4 seconds and 1 second for every 2 ranks in Leadership, all party members within earshot take 20...35% less damage. Affected party members are healed for 35...60 Health when this shout ends.','(4 seconds plus 1 second for every 2 ranks in Leadership.) Reduces damage by 20...35% for party members in earshot. End effect: heals for 35...60 Health.'],
2116=>['Sneak Attack','If this attack hits, target foe is Blinded for 5...8 seconds. This attack counts as a lead attack.','Inflicts Blindness (5...8 seconds). <gray>Counts as a lead attack.</gray>'],
2135=>['Trampling Ox','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If you a <sic/> hit a Crippled foe, that foe is knocked down.','Deals +5...20 damage; causes knock-down if target foe is Crippled. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
2136=>['Smoke Powder Defense','For 8 seconds, the next time you are struck, you take half damage and all adjacent foes are Blinded for 2...6 seconds.','(8 seconds.) The next time you are struck, you take half damage and inflict Blindness condition (2...6 seconds) on adjacent foes.'],
2137=>['Confusing Images','For 2...10 seconds, target foe takes twice as long to activate non-attack skills.','(2...10 seconds). Target foe takes twice as long to activate non-attack skills.'],
2138=>['Hexer\'s Vigor','For 10 seconds, you have +1...8 Health regeneration. Hexer\'s Vigor ends if you cast a non-hex skill.','(10 seconds.) You have +1...8 Health regeneration. <gray>Ends if you use a non-hex skill.</gray>'],
2139=>['Masochism','For 10...40 seconds, you have +2 to your Death Magic and Soul Reaping attributes and sacrifice 5...3% of your maximum Health when you cast a spell.','(10...40 seconds.) You have +2 Death Magic and Soul Reaping. Sacrifice 5...3% Health when you cast a spell.'],
2140=>['Piercing Trap','When Piercing Trap is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 5...50 piercing damage. Any foes with Cracked Armor are struck for an additional 15...60 damage. Piercing Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 5...50 piercing damage. Deals 15...60 more damage to any foes with Cracked Armor. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
2141=>['Companionship','If you have less Health than your pet, you are healed for 30...120 Health. If your pet has less Health than you, it is healed for 30...120 Health.','Heals you for 30...120 if you have less Health than your pet. Heals your pet for 30...120 if it has less Health than you.'],
2142=>['Feral Aggression','For 5...20 seconds, your pet attacks 33% faster and deals +3...10 additional damage.','(5...20 seconds.) Your pet attacks 33% faster and deals +3...10 damage.'],
2143=>['Disrupting Shot','If this attack hits, target foe\'s action is interrupted. If that action was a Skill, you strike for +10...40 damage.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: +10...40 damage if you interrupt a skill.'],
2144=>['Volley','All your Preparations are removed. Shoot arrows at target foe and up to 3 foes adjacent to your target. These arrows strike for +1...10 damage if they hit.','Deals +1...10 damage. Hits up to 3 foes adjacent to your target. <gray>All your preparations are removed.</gray>'],
2145=>['Expert Focus','For 24 seconds, your bow attack skills cost 1...2 less Energy and deal 1...10 extra damage.','(24 seconds.) Your bow attack skills cost 1...2 less Energy and do +1...10 damage.'],
2146=>['Pious Fury (PvP)','Remove one Dervish enchantment. For 1...5 seconds, you attack 25% faster. If an enchantment was removed, this stance lasts twice as long.','(1...5 seconds.)You <sic/> attack 25% faster and remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: this stance lasts twice as long.'],
2147=>['Crippling Victory','If this attack hits a foe, that foe is Crippled for 3...8 seconds. If you have more Health than target foe, all adjacent foes take 10...30 earth damage.','(3...8 seconds) Cripples target foe. If your health is greater than target foe\'s, all adjacent foes take 10...30 earth damage.'],
2148=>['Sundering Weapon','For 4...10 seconds, target ally\'s next 3 attacks have 10% armor penetration and cause Cracked Armor for 5...20 seconds.','(4...10 seconds.) Target ally\'s next 3 attacks inflict Cracked Armor condition (5...20 seconds) and have 10% armor penetration.'],
2149=>['Weapon of Renewal','For 4...10 seconds, the next time target ally hits with an attack skill, that ally gains 1...7 Energy.','(4...10 seconds.) Target ally gains 1...7 Energy the next time this ally hits with an attack skill.'],
2150=>['Maiming Spear','If your attack hits a Bleeding foe, that foe is Crippled for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Crippled condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe is Bleeding.'],
2186=>['Signet of Deadly Corruption','Target foe takes 5...35 damage for each condition on that foe (maximum 130 damage).','Deals 5...35 damage (maximum 130) for each condition on target foe.'],
2187=>['Way of the Master','For 60 seconds, while holding a non-dagger weapon, you have an additional 3...33% chance to land a critical hit.','(60 seconds.) While holding a non-dagger weapon, you have +3...33% chance to land a critical hit.'],
2188=>['Defile Defenses','For 5...20 seconds, the next time target foe blocks, that foe takes 30...120 damage.','(5...20 seconds.) Deals 30...120 damage the next time target foe blocks.'],
2189=>['Angorodon\'s Gaze','Steal 10...50 Health from target foe. If you are suffering from a condition, you gain 3...12 Energy.','Steals 10...50 Health. You gain 3...12 Energy if you have a condition.'],
2190=>['Magnetic Surge','Target foe takes 15...75 damage. If you are Overcast, Magnetic Surge enchants all allies in earshot for 1...5 seconds to block the next attack against them.','Deals 15...75 damage. If you are Overcast, allies in earshot are enchanted for 1...5 <sic/> and block the next attack against them.'],
2191=>['Slippery Ground','If target or adjacent foes are Blind or moving, these foes are knocked down. There is a 50% chance of failure with Water Magic less than 5.','Causes knock-down if this foe is Blind or moving. Affects foes adjacent to your target. <gray>50% failure chance unless Water Magic greater than 4.</gray>'],
2192=>['Glowing Ice','Target foe is struck for 5...50 cold damage. If that foe is under the effects of a Water Magic hex, you gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage.','Deals 5...50 cold damage. You gain 5 Energy plus 1 Energy for every 2 ranks of Energy Storage if target foe is hexed with Water Magic.'],
2193=>['Energy Blast','Target foe takes 1...2 damage for each point of Energy you have (maximum 130 damage).','Deals 1...2 damage (maximum 130) for each point of Energy you have.'],
2194=>['Distracting Strike','If Distracting Strike hits, it deals no damage and interrupts target foe\'s action. If target foe has Cracked Armor, that skill is disabled for 20 seconds.','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: Disables interrupted skill (20 seconds) if target foe has Cracked Armor. <gray>Deals no damage.</gray>'],
2195=>['Symbolic Strike','If this attack hits, you deal +12 damage for each signet you have equipped (maximum 70 damage).','Deals +12 damage (maximum 70) for each signet you have equipped.'],
2196=>['Soldier\'s Speed','For 3...18 seconds, you move 15% faster. You move an additional 15% faster while under the effects of a chant or shout.','(3...18 seconds.) You move 15% faster and an additional 15% while affected by a chant or shout.'],
2197=>['Body Blow','If this attack hits, target foe takes +10...40 damage. If target foe has Cracked Armor, that foe suffers from a Deep Wound for 0...15 seconds.','Deals +10...40 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound (0...15 seconds) if target foe has Cracked Armor.'],
2198=>['Body Shot','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If it hits a foe with Cracked Armor, you gain 5...10 Energy.','Deals +5...20 damage. You gain 5...10 Energy if target foe has Cracked Armor.'],
2199=>['Poison Tip Signet','For 60 seconds, your next attack also inflicts Poison for 8...15 seconds.','(60 seconds.) Inflicts Poisoned condition (8...15 seconds) with your next attack.'],
2200=>['Signet of Mystic Speed','For 30 seconds, your next 1...3 self-targeting enchantments cast instantly. Flash enchantments do not consume uses of this skill.','(30 seconds.) Your next 1...3 self-targeted enchantments <sic/> cast instantly. <gray>Flash enchantments do not consume uses of this skill.</gray>'],
2201=>['Shield of Force','For 1...16 seconds, blocks the next 1 attack against you. If an attack is blocked, all adjacent attacking foes are knocked down and suffer from Weakness for 5...20 seconds.','(1...16 seconds.) Blocks the next 1 attack against you. Knocks down and inflicts Weakness (5...20 seconds) on all adjacent attacking foes.'],
2202=>['Mending Grip','Target ally is healed for 15...75 Health. If that ally is under the effects of a weapon spell, that ally loses one condition.','Heals for 15...75. Removes one condition if target ally is under a Weapon <sic/> spell.'],
2203=>['Spiritleech Aura','For 5...20 seconds, all of your spirits within earshot deal 5...20 less damage and steal 5...20 Health when they attack.','(5...20 seconds.) All of your spirits within earshot deal 5...20 less damage and steal 5...20 Health when they attack.'],
2204=>['Rejuvenation','Create a level 1...20 spirit. This spirit heals all party members within earshot for 3...10 Health each second. This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each party member healed in this way. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...20 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Heals party members in earshot for 3...10 each second. <gray>Healing cost: this spirit loses 3...10 Health.</gray>'],
2205=>['Agony','Create a level 1...12 spirit. This spirit causes 3...10 Health loss each second to foes within earshot. This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each foe hurt in this way. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...12 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Causes 3...10 Health loss each second to foes in earshot. <gray>This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each foe that loses Health.</gray>'],
2206=>['Ghostly Weapon','For 5...20 seconds, target other ally\'s next attack cannot be blocked.','(5...20 seconds.) Target ally\'s next attack is unblockable. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2207=>['Inspirational Speech','You lose all adrenaline and target other ally gains 1...4 strikes of adrenaline.','Target ally gains 1...4 strikes of adrenaline. <gray>Cannot self-target. You lose all adrenaline.</gray>'],
2208=>['Burning Shield','For 3...9 seconds, while wielding a shield, the next attack skill used against you is blocked. If it was a melee attack, your attacker is set on fire for 1...6 seconds.','(3...9 seconds.) Blocks the next attack skill against you. Inflicts Burning condition (1...6 seconds) if it was a melee attack. <gray>No effect unless you are wielding a shield.</gray>'],
2209=>['Holy Spear','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If it hits a summoned creature, all nearby foes take 15...90 holy damage, and are set on fire for 3 seconds.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals 15...90 holy damage and inflicts Burning condition (3 seconds) to nearby foes if you hit a summoned creature.'],
2210=>['Spear Swipe','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage and target foe is Dazed for 4...10 seconds. This attack has melee range.','Spear Melee Attack. Deals +5...20 damage and inflicts Dazed condition (4...10 seconds). <gray>This attack has melee range.</gray>'],
2211=>['Alkar\'s Alchemical Acid','Throw Alkar\'s Alchemical Acid at target foe. Target and adjacent foes are struck for 40...50 damage. Destroyers take an additional 45...70 damage and they have Cracked Armor for 14...20 seconds.','Projectile: deals 40...50 damage to target and adjacent foes. Deals 45...70 more damage and inflicts Cracked Armor condition (14...20 seconds) to Destroyers.'],
2212=>['Light of Deldrimor','All foes in the area are struck for 55...80 holy damage. The location of hidden objects are briefly indicated on your Compass. Any hidden objects in the area are revealed.','Deals 55...80 holy damage to foes in the area. Pings hidden objects within the area on the compass.'],
2213=>['Ear Bite','Target touched foe takes 50...70 piercing damage and begins Bleeding for 15...25 seconds.','Deals 50...70 piercing damage and inflicts Bleeding condition (15...25 seconds).'],
2214=>['Low Blow','Strike target foe for 45...70 damage. If target foe is knocked down, that foe takes an additional 30...50 damage and suffers from Cracked Armor for 14...20 seconds.','Deals 45...70 damage. Inflicts 30...50 damage and Cracked Armor (14...20 seconds) if target foe is knocked down.'],
2215=>['Brawling Headbutt','You headbutt target touched foe dealing 45...70 damage and knocking down that foe if it hits.','Deals 45...70 damage; causes knock-down.'],
2216=>['"Don\'t Trip!"','For 3...5 seconds, party members within earshot cannot be knocked down.','(3...5 seconds.) Prevents knock-down; affects party members within earshot.'],
2217=>['"By Ural\'s Hammer!"','For 30 seconds, all dead party members in earshot are resurrected with full Health and Energy. Resurrected party members deal 25...33% more damage. When this effect ends, affected party members die. This skill does not incur a death penalty.','(30 seconds.) Resurrect all dead party members in earshot with full Health and Energy. Affected party members deal 25...33% more damage. Affected party members die when it ends, but do not receive a death penalty.'],
2218=>['Drunken Master','For 72...90 seconds, your movement and attack speeds are increased by 10...15%. If you are drunk while activating this skill, your movement and attack speeds are increased by 25...33% instead.','(72...90 seconds.) You move and attack 10...15% faster if you are not drunk. You move and attack 25...33% faster if you are drunk.'],
2219=>['Great Dwarf Weapon','For 20 seconds, target other ally\'s weapon strikes for +15...20 damage and has a 28...40% chance to cause knock down.','(20 seconds.) +15...20 weapon damage and 28...40% chance to cause knock-down with attacks. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2220=>['Great Dwarf Armor','For 22...40 seconds, target ally has +24 armor, +60 maximum Health, and an additional +24 armor against Destroyers.','(22...40 seconds.) +24 armor and +60 maximum Health. Additional +24 armor against Destroyers.'],
2221=>['Breath of the Great Dwarf','All party members are relieved of Burning and are healed for 50...60 Health.','Removes burning and heals for 50...60 Health. Affects party members.'],
2222=>['Snow Storm','Create a Snow Storm at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, foes adjacent to that location are struck for 30...40 cold damage each second.','Deals 30...40 cold damage each second (5 seconds). Hits foes adjacent to target foe\'s initial location.'],
2223=>['Black Powder Mine','When Black Powder Mine is triggered, all nearby foes are struck for 20...30 damage, become Blinded, and begin Bleeding for 7...10 seconds. Black Powder Mine ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 20...30 damage. Inflicts Blindness and Bleeding conditions (7...10 seconds). <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
2224=>['Summon Mursaat','Summon a level 14...20 Mursaat that lives for 40...60 seconds and has Enervating Charge. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active at a time.','Summon a level 14...20 Mursaat (40...60 lifespan) that has Enervating Charge. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.'],
2225=>['Summon Ruby Djinn','Summon a level 14...20 Ruby Djinn that lives for 40...60 seconds and has Immolate. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active at a time.','Summon a level 14...20 Ruby Djinn (40...60 lifespan) that has Immolate. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.'],
2226=>['Summon Ice Imp','Summon a level 14...20 Ice Imp that lives for 40...60 seconds and has Ice Spikes. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.','Summon a level 14...20 Ice Imp (40...60 lifespan) that has Ice Spikes. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.'],
2227=>['Summon Naga Shaman','Summon a level 14...20 Naga Shaman that lives for 40...60 seconds and has Stoning. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.','Summon a level 14...20 Naga Shaman (40...60 lifespan) that has Stoning. Only 1 Asura Summon can be active a time.'],
2228=>['Deft Strike','If this attack hits, target foe takes 18...30 damage. If that foe has Cracked Armor, it begins Bleeding for 18...30 seconds.','Deals 18...30 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition (18...30 seconds) if target foe has Cracked Armor.'],
2229=>['Signet of Infection','If target foe is Bleeding, that foe is Diseased for 13...20 seconds.','Inflicts Diseased condition 13...20 seconds if target foe is Bleeding.'],
2230=>['Tryptophan Signet','For 14...20 seconds, target foe and all adjacent foes move and attack 23...40% slower.','(14...20 seconds.) Target and adjacent foes move and attack 23...40% slower.'],
2231=>['Ebon Battle Standard of Courage','You plant an Ebon Battle Standard of Courage at your current location. For 14...20 seconds, non-spirit allies in this area gain +24 armor and an additional +24 armor against Charr.','(14...20 seconds.) Allies in this ward have +24 armor and +24 more armor against Charr. <gray>Spirits are unaffected.</gray>'],
2232=>['Ebon Battle Standard of Wisdom','You plant an Ebon Battle Standard of Wisdom at your current location. For 14...20 seconds, non-spirit allies in this area have a 44...60% chance to halve skill recharge of spells they cast.','(14...20 seconds.) Spells that allies in this ward cast have a 44...60% chance to recharge 50% faster. <gray>Spirits are unaffected.</gray>'],
2233=>['Ebon Battle Standard of Honor','You plant an Ebon Battle Standard of Honor at your current location. For 14...20 seconds, non-spirit allies in this area strike for +8...15 damage and an additional +7...10 vs. Charr.','(14...20 seconds.) Allies in this ward deal +8...15 damage and +7...10 more damage against Charr. <gray>Spirits are unaffected.</gray>'],
2234=>['Ebon Vanguard Sniper Support','Target foe is struck for 54...90 piercing damage and begins Bleeding for 5...25 seconds. This attack has a 10% chance of doing an additional +540...900 piercing damage. If this attack hits a Charr it has a 25% chance of doing an additional +540...900 piercing damage.','Deals 54...90 piercing damage and inflicts Bleeding condition (5...25 seconds). 10% chance of +540...900 piercing damage. 25% chance of +540...900 piercing damage if target foe is a Charr.'],
2235=>['Ebon Vanguard Assassin Support','Summon a level 14...20 Ebon Vanguard Assassin that has Iron Palm, Fox Fangs, and Nine Tail Strike. This summoned Assassin Shadow Steps to target foe. If that foe is a Charr, the Assassin lives for 24...30 seconds. If target foe is not a Charr, the Assassin lives for 12...15 seconds.','Summon a level 14...20 assassin that has Iron Palm, Fox Fangs, and Nine Tail Strike; it Shadow Steps to this foe. If this foe is a Charr, the assassin lives for 24...30 seconds. If target foe is not a Charr, the Assassin lives for 12...15 seconds.'],
2236=>['Well of Ruin','Exploit nearest corpse to create a Well of Ruin at its location. For 5...30 seconds, whenever a foe in the well takes physical damage, that foe has Cracked Armor for 5...20 seconds.','(5...30 seconds.) Inflicts Cracked Armor condition (5...20 seconds) to any foe in the well that takes physical damage. <gray>Exploits a fresh corpse.</gray>'],
2237=>['Atrophy','For 3...7 seconds, target foe\'s primary attribute is reduced to 0.','(3...7 seconds.) Reduces this foe\'s primary attribute to 0.'],
2238=>['Spear of Redemption','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If it fails to hit, you lose one condition.','Deals +5...20 damage. If it fails to hit, you lose one condition.'],
2353=>['"Finish Him!"','If target foe has less than 50% Health, that foe takes 44...80 damage and suffers from Cracked Armor and a Deep Wound for 12...20 seconds.','Deals 44...80 damage and inflicts Cracked Armor and Deep Wound conditions (12...20 seconds). <gray>No effect unless target foe has less than 50% Health.</gray>'],
2354=>['"Dodge This!"','For 16...20 seconds, your next attack cannot be blocked and does +14...20 damage.','(16...20 seconds.) Your next attack is unblockable and deals +14...20 damage.'],
2355=>['"I Am the Strongest!"','Your next 5...8 attacks do an additional +14...20 damage.','Your next 5...8 attacks deal +14...20 damage.'],
2356=>['"I Am Unstoppable!"','For 16...20 seconds, you have +24 armor and cannot be knocked down or Crippled.','(16...20 seconds.) You have +24 armor and cannot be knocked-down or Crippled.'],
2357=>['A Touch of Guile','Target touched foe takes 44...80 damage. If target foe was knocked down, that foe cannot attack for 5...8 seconds.','Touch Hex Spell. Deals 44...80 damage. Target foe cannot attack (5...8 seconds) if it was knocked-down.'],
2358=>['"You Move Like a Dwarf!"','Target foe is knocked down and takes 44...80 damage. That foe is also Crippled for 8...15 seconds.','Deals 44...80 damage, causes knock-down, and inflicts Crippled condition (8...15 seconds).'],
2359=>['"You Are All Weaklings!"','Target foe and foes adjacent to target are Weakened for 8...12 seconds.','Inflicts Weakness condition (8...12 seconds). Also affects adjacent foes.'],
2360=>['Feel No Pain','For 30 seconds you have +2...3 Health regeneration. If you are drunk when activating this skill, you also have +200...300 maximum Health.','(30 seconds.) You have +2...3 Health regeneration. You have +200...300 maximum Health if you are drunk when activating this skill.'],
2361=>['Club of a Thousand Bears','If this attack hits, it deals +6...9 damage for each adjacent foe (maximum 60 damage). If target foe is non-human it is knocked down.','Deals +6...9 damage for each adjacent foe (maximum 60 damage). Causes knock-down if target foe is non-human.'],
2374=>['Ursan Blessing','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the bear. For 60 seconds, you have 100 armor and 750...800 Health. All your attributes are set to 0 and bear attacks replace your skills.','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the bear (60 seconds). All your attributes are set to 0 and bear attacks replace your skills, and you have 100 armor and 750...800 Health.'],
2379=>['Volfen Blessing','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the wolf. For 60 seconds, you have 80 armor, 660...700 Health, and 2...4 Health regeneration. All your attributes are set to 0 and wolf attacks replace your skills.','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the wolf (60 seconds). All your attributes are set to 0 and wolf attacks replace your skills, and you have 80 armor, 660...700 Health and 2...4 Health regeneration.'],
2384=>['Raven Blessing','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the raven. For 60 seconds, you have 80 armor, 660...700 Health, and a 20...30% chance to block, All your attributes are set to 0 and raven attacks replace your skills.','You lose all effects and take on the aspect of the Raven (60 seconds). All your attributes are set to 0 and raven attacks replace your skills, and you have 80 armor, 660...700 Health, and a 20...30% block chance.'],
2411=>['Mindbender','For 10...16 seconds, you move 20...33% faster and your Spells take 20% less time to cast.','(10...16 seconds.) You move 20...33% faster and cast Spells 20% faster.'],
2412=>['Smooth Criminal','For 10...20 seconds, one random spell is disabled for target foe and Smooth Criminal is replaced by that spell. You gain 5...10 Energy.','(10...20 seconds.) Disables one Spell. This skill becomes that Spell. You gain 5...10 Energy.'],
2413=>['Technobabble','Target foe and all adjacent foes are struck for 30...40 damage. If target foe is not a boss, that foe and all adjacent foes are Dazed for 3...5 seconds.','Deals 30...40 damage to target and adjacent foes. Inflicts Dazed condition (3...5 seconds) on these foes if target was not a boss.'],
2414=>['Radiation Field','For 5 seconds, foes in the area have &#45;-4...6 Health degeneration. When the portal ends, foes in the area are Diseased for 12...20 seconds.','(5 seconds.) Causes &#45;-4...6 Health degeneration to foes in the area. End effect: inflicts Disease condition (12...20 seconds) to foes in the area.'],
2415=>['Asuran Scan','For 9...12 seconds your attacks cannot miss target foe. Killing a foe hexed with Asuran Scan removes 5% Death Penalty.','(9...12 seconds.) You cannot miss target foe. If you kill this foe, you lose 5% Death Penalty.'],
2416=>['Air of Superiority','For 20...30 seconds you gain a random Asura benefit every time you earn experience from killing an enemy.','(20...30 seconds). Gain a random Asura benefit every time you earn experience from killing an enemy.'],
2417=>['Mental Block','For 5...11 seconds you have a 50% chance to block attacks. This Enchantment is reapplied every time an enemy strikes you.','(5...11 seconds.) You have a 50% chance to block. Renewal: every time an enemy hits you.'],
2418=>['Pain Inverter','For 6...10 seconds, every time target foe deals damage that foe takes 100...140% of the damage it causes (maximum 80 damage).','(6...10 seconds.) Deals 100...140% of the damage (maximum 80) back to target foe every time it does damage.'],
2420=>['Ebon Escape','Shadow Step to target other ally. You and that other ally are healed for 70...110 health.','Heals you and target ally for 70...110. Initial effect: Shadow Step to this ally. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2421=>['Weakness Trap','When Weakness Trap is triggered, all nearby foes are Weakened for 10...20 seconds and take 24...50 lightning damage. All Charr are knocked down. Weakness Trap ends after 90 seconds. While activating this skill, you are easily interrupted.','(90 seconds.) Affects nearby foes. Deals 24...50 lightning damage. Inflicts Weakness condition (10...20 seconds). Knocks-down Charr. <gray>Easily interrupted.</gray>'],
2422=>['Winds','Create a level 4...10 Spirit. All foes within its range have 15% chance to miss with ranged attacks. This spirit dies after 54...90 seconds.','Creates a level 4...10 spirit (54...90 second lifespan.) Affects foes within range. 15% chance to miss with ranged attacks.'],
2423=>['Dwarven Stability','For 24...30 seconds, your stances last 55...100% longer. If you activated this skill while drunk, you cannot be knocked down.','(24...30 seconds.) Your stances last 55...100% longer. You cannot be knocked-down if you activated this skill while drunk . <sic/>'],
2657=>['Call of Haste (PvP)','For 30 seconds, your animal companion has a 25% faster attack speed and moves 25% faster.','(30 seconds.) Your pet moves and attacks 25% faster.'],
2734=>['Mind Wrack (PvP)','For 5...40 seconds, whenever this foe is the target of one of your non-hex Mesmer skills, that foe loses 1 Energy. If the target foe\'s Energy drops to 0, Mind Wrack ends and that foe takes 15...100 damage.','(5...40 seconds.) Causes 1 Energy loss each time foe is the target of your non-hex Mesmer skills. If target foe\'s Energy drops to 0, Mind Wrack ends and that foe takes 15...100 damage.'],
2803=>['Mind Freeze (PvP)','Target foe takes 10...40 cold damage. If you have more Energy than target foe, that foe suffers an additional 10...40 cold damage and moves 90% slower for 1...5 seconds.','Deals 10...40 cold damage. If you have more Energy than target foe, deals +10...40 cold damage and causes 90% slower movement (1...5 seconds).'],
2804=>['Mind Shock (PvP)','Target foe suffers 10...50 lightning damage. If you have more Energy than target foe, that foe suffers 10...50 more lightning damage and is knocked down. This spell has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...50 lightning damage. If you have more Energy than target foe, deals +10...50 lightning damage and causes knockdown. 25% armor penetration.'],
2805=>['Mist Form (PvP)','For 10...45 seconds, you take 33% less damage from foes under the effects of Water Magic hexes. Whenever you cast an elemental spell, all non-spirit allies in earshot are healed for 50...250% of the Energy cost of the spell. This spell does not heal allies above 80% Health.','(10...45 seconds.) Take 33% less damage from foes hexed with Water Magic. Heals non-spirit allies in earshot for 50...250% of the energy cost of your elemental spells. <gray>Does not heal allies above 80% Health.</gray>'],
2806=>['Ward Against Harm (PvP)','Create a Ward Against Harm at this location. For 5...15 seconds, non-spirit allies in this area have +1...3 health regeneration, +12...24 armor, and an additional +12...24 armor against elemental damage. This spell is disabled for 30 seconds.','(5...15 seconds.) Allies in this ward have +1...3 Health regeneration, +12...24 armor, and +12...24 additional armor against elemental damage. <gray>Spirits are unaffected. This spell is disabled for 30 seconds.</gray>'],
2807=>['Ride the Lightning (PvP)','You Ride the Lightning to target. All adjacent foes are Blinded for 1...5 seconds. If your target is a foe, it is struck for 10...70 lightning damage. This spell has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...70 lightning damage. 25% armor penetration. Blinds all adjacent foes (1...5 seconds). You instantly move to your target. May target allies.'],
2808=>['Enraged Smash (PvP)','If Enraged Smash hits, you gain 1...4 strikes of adrenaline. If you hit a moving foe, you strike for +10...40 damage, and target foe is knocked down.','Gives you 1...4 strikes of adrenaline if you hit. Deals +10...40 damage and causes knockdown if target foe was moving.'],
2809=>['Obsidian Flame (PvP)','Deal 22...92 damage to target foe. This spell ignores armor.','Deals 22...92 damage.'],
2857=>['Aegis (PvP)','For 1...3 seconds, target other party member cannot be the target of hostile spells, and attacks against this party member fail.','(1...3 seconds). Target party member cannot be targeted by hostile spells. Attacks against this party member fail. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
2858=>['"Watch Yourself!" (PvP)','Party members within earshot gain +5...25 armor for 10 seconds. This shout ends after 1...3 incoming attacks.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot have +5...25 armor. <gray>Ends after 1...3 incoming attacks.</gray>'],
2859=>['Enfeeble (PvP)','Target suffers from Weakness for 10...30 seconds.','Inflicts Weakness condition (10...30 seconds).'],
2860=>['Ether Renewal (PvP)','For 7 seconds, each time you cast a spell, you gain 1...3 Energy and 5...20 Health for each enchantment on you.','(7 seconds.) Each time you cast a spell, you gain 1...3 Energy and 5...20 Health for each enchantment on you.'],
2861=>['Penetrating Attack (PvP)','If Penetrating Attack hits, you strike for +3...10 damage and this attack has 10% armor penetration.','Deals +3...10 damage. 10% armor penetration.'],
2862=>['Shadow Form (PvP)','For 5...15 seconds, all hostile spells that target you fail and all attacks against you miss. When Shadow Form ends, lose all but 5...50 Health.','(5...15 seconds.) Hostile spells targeting you fail, and attacks against you miss. <gray>End effect: lose all but 5...50 Health.</gray>'],
2863=>['Discord (PvP)','If target foe is suffering from a condition and under the effects of a hex or an enchantment, that foe suffers 30...110 damage.','Deals 30...110 damage. <gray>No effect unless target foe has a condition and is either hexed or enchanted.</gray>'],
2864=>['Sundering Attack (PvP)','If Sundering Attack hits, you strike for +3...10 damage and this attack has 10% armor penetration.','Deals +3...10 damage. 10% armor penetration.'],
2866=>['Flesh of My Flesh (PvP)','Lose half your Health. Resurrect target party member with your current Health and 5...20% Energy.','Resurrect target party member (half your current Health and 5...20% Energy). Lose half your Health.'],
2867=>['Ancestors\' Rage (PvP)','For 3 seconds all foes adjacent to target ally are struck for 1...41 lightning damage each second.','(3 seconds.) Deals 1...41 lightning damage to foes adjacent to target ally each second.'],
2868=>['Splinter Weapon (PvP)','For 20 seconds, target ally has a Splinter Weapon. Target ally\'s next 1...5 attacks deal 5...30 damage to up to 4 adjacent foes.','(20 seconds.) Attacks deal 5...30 damage to 3 <sic/> adjacent foes. <gray>Ends after 1...5 attacks.</gray>'],
2869=>['Assassin\'s Remedy (PvP)','For 30 seconds, the next 1...10 attack skills you use remove one condition.','(30 seconds.) Your next 1...10 attack skills each remove one condition.'],
2871=>['Light of Deliverance (PvP)','All party members are healed for 5...70 Health. All your Smiting Prayers are disabled for 20 seconds.','Heals entire party for 5...70. <gray>Disables your Smiting Prayers (20 seconds).</gray>'],
2872=>['Death Pact Signet (PvP)','Resurrect target party member with your current Health and 15...100% Energy. The next time that ally dies within 120 seconds, so do you.','Resurrects target party member with your current Health and 15...100% maximum Energy. For 120 seconds, you die the next time this party member dies.'],
2875=>['Harrier\'s Toss (PvP)','If this attack hits, you deal +5...20 damage. If this attack hits a moving foe, it deals an additional 5...30 damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals 5...30 more damage if target is moving.'],
2876=>['Defensive Anthem (PvP)','For 4...10 seconds, each party member within earshot has a 50% chance to block incoming attacks. This chant ends if that party member hits with an attack skill.','(4...10 seconds.) Party members in earshot have 50% chance to block. <gray>Ends when hitting with an attack skill.</gray>'],
2877=>['Ballad of Restoration (PvP)','For 10 seconds, the next time each party member within earshot takes damage, that party member gains 15...75 Health.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 15...75 Health the next time they take damage.'],
2878=>['Song of Restoration (PvP)','For 10 seconds, the next time each party member within earshot uses a skill, that party member gains 45...110 Health.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain 45...110 Health with their next skill.'],
2879=>['"Incoming!" (PvP)','For 4...10 seconds, all allies within earshot move 33% faster, and gain 5...15 Health while moving.','(4...10 seconds) Allies in earshot move 33% faster and gain 5...15 Health while moving.'],
2880=>['"Never Surrender!" (PvP)','For 10 seconds, all party members within earshot and below 75% Health gain +1...5 Health regeneration.','(10 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain +1...5 Health regeneration. <gray>Only affects party members below 75% Health.</gray>'],
2883=>['"For Great Justice!" (PvP)','For 8 seconds, when you hit with an attack, you gain 1 additional strike of adrenaline.','(8 seconds.) You gain 1 extra strike of adrenaline whenever you hit with an attack.'],
2884=>['Mystic Regeneration (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, you have +1...4 Health regeneration for each enchantment (maximum of 3) on you.','(5...20 seconds.) You have +1...4 Health regeneration for each enchantment (maximum of 3) on you.'],
2885=>['Enfeebling Blood (PvP)','Target foe and all nearby foes suffer from Weakness for 1...16 seconds.','Inflicts Weakness condition (1...16 seconds) on this foe and nearby foes.'],
2887=>['Signet of Judgment (PvP)','Target foe is knocked down. That foe and all adjacent foes take 5...50 holy damage. This signet has half the normal range.','Elite Half Range Signet. Knocks down target. Deals 5...50 holy damage to target and adjacent foes.'],
2891=>['Unyielding Aura (PvP)','Bring target dead party member back to life at full Health and full Energy. If you stop maintaining this enchantment or if this enchantment is removed, that party member dies and leaves an exploited corpse. Deaths while enchanted with Unyielding Aura do not incur a death penalty. (50% failure chance with Divine Favor 4 or less.)','Resurrects target party member (full Health, full Energy). End effect: this ally dies and leaves an exploited corpse. Does not incur a death penalty. <gray>50% failure chance unless Divine Favor 5 or more.</gray>'],
2892=>['Spirit Bond (PvP)','For 8 seconds, whenever target ally takes more than 50 damage from the next 10 attacks or spells, that ally is healed for 30...90 Health.','(8 seconds.) Heals for 30...90 whenever target ally takes more than 50 damage. <gray>Ends after this ally takes damage from 10 attacks or spells.</gray>'],
2893=>['Weapon of Warding (PvP)','For 3...8 seconds, target ally has a Weapon of Warding that grants target ally +2...4 Health regeneration and a 50% chance to block. Weapon of Warding ends if that ally attacks.','(3...8 seconds.) +2...4 Health regeneration. 50% chance to block. <gray>Ends if target ally attacks.</gray>'],
2895=>['Smiter\'s Boon (PvP)','For 5 seconds, your Smiting Prayers have double the Divine Favor bonus.','(5 seconds.) Your Smiting Prayers have double Divine Favor healing bonus.'],
2925=>['Sloth Hunter\'s Shot (PvP)','If this attack hits, target foe takes +5...20 damage. If that foe is not using a skill, Sloth Hunter\'s Shot does an additional +5...15 damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals +5...15 more damage if target foe is not using a skill.'],
2959=>['Expert\'s Dexterity (PvP)','For 1...20 seconds, you attack 15% faster and your Marksmanship attribute is increased by 1.','(1...20 seconds.) You attack 15% faster and you gain +1 to your Marksmanship attribute.'],
2965=>['Signet of Spirits (PvP)','You gain 3...12 Energy if you are within earshot of a spirit.','You gain 3...12 Energy. <gray>No effect unless you are within earshot of a spirit.</gray>'],
2966=>['Signet of Ghostly Might (PvP)','Target allied summoned creature\'s attacks deal 5...35 more damage. After 10 seconds, that creature is destroyed.','Target allied summoned creature deals +5...35 damage. <gray>That creature is destroyed after 10 seconds.</gray>'],
2969=>['Read the Wind (PvP)','For 24 seconds, your arrows move twice as fast.','(24 seconds). Your arrows move twice as fast.'],
2998=>['Fragility (PvP)','For 8...20 seconds, target foe takes 5...20 damage each time that foe suffers or recovers from a new condition.','(8...20 seconds.) Target foe takes 5...20 damage each time it gains or loses a condition.'],
2999=>['Strength of Honor (PvP)','While you maintain this enchantment, target ally deals 1...5 more damage in melee.','Target ally deals 1...5 more damage in melee.'],
3002=>['Warrior\'s Endurance (PvP)','For 5...35 seconds, you gain 3 Energy each time you hit with a melee attack. Warrior\'s Endurance cannot raise your Energy above 10...25.','(5...35 seconds.) You gain 3 Energy each time you hit with a melee attack. <gray>No Energy gain if you have more than 10...25 Energy.</gray>'],
3003=>['Armor of Unfeeling (PvP)','For 10...35 seconds, you have 10 base damage reduction while casting Binding Rituals.','(10...35 seconds.) You have 10 base damage reduction while casting binding rituals.'],
3005=>['Union (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. Whenever a non-spirit ally in its range takes damage or life steal, it is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Whenever a non-spirit ally within range takes damage or life steal, that damage is reduced by 15 and the spirit takes 15 damage.'],
3006=>['Shadowsong (PvP)','Create a level 1...6 spirit. The spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage and cause Blindness for 1...6 seconds. This spirit dies after 30 seconds. <sic/>','Creates a level 1...6 spirit (30-second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and inflict Blindness condition (1...6 seconds).'],
3007=>['Pain (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...30 damage. This spirit dies after 30...150 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...30 damage.'],
3008=>['Destruction (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 Spirit <sic/> that dies after 30 seconds. When this Spirit dies, all foes in the area take 1...10 damage for each second the Spirit was alive (maximum of 150 damage).','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30 second lifespan). On death, it deals 1...10 damage for each second it was alive to all foes in the area (maximum 150 damage).'],
3009=>['Soothing (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. All foes within its range take twice as long to build adrenaline. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Building adrenaline takes twice as long for foes within range.'],
3010=>['Displacement (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. All non-spirit allies within its range have a 75% chance to block incoming attacks. Every time an attack is blocked in this way, this spirit takes 60 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range have 75% chance to block. <gray>Block effect: this spirit takes 60 damage.</gray>'],
3011=>['Preservation (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Every 4 seconds, this spirit heals one non-spirit ally in the area for 10...115 Health. This spirit dies after 90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 Spirit (90 second lifespan). Every 4 seconds this spirit heals one non-spirit ally for 10...115.'],
3012=>['Life (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. When this spirit dies, all non-spirit allies within its range are healed for 1...7 Health for each second this spirit was alive. This spirit dies after 20 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (20 second lifespan). Affects non-spirit allies within range. End effect: heals for 1...7 for each second this spirit was alive.'],
3013=>['Recuperation (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Non-spirit allies within its range gain +1...3 Health regeneration. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range have +1...3 Health regeneration.'],
3014=>['Dissonance (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. This spirit deals 5...20 damage and anyone struck by its attack is interrupted. This spirit dies after 10...25 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (10...25 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and interrupt actions.'],
3015=>['Earthbind (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. All non-spirit foes knocked down within its range are knocked down for at least 3 seconds. Whenever this happens, this spirit loses 50...25 Health. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Any time non-spirit foes within range are knocked down, they are knocked down for at least 3 seconds. <gray>Knock-down cost: this spirit loses 50...25 Health.</gray>'],
3016=>['Shelter (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. Non-spirit allies within its range cannot lose more than 10% maximum Health from a single attack. When this spirit prevents damage, it loses 75...45 Health. This spirit lasts 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Non-spirit allies within range cannot lose more than 10% maximum Health from a single attack. <gray>Damage prevention cost: this spirit loses 75...45 Health.</gray>'],
3017=>['Disenchantment (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. This spirit deals 5...20 damage and anyone struck by its attack loses one enchantment. This spirit dies after 10...35 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (10...35 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage and remove one enchantment.'],
3018=>['Restoration (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. When this spirit dies, all party members in the area are resurrected with 5...50% Health and zero Energy. This spirit dies after 30 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30 second lifespan). End effect: resurrects party members in the area with 5...50% Health and zero Energy.'],
3019=>['Bloodsong (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit who dies after 30...150 seconds. Attacks by that spirit steal up to 5...25 Health.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...150 second lifespan). Its attacks steal 5...25 Health.'],
3020=>['Wanderlust (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. Whenever this spirit\'s attack hits a stationary foe, that foe is knocked down and the spirit loses 70...50 Health. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Its attacks against stationary foes cause knock-down. <gray>Knock-down cost: this spirit loses 70...50 Health.</gray>'],
3021=>['Savannah Heat (PvP)','You create Savannah Heat at target foe\'s location. For 5 seconds, all nearby foes take 5...20 fire damage for each second this spell has been in effect.','Deals 5...20 fire damage for each second since casting this spell (5 seconds). Hits foes near target\'s initial location.'],
3022=>['Gaze of Fury (PvP)','Destroy target allied spirit and create a level 1...10 Spirit of Fury. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Destroys an allied spirit. Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage.'],
3023=>['Anguish (PvP)','Create a level 1...7 spirit. This spirit\'s attacks deal 5...20 damage and deal double damage to hexed foes. This spirit dies after 15...45 seconds.','Creates a level 1...7 spirit (15...45 second lifespan). Its attacks deal 5...20 damage. Double damage to hexed foes.'],
3024=>['Empowerment (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. All allies within its range holding an item gain 15...45 maximum Health and 10 maximum Energy. This spirit dies after 15...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (15...60 second lifespan). Allies in range holding an item gain 15...45 maximum Health and 10 maximum Energy.'],
3025=>['Recovery (PvP)','Create a level 1...10 spirit. Conditions on allies within range of this spirit expire 20...50% faster. This spirit dies after 30...60 seconds.','Creates a level 1...10 spirit (30...60 second lifespan). Conditions on allies in range expire 20...50% faster.'],
3026=>['"Go for the Eyes!" (PvP)','For 10 seconds, the next time each ally within earshot makes an attack, that attack has an additional 30...75% chance to critical.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot have +30...75% to land a critical hit with their next attack.'],
3027=>['"Brace Yourself!" (PvP)','For 5...15 seconds, the next time target other ally would be knocked down, 1 nearby foe takes 15...75 damage instead.','(5...15 seconds.) Prevents the next knock-down and deals 15...75 damage to one foe near target ally. <gray>Cannot self-target.</gray>'],
3028=>['Blazing Finale (PvP)','For 10...35 seconds, whenever a chant or shout ends on target non-spirit ally, all foes adjacent to that ally are set on Fire for 1...3 seconds.','(10...35 seconds.) Inflicts Burning condition (1...3 seconds) to adjacent foes whenever a chant or shout ends on target ally. Cannot target spirits.'],
3029=>['Bladeturn Refrain (PvP)','For 20 seconds, target non-spirit ally has +10...40 armor against slashing damage. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(20 seconds.) Target ally has +10...40 armor against slashing damage. Renewal: Whenever a chant or shout ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
3030=>['Signet of Return (PvP)','Resurrect target party member with 5...15% Health and 1...4% Energy for each party member within earshot.','Resurrects target party member (5...15% Health and 1...4% Energy for each party member in earshot).'],
3031=>['"Can\'t Touch This!" (PvP)','For 20 seconds, the next 1...5 touch skills used against you fails.','(20 seconds.) The next 1...5 touch-range skills used against you fails.'],
3032=>['"Stand Your Ground!" (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, all party members within earshot receive +24 armor when not moving. This effect ends on an ally affected by this shout when that ally attacks.','(5...20 seconds.) Party members in earshot gain +24 armor when not moving. Ends for an ally if that ally attacks.'],
3033=>['"We Shall Return!" (PvP)','For 10 seconds, whenever party members within earshot use a resurrection skill, their fallen allies return with 10...75% more Health and 5...50% more Energy.','(10 seconds.) Whenever party members in earshot use a resurrection skill, their fallen allies return with 10...75% more Health and 5...50% more Energy.'],
3034=>['"Find Their Weakness!" (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, the next time target ally criticals, that ally also inflicts a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) Target ally inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) with the next critical hit.'],
3035=>['"Never Give Up!" (PvP)','All allies within earshot and below 75% Health gain 1...10 Energy.','Allies in earshot gain 1...10 Energy. <gray>Only affects allies below 75% Health.</gray>'],
3036=>['"Help Me!" (PvP)','You gain 5...50 Health. For 1...10 seconds, other allies\' spells targeting you cast 50% faster.','(1...10 seconds.) Other allies\' spells targeting you cast 50% faster. You gain 5...50 Health.'],
3037=>['"Fall Back!" (PvP)','For 4...10 seconds, all allies within earshot gain 5...15 Health per second while moving and move 33% faster. "Fall Back!" ends on an ally affected by this shout when that ally successfully hits with an attack.','(4...10 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain 5...15 Health per second while moving and move 33% faster. <gray>Ends for an ally if that ally hits with an attack.</gray>'],
3038=>['Agony (PvP)','Create a level 1...8 spirit. This spirit causes 3...10 Health loss each second to foes within earshot. This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each foe hurt in this way. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...8 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Causes 3...10 Health loss each second to foes in earshot. <gray>This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each foe that loses Health.</gray>'],
3039=>['Rejuvenation (PvP)','Create a level 1...16 spirit. This spirit heals all party members within earshot for 3...10 Health each second. This spirit loses 3...10 Health for each party member healed in this way. This spirit dies after 30...90 seconds.','Creates a level 1...16 spirit (30...90 second lifespan). Heals party members in earshot for 3...10 each second. <gray>Healing cost: this spirit loses 3...10 Health.</gray>'],
3040=>['Anthem of Disruption (PvP)','For 1...10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot also interrupts an action.','(1...10 seconds.) Allies in earshot interrupt an action with their next attack skill.'],
3045=>['Comfort Animal (PvP)','You heal your animal companion for 20...104 Health. If your companion is dead, it is resurrected with 10...58% Health.','Your pet gains 20...104 Health. Resurrects your pet (10...58% Health.)'],
3047=>['Melandru\'s Assault (PvP)','Your animal companion attempts a Melandru\'s Assault that deals +5...20 damage. If that attack strikes a foe with an enchantment, that foe and all adjacent foes take +5...35 additional damage.','Deals +5...20 damage. Deals +5...35 more damage to target and foes adjacent to target if this foe is enchanted.'],
3048=>['Shroud of Distress (PvP)','For 30...60 seconds, if you are below 50% Health, you have a 75% chance to block attacks.','(30...60 seconds.) You have 75% chance to block. No effect unless your Health is below 50%.'],
3049=>['Unseen Fury (PvP)','For 15...60 seconds, you cannot be blocked by Blinded foes.','(15...60 seconds.) You cannot be blocked by Blinded foes.'],
3050=>['Predatory Bond (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, attacks by your animal companion heal you for 1...31 Health.','(5...20 seconds.) You gain 1...31 Health whenever your pet makes a successful attack.'],
3051=>['Enraged Lunge (PvP)','Your animal companion attempts an Enraged Lunge that deals +3...23 damage (maximum bonus 80) for each recharging Beast Mastery skill.','Deals +3...23 damage (maximum 80) for each of your recharging Beast Mastery skills.'],
3053=>['Signet of Deadly Corruption (PvP)','Must follow a dual attack. Target foe takes 5...35 damage for each condition on that foe (maximum 130 damage).','Deals 5...35 damage (maximum 130) for each condition on target foe. <gray>Must follow a dual attack.</gray>'],
3054=>['Masochism (PvP)','For 30 seconds, you gain 1...3 Energy whenever you sacrifice Health.','(30 seconds.) You gain 1...3 Energy whenever you sacrifice Health.'],
3058=>['Unholy Feast (PvP)','Steal up to 10...65 Health from up to 1...4 foes <sic/> in the area.','Steals 10...65 Health from 1...4 foes in the area around you.'],
3059=>['Signet of Agony (PvP)','You suffer from Bleeding for 25 seconds. All nearby foes take 10...70 damage.','Deals 10...70 damage to foes near you. <gray>You begin Bleeding (25 seconds).</gray>'],
3060=>['Escape (PvP)','For 1...8 seconds, you move 33% faster and have a 75% chance to block attacks. Escape ends if you make a melee attack.','(1...8 seconds.) You move 33% faster and have 75% chance to block. <gray>Ends if you make a melee attack.</gray>'],
3061=>['Death Blossom (PvP)','Must follow an off-hand attack. If it hits, Death Blossom strikes target foe for +20...45 damage and all adjacent foes take 20...45 damage.','Deals +20...45 damage. Also affects foes adjacent to target foe. <gray>Must follow an off-hand attack.</gray>'],
3062=>['Finale of Restoration (PvP)','For 10...35 seconds, the next 5 times that a chant or shout ends on target non-spirit ally, that ally is healed for 15...75 Health.','(10...35 seconds.) Target ally gains <sic/> 15...75 Health the next 5 times a shout or chant ends on that ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits.</gray>'],
3063=>['Mantra of Resolve (PvP)','For 5 seconds, you cannot be interrupted, but each time you would have been interrupted, you lose 10...4 Energy or Mantra of Resolve ends.','(5 seconds.) Prevents interrupts against you. <gray>Prevention cost: lose 10...4 Energy or Mantra of Resolve ends.</gray>'],
3141=>['Lightning Reflexes (PvP)','For 5...11 seconds, you have a 75% chance to block melee and projectile attacks, and you attack 33% faster.','(5...11 seconds.) You attack 33% faster and have 75% chance to block.'],
3143=>['Renewing Smash (PvP)','If Renewing Smash hits, it deals +5...20 damage. If it hits a knocked-down foe, you gain 3 Energy and this attack recharges instantly.','Deals +5...20 damage. You gain 3 energy and this attack recharges instantly if target foe was knocked down.'],
3144=>['Heal as One (PvP)','If you or your animal companion are below 75% Health, you are both healed for 25...145 Health. If your companion is dead, it is resurrected with 50% Health.','Heals you and your pet for 25...145. If your pet is dead, it is resurrected with 50% Health. <gray>No effect if neither you nor your pet are below 75% Health.</gray>'],
3145=>['Glass Arrows (PvP)','For 10...35 seconds, your arrows strike for +5...12 damage if they hit and cause Bleeding for 10...20 seconds if they are blocked.','(10...35 seconds.) Your arrows deal +5...12 damage. Inflicts Bleeding condition if blocked (10...20 seconds).'],
3147=>['Keen Arrow (PvP)','If this attack hits, you strike for +1...5 damage. If you land a critical hit, you deal an additional +5...30 damage.','Deals +1...5 damage. Deals +5...30 more damage if you land a critical hit.'],
3148=>['Anthem of Envy (PvP)','For 10 seconds, the next attack skill used by each ally within earshot deals +10...20 damage against foes with more than 50% Health.','(10 seconds.) Allies in earshot do +10...20 damage with their next attack skill. <gray>Damage bonus only applies to foes with more than 50% Health.</gray>'],
3149=>['Mending Refrain (PvP)','For 15 seconds, you have +2...3 Health regeneration. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on you.','(15 seconds.) You have +2...3 Health regeneration. Renewal: whenever a chant or shout ends on you.'],
3151=>['Empathy (PvP)','For 5...15 seconds, whenever target foe attacks, that foe takes 15...45 damage.','(5...15 seconds.) Target foe takes 15...45 damage whenever it attacks.'],
3152=>['Crippling Anguish (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, target moves 50% slower and suffers -1...5 Health degeneration.','(5...20 seconds.) Target foe moves 50% slower and has -1...5 Health degeneration.'],
3156=>['Soldier\'s Stance (PvP)','For 4...10 seconds, you attack 33% faster while under the effects of a shout or chant.','(4...10 seconds.) You attack 33% faster while under the effects of a shout or chant.'],
3157=>['Destructive Was Glaive (PvP)','Hold Glaive\'s ashes for up to 30...60 seconds. While you hold her ashes, all Ritualist skills have 10% armor penetration. When you drop her ashes, all foes in the area are struck for 15...85 lightning damage.','(30...60 seconds.) Your Ritualist skills have 10% armor penetration. Drop effect: deals 15...85 lightning damage to all foes in the area.'],
3179=>['Mantra of Signets (PvP)','For 10...40 seconds, whenever you use a signet, you gain 5...60 Health.','(10...40 seconds.) You gain 5...60 Health each time you use a signet.'],
3180=>['Shatter Delusions (PvP)','Remove one Mesmer hex from target foe. If a hex was removed, that foe and all adjacent foes takes 15...75 damage.','Removes a Mesmer hex from target foe. Removal effect: 15...75 damage to target and all adjacent foes.'],
3181=>['Illusionary Weaponry (PvP)','For 30 seconds, your melee attacks neither hit nor fail to hit. Instead, Illusionary Weaponry deals 8...40 damage to your targets for each melee attack.','(30 seconds.) Deals 8...40 damage to foes in place of other damage or effects from melee attacks. <gray>Your melee attacks neither hit nor fail to hit.</gray>'],
3183=>['Migraine (PvP)','For 3...12 seconds, target foe suffers -1...8 Health degeneration and takes 100% longer to activate skills.','(3...12 seconds.) Causes -1...8 Health degeneration and doubles skill activation time.'],
3184=>['Accumulated Pain (PvP)','Target foe takes 10...35 damage. If target foe is suffering from 2 or more hexes, that foe suffers a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Deals 10...35 damage. Inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds) if target foe has 2 or more hexes.'],
3185=>['Psychic Instability (PvP)','Interrupts the target foe\'s action. If that action is a skill, that foe and all adjacent foes are knocked down for 2...3 seconds. (50% failure chance with Fast Casting 4 or less.)','Interrupts an action. Interruption effect: if the action is a skill, causes knockdown for 2...3 seconds on target foe and all adjacent foes. <gray>50% failure chance unless Fast Casting 5 or higher.</gray>'],
3186=>['Shared Burden (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, target foe and all nearby foes attack, cast spells, and move 33% slower.','Also hexes foes near your target (5...20 seconds). These foes attack, cast spells, and move 33% slower.'],
3187=>['Stolen Speed (PvP)','For 1...10 seconds, spells cast by the target foe and all adjacent foes take 100% longer to cast. Spells you cast that target these foes take 50% less time to cast.','Also hexes adjacent foes (1...10 seconds). Doubles spell casting time. Spells you cast on hexed foes have -50% casting time.'],
3188=>['Unnatural Signet (PvP)','Target foe takes 10...60 damage. If that foe is under the effects of a hex or enchantment, foes adjacent to your target take 10...60 damage. All your non-Mesmer skills except signets are disabled for 10 seconds.','Deals 10...60 damage. Deals 10...60 damage to other adjacent foes if the target is hexed or enchanted. <gray>Your non-Mesmer skills except signets are disabled (10 seconds).</gray>'],
3189=>['Spiritual Pain (PvP)','Target foe takes 5...40 damage. All hostile summoned creatures in the area of that foe take 25...125 damage.','Deals 5...40 damage. Deals 25...125 damage to hostile summoned creatures in the area of your target foe.'],
3190=>['Frustration (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, target foe casts spells 50% slower and takes 5...50 damage whenever interrupted.','(5...20 seconds.) Causes 50% slower spell casting. Target foe takes 5...50 damage whenever interrupted.'],
3191=>['Mistrust (PvP)','For 6 seconds, the next spell that target foe casts on one of your allies fails and deals 10...75 damage to that foe and all nearby foes.','(6 seconds.) The next spell that target foe casts on one of your allies fails and deals 10...75 damage to target and nearby foes.'],
3192=>['Enchanter\'s Conundrum (PvP)','For 10 seconds, target foe casts enchantments 100...200% slower. If target foe is not under the effects of an enchantment when this hex is applied, that foe and all adjacent foes take 10...100 damage.','Causes 100...200% slower enchantment casting (10 seconds). Initial effect: deals 10...100 damage to target and adjacent foes if target foe is not enchanted.'],
3193=>['Signet of Clumsiness (PvP)','If target foe is attacking, that foe and all adjacent foes are interrupted and take 15...60 damage. Any foes using attack skills are knocked down.','Interrupts an attack for target foe and all adjacent foes. Interruption effect: deals 15...60 damage; knocks down foes using attack skills.'],
3194=>['Mirror of Disenchantment (PvP)','Remove one enchantment from target foe. All of that foe\'s party members also lose that same enchantment.','Removes one enchantment from target foe. That foe\'s party members also lose this enchantment.'],
3195=>['Wandering Eye (PvP)','For 4 seconds, the next time target foe attacks, that attack is interrupted and all nearby foes take 10...92 damage.','(4 seconds.) Interrupts target foe\'s next attack. Interruption effect: 10...92 damage to nearby foes.'],
3196=>['Calculated Risk (PvP)','For 3...12 seconds, target foe\'s attacks do +10 damage, but there is a 50% chance that the damage from each attack will be done to that foe instead. (Maximum 10...60 damage.)','Target foe does +10 damage with attacks (3...12 seconds). There is a 50% chance that the damage from each attack (maximum 10...60) will be done to that foe instead.'],
3204=>['Defy Pain (PvP)','For 20 seconds you have an additional 90...300 Health and an additional 20 armor.','(20 seconds.) You have +90...300 maximum Health and +20 armor.'],
3232=>['Heal Party (PvP)','Heal entire party for 30...75 Health.','Heals entire party for 30...75.'],
3233=>['Spoil Victor (PvP)','For 3...15 seconds, whenever target foe attacks or casts a spell on a creature with less Health that foe loses 15...75 Health.','(3...15 seconds.) Causes 15...75 Health loss whenever target foe attacks or casts spells on a creature with less Health.'],
3234=>['Visions of Regret (PvP)','For 10 seconds, target foe and adjacent foes take 10...30 damage whenever they use a skill and 5...40 additional damage if not under the effects of another Mesmer hex.','Also hexes foes adjacent to target (10 seconds). These foes take 10...30 damage whenever they use a skill and 5...40 additional damage if not under the effects of another Mesmer hex.'],
3251=>['Fox Fangs (PvP)','Must follow a lead attack. Fox Fangs cannot be blocked and strikes for +10...25 damage if it hits.','Deals +10...25 damage. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
3252=>['Wild Strike (PvP)','Must follow a lead attack. If it hits, this attack strikes for +10...35 damage and any stance being used by target foe ends. This attack cannot be blocked.','Deals +10...35 damage. Removes target foe\'s stance. Unblockable. <gray>Must follow a lead attack.</gray>'],
3263=>['Banishing Strike (PvP)','If it hits, this attack deals 10...60 holy damage. It deals double damage to summoned creatures.','Deals 10...60 holy damage. Deals double damage to summoned creatures.'],
3264=>['Twin Moon Sweep (PvP)','You lose 1 Dervish enchantment and gain 10...20 Health. If an enchantment is lost in this way, you cannot be blocked, you strike twice, with each strike doing 25% less damage than normal, and you gain an additional 10...30 Health.','Remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Gain 10...20 Health. Removal effect: Unblockable, attack twice, each strike doing 25% less damage, and gain 10...30 more Health.'],
3265=>['Irresistible Sweep (PvP)','Deal +3...15 damage and lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If you lose an enchantment in this way, Irresistible Sweep cannot be blocked and removes a stance.','Deals +3...15 damage. Remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: unblockable, removes a stance.'],
3266=>['Pious Assault (PvP)','You remove 1 Dervish enchantment. If a Dervish enchantment was removed, this skill recharges 75% faster and adjacent foes take 10...30 damage.','Removes 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: this skill recharges 75% faster and adjacent foes take 10...30 damage.'],
3269=>['Guiding Hands (PvP)','For 20 seconds, your next 0...3 attacks cannot be blocked. When activated, this skill removes the Blindness condition.','(20 seconds.) Your next 0...3 attacks cannot be blocked. Initial effect: removes Blindness.'],
3270=>['Avatar of Dwayna (PvP)','For 10...90 seconds, your attacks deal holy damage. Whenever you use a Dervish attack skill, you lose 1 hex. Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment, you are healed for 5...50 Health. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) Deal holy damage. You lose 1 hex whenever you use a Dervish attack skill. Heal yourself for 5...50 Health whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.'],
3271=>['Avatar of Melandru (PvP)','For 10...90 seconds, you have +100 Health, +30 elemental armor, and your attacks deal earth damage. Whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment you lose 2 conditions. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.','(10...90 seconds.) You have +100 maximum Health, +30 elemental armor, and your attacks deal earth damage. Cure 2 conditions from yourself whenever you lose a Dervish enchantment. This skill is disabled for 45 seconds.'],
3272=>['Mystic Healing (PvP)','You are healed for 5...65 Health. Also heals all enchanted party members for 5...65 Health.','Heals you for 5...65. Heals all enchanted party members for 5...65 Health.'],
3273=>['Signet of Pious Restraint (PvP)','Lose 1 Dervish enchantment and Cripple target foe 5...15 seconds. If an enchantment was removed, this skill recharges 75% faster.','(5...15 seconds.) Cripples target foe and removes 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: recharges 75% faster.'],
3289=>['Fevered Dreams (PvP)','For 5...15 seconds, whenever target foe suffers from a new condition, all foes in the area suffer from that condition as well.','(5...15 seconds.) Foes in the area also have any new conditions that target foe acquires.'],
3346=>['Aura of Thorns (PvP)','All nearby foes begin Bleeding for 5...15 seconds. For 30 seconds, this enchantment does nothing. When this enchantment ends, all nearby foes are Crippled for 3...8 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Initial effect: inflicts Bleeding condition (5...15 seconds) on nearby foes. End effect: inflicts Crippled condition (3...8 seconds) on nearby foes.'],
3347=>['Dust Cloak (PvP)','All adjacent foes are struck for 10...40 earth damage. For 30 seconds, your attacks deal earth damage. When this enchantment ends, all adjacent foes are Blinded for 1...4 seconds.','(30 seconds.) Your attacks deal earth damage. Initial effect: deals 10...40 earth damage to adjacent foes. End effect: inflicts Blindness condition (1...4 seconds) on adjacent foes.'],
3348=>['Lyssa\'s Haste (PvP)','For 3...15 seconds, your Dervish enchantments recharge 33% faster. When you activate this enchantment, all adjacent foes are interrupted. When this enchantment ends, all adjacent foes are interrupted. 50% failure chance unless Wind Prayers 5 or higher.','(3...15 seconds.) Your Dervish enchantments recharge 33% faster. Initial Effect: interrupts all adjacent foes. End Effect: interrupts all adjacent foes. <gray>50% failure chance unless Wind Prayers 5 or higher.</gray>'],
3365=>['Onslaught (PvP)','For 2...8 seconds, you attack and gain adrenaline 25% faster.','(2...8 seconds.) You attack and gain adrenaline 25% faster.'],
3366=>['Heart of Fury (PvP)','For 2...10 seconds, you attack 25% faster.','(2...10 seconds.) You attack 25% faster.'],
3367=>['Wounding Strike (PvP)','If this attack hits, target foe suffers from Bleeding for 5...20 seconds, and you lose 1 Dervish enchantment. If an enchantment is removed, target foe also suffers from a Deep Wound for 5...20 seconds.','Inflicts Bleeding condition (5...20 seconds). Removes 1 Dervish enchantment. Removal effect: inflicts Deep Wound condition (5...20 seconds).'],
3368=>['Pious Fury (PvP)','Remove one Dervish enchantment. For 1...5 seconds, you attack 25% faster. If an enchantment was removed, this stance lasts twice as long.','(1...5 seconds.)You <sic/> attack 25% faster and remove 1 of your Dervish enchantments. Removal effect: this stance lasts twice as long.'],
3373=>['Illusion of Haste (PvP)','For 5...11 seconds, you move 33% faster. When Illusion of Haste ends, you become Crippled for 3 seconds.','(5...11 seconds.) You move 33% faster. <gray>End effect: you are Crippled (3 seconds).</gray>'],
3374=>['Illusion of Pain (PvP)','For 8 seconds, target foe has -3...10 Health degeneration and takes 3...10 damage each second. When Illusion of Pain ends or is reapplied, that foe is healed for 36...120.','(8 seconds.) Causes -3...10 Health degeneration and target foe takes 3...10 damage each second. End effect: that foe is healed for 36...120. <gray>Ends if reapplied.</gray>'],
3375=>['Aura of Restoration (PvP)','For 60 seconds, you gain 0...1 Energy and are healed for 200...400% of the Energy cost each time you cast a spell.','(60 seconds.) You gain 0...1 Energy and are healed for 200...400% of the Energy cost each time you cast a spell.'],
3386=>['Web of Disruption (PvP)','Interrupt target foe. For 10 seconds, target foe is hexed with Web of Disruption. When this hex ends, that foe is interrupted again.','(10 seconds.) Initial effect: interrupts a skill. End effect: interrupts a skill.'],
3396=>['Lightning Hammer (PvP)','Target foe is struck for 10...100 lightning damage. Lightning Hammer has 25% armor penetration.','Deals 10...100 lightning damage. 25% armor penetration.'],
3397=>['Elemental Flame (PvP)','For 5...20 seconds, whenever you apply an Elemental hex to a foe, that foe is set on fire for 1...2 seconds.','(5...20 seconds.) Inflicts Burning condition (1...2 seconds) whenever you apply an Elemental hex to a target.'],
3398=>['Slippery Ground (PvP)','If target foe is Blind or moving, that foe is knocked down. (50% failure chance with Water Magic 4 or less.)','Causes knock-down if this foe is Blind or moving. <gray>50% failure chance unless Water Magic 5 or higher.</gray>'],
3422=>['Time Ward','You create a Time Ward at your location. For 3...15 seconds, non-spirit allies in this area cast spells 15...20% faster and recharge skills 15...20% faster.','(3...15 seconds.) Allies in this ward cast spells 15...20% faster and recharge skills 15...20% faster. <gray>Allied spirits are not affected. PvE Skill</gray>'],
3423=>['Soul Taker','For 3...30 seconds, your attacks sacrifice 15...20 health and deal 15...20 more damage.','(3...30 seconds.) Attacks deal +15...20 damage and sacrifice 15...20 health.'],
3424=>['Over the Limit','While you maintain this enchantment, your spells cast 15...20% faster, and recharge 15...50% faster, but you continuously gain Overcast.','Spells cast 15...20% faster and recharge 15...50% faster. Continuously gain Overcast while active.'],
3425=>['Judgment Strike','Attack target and adjacent foes. Each attack that hits deals +13...30 Holy damage <sic/> and knocks down attacking foes.','Attacks target and adjacent foes for +13...30 Holy damage. Causes knock down on attacking foes.'],
3426=>['Seven Weapons Stance','For 3...20 seconds, your weapon attributes are increased by +1...15 and you attack 33% faster.','(3...20 seconds.) Weapon attributes are increased by +1...15. You attack 33% faster.'],
3427=>['"Together as One!"','For 3...15 seconds, all party members near you or near your pet deal +5...15 additional damage with attacks and gain +1...7 Health regeneration.','(3...15 seconds.) All party members near you or your pet deal +5...15 damage <sic/> and gain +1...7 Health regeneration.'],
3428=>['Shadow Theft','Shadow Step to target foe. For 5...20 seconds that foe\'s attributes are reduced by 1...5 and your attributes are increased by 1...5. This skill counts as a Lead Attack.','Shadow Step to target foe. For 5...20 seconds that foe\'s attributes are reduced by 1...5 and your attributes are increased by 1...5. Counts as a Lead Attack.'],
3429=>['Weapons of Three Forges','For 3...20 seconds, each non-spirit ally in earshot gains the effect of a random Weapon Spell.','(3...20 seconds.) Allies in earshot gain the effect of a random Weapon Spell. <gray>Allied spirits are not affected. PvE Skill</gray>'],
3430=>['Vow of Revolution','For 3...10 seconds, you have +1...5 energy regeneration. This skill reapplies itself every time you use a non-Dervish skill.','(3...10 seconds.) Gain +1...5 energy regeneration. Renewal: whenever you use a non-Dervish skill.'],
3431=>['Heroic Refrain','For 3...15 seconds, target non-spirit ally gains +1...3 to all attributes. This echo is reapplied every time a chant or shout ends on that ally.','(3...15 seconds.) Target ally gains +1...3 to all attributes. Renewal: every time a chant or shout ends on this ally. <gray>Cannot target spirits. PvE Skill</gray>'],
];}
